/****** Object:  UserDefinedFunction [dbo].[splitstring]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[splitstring] ( @stringToSplit VARCHAR(MAX), @dau NVARCHAR(10) )
RETURNS
 @returnList TABLE ([Name] [nvarchar] (500))
AS
BEGIN

 DECLARE @name NVARCHAR(255)
 DECLARE @pos INT

 WHILE CHARINDEX(@dau, @stringToSplit) > 0
 BEGIN
  SELECT @pos  = CHARINDEX(@dau, @stringToSplit)  
  SELECT @name = SUBSTRING(@stringToSplit, 1, @pos-1)

  INSERT INTO @returnList 
  SELECT @name

  SELECT @stringToSplit = SUBSTRING(@stringToSplit, @pos+1, LEN(@stringToSplit)-@pos)
 END

 INSERT INTO @returnList
 SELECT @stringToSplit

 RETURN
END

GO
/****** Object:  Table [dbo].[Data_Customer]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Data_Customer](
	[Id] [bigint] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[Name] [nvarchar](max) NULL,
	[Phone] [nvarchar](max) NULL,
	[Email] [nvarchar](max) NULL,
	[DbName] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[StartedDate] [datetime] NULL,
	[Theme] [nvarchar](max) NULL,
	[CreatedBy] [bigint] NULL,
	[CreatedDate] [datetime] NULL,
	[UpdatedBy] [bigint] NULL,
	[UpdatedDate] [datetime] NULL,
	[IsActive] [bit] NULL,
	[IsDeleted] [bit] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Data_Customer] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[Id] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]

	[ErrorId] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[ErrorNum] [int] NULL,

	[DataBaseName] [varchar](200) NULL,

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Attachment_Get_GetAttackmenByRecordId]
	@RecordId BIGINT,
	@DataType NVARCHAR(100),
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
				SELECT  
					*
				FROM dbo.Data_Attachment 
				WHERE RecordId=@RecordId AND IsDeleted=0 AND DataType=@DataType
				ORDER BY Id DESC
		'
	SET @params = '@RecordId BIGINT,@DataType NVARCHAR(100)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@RecordId,@DataType

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Attachment_Update_SaveAttachment]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Attachment_Update_SaveAttachment]
	 @Id				BIGINT,
     @FileName			NVARCHAR(500),
     @DisplayFileName	NVARCHAR(500),
     @FileExtension		NVARCHAR(500),
     @FileSize			FLOAT,
     @Name				NVARCHAR(500),
     @Description		NVARCHAR(500),
     @RecordId			BIGINT,
     @DataType			NVARCHAR(500),
     @DbName			NVARCHAR(500)
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 					 
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				
				IF(@Id=0)
				BEGIN
					INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Attachment
							 ( FileName ,
							   DisplayFileName ,
							   FileExtension ,
							   FileSize ,
							   Name ,
							   Description ,
							   RecordId ,
							   DataType ,
							   IsDeleted ,
							   CreatedDate
							 )
					 VALUES  ( @FileName , -- FileName - nvarchar(max)
							   @DisplayFileName , -- DisplayFileName - nvarchar(max)
							   @FileExtension , -- FileExtension - nvarchar(50)
							   @FileSize	, -- FileSize - float
							   @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(max)
							   @Description , -- Description - nvarchar(max)
							   0 , -- RecordId - bigint
							   @DataType , -- DataType - nvarchar(200)
							   0 , -- IsDeleted - bit
							   GETDATE()  -- CreatedDate - datetime
							 )
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					 UPDATE  Hrm_System.dbo.Data_Attachment 
							SET 
							   FileName=@FileName,
							   DisplayFileName=@DisplayFileName ,
							   FileExtension=@FileExtension,
							   FileSize=@FileSize,
							   Name=@Name,
							   Description=@Description ,
							   DataType=@DataType,
							   IsDeleted=0
					 WHERE Id=@Id
				END
			'	
	SET @params ='@Id BIGINT,@FileName	NVARCHAR(500), @DisplayFileName	NVARCHAR(500),@FileExtension NVARCHAR(500),@FileSize FLOAT, @Name NVARCHAR(500),
	 @Description NVARCHAR(500),@RecordId BIGINT, @DataType	NVARCHAR(500)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@FileName,@DisplayFileName,@FileExtension,@FileSize,@Name,@Description,@RecordId,@DataType
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Del_DeleteChecklist]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Del_DeleteChecklist]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
						IF((SELECT 
								COUNT(DSC.Id)
							FROM dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail DSC
							INNER JOIN dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DCD ON DCD.Id=DSC.ChecklistDetailId
							INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Checklist C ON C.Id=DCD.ChecklistId
							WHERE C.Id=@Id)>0)	
						BEGIN
							SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Checklist
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							UPDATE dbo.Data_Checklist SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE Id=@Id	
							UPDATE dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE ChecklistId=@Id
							--UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE Id=@Id
						END			

					'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklist]
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
								SELECT DCL.Id,
									DCL.Name,
									DCL.Note
							FROM dbo.Data_Checklist DCL
							WHERE DCL.IsDeleted=0
					'
	SET @params = ''
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklistDetailByChecklistId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklistDetailByChecklistId]
	@ChecklistId					BIGINT,
	@DbName							VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT 
							DCD.*,
							DC.Name AS ChecklistName,
							DC.Note AS ChecklistNote,
							SMDT.Name AS ChecklistDetailTypeName,
							SMDC.Name AS ControlTypeName,
							DSI.Name AS AssigneeName,
							DCA.AssigneeId,
							DCA.Id as AssignId
						FROM dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DCD
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Checklist DC ON DCD.ChecklistId = DC.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMDT ON SMDT.Id = DCD.ChecklistDetailTypeId AND SMDT.IsDeleted = 0
						LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMDC ON SMDC.Id = DCD.TypeControlId AND SMDC.IsDeleted = 0
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign DCA ON DCA.ChecklistDetailId=DCD.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id=DCA.AssigneeId
						WHERE DCD.ChecklistId = @ChecklistId and DC.IsDeleted = 0 and DCD.IsDeleted=0
					'
	SET @params = '@ChecklistId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @ChecklistId
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklistDetailByStaffId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklistDetailByStaffId]
	@StaffId						BIGINT,
	@DbName							VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT 
							DCD.*,
							DC.Name AS ChecklistName,
							DC.Note AS ChecklistNote,
							SMDT.Name AS ChecklistDetailTypeName,
							SMDC.Name AS ControlTypeName,
							DSCD.IsFinish AS IsFinished,
							ISNULL(DSCD.Value, '''') AS Value,
							DSI.Name AS AssigneeName,
							CASE 
								WHEN ISNULL(DSCD.UpdatedDate,0) = 0 THEN  DSCD.CreatedDate
								ELSE  DSCD.UpdatedDate
							END AS UpdatedDate
						FROM dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DCD
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail DSCD ON DCD.Id = DSCD.ChecklistDetailId AND DSCD.StaffId = @StaffId AND DSCD.IsDeleted = 0
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Checklist DC ON DCD.ChecklistId = DC.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMDT ON SMDT.Id = DCD.ChecklistDetailTypeId AND SMDT.IsDeleted = 0
						LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMDC ON SMDC.Id = DCD.TypeControlId AND SMDC.IsDeleted = 0
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign  CLA ON DCD.Id = CLA.ChecklistDetailId AND CLA.IsDeleted = 0
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON CLA.AssigneeId = DSI.Id AND DSI.IsDeleted = 0
						WHERE DCD.IsDeleted = 0 AND DC.IsDeleted = 0 AND DCD.ChecklistId=2
					'
	SET @params = '@StaffId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @StaffId
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklistStaffDetail]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Get_GetChecklistStaffDetail]
	@StaffId						BIGINT,
	@ChecklistId					BIGINT,
	@DbName							VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
	;WITH ChecklistDetail_CTE(Id, ChecklistId,Name, ColumnLink, ChecklistDetailTypeId, TypeControlId, IsDefault, ParentId)
		AS
		(
		SELECT		DSC.ChecklistDetailId AS Id
				,	DSC.ChecklistId AS ChecklistId
				,	DSC.Name AS Name
				,	DSC.ColumnLink AS ColumnLink
				,	DSC.ChecklistDetailTypeId AS ChecklistDetailTypeId
				,	DSC.TypeControlId AS TypeControlId
				,	DSC.IsDefault AS IsDefault
				,	DSC.ParentId AS ParentId
		FROM dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail DSC 
		INNER JOIN dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DC ON DSC.ChecklistDetailId = DC.Id
		WHERE DSC.StaffId = @StaffId AND ISNULL(DSC.IsDeleted,0) <> 1 

		UNION 
		SELECT		DC.Id AS Id
				,	DC.ChecklistId AS ChecklistId
				,	DC.Name AS Name
				,	DC.ColumnLink AS ColumnLink
				,	DC.ChecklistDetailTypeId AS ChecklistDetailId
				,	DC.TypeControlId AS TypeControlId
				,	DC.IsDefault AS IsDefault
				,	DC.ParentId AS ParentId
		FROM dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DC WHERE Id NOT IN (SELECT  DC.Id
		FROM dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail DSC
		INNER JOIN dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DC ON DSC.ChecklistDetailId = DC.Id
		WHERE DSC.StaffId = @StaffId AND ISNULL(DSC.IsDeleted,0) <> 1 ) 
		)
		SELECT
		CTE.*,
		DC.Name AS ChecklistName,
		DC.Note AS ChecklistNote,
		SMDT.Name AS ChecklistDetailTypeName,
		SMDC.Name AS ControlTypeName,
		DSI.Name AS AssigneeName,
		DCA.AssigneeId,
		DCA.Id as AssignId
		FROM ChecklistDetail_CTE CTE
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Checklist DC ON CTE.ChecklistId = DC.Id
		LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMDT ON SMDT.Id = CTE.ChecklistDetailTypeId AND SMDT.IsDeleted = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMDC ON SMDC.Id = CTE.TypeControlId AND SMDC.IsDeleted = 0
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign DCA ON DCA.ChecklistDetailId=CTE.Id
		LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id=DCA.AssigneeId
		WHERE CTE.ChecklistId = @ChecklistId
		'
	SET @params = '@StaffId BIGINT, @ChecklistId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @ChecklistId,@StaffId
END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Get_SearchChecklist]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Get_SearchChecklist]
	@LanguageId			BIGINT,
	@SearchKey			NVARCHAR(500),
	@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
								SELECT DCL.Id,
									DCL.Name,
									DCL.Note
							FROM dbo.Data_Checklist DCL
							WHERE DCL.IsDeleted=0 and LOWER(DCL.Name) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')

							--SELECT DCL.Id,
							--		DCL.Name,
							--		DCL.Note
							--FROM dbo.Data_Checklist DCL
							--INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = DCL.Id
							--WHERE L.DataType = ''Checklist'' AND L.PropertyName = ''Name'' AND L.LanguageId = @LanguageId AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')
							'
	SET @params = '@LanguageId BIGINT,@SearchKey NVARCHAR(500)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@LanguageId,@SearchKey

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Update_ChecklistDetail]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

CREATE procedure[dbo].[Checklist_Update_ChecklistDetail] 
			@ChecklistId bigint
			,@Name nvarchar(2000)
           ,@Value nvarchar(max)
           ,@ColumnLink nvarchar(50)
           ,@ChecklistDetailTypeId bigint
           ,@TypeControlId bigint
           ,@IsDefault bit
           ,@IsSendMail bit
           ,@MailTemplateId bigint
           ,@Note nvarchar(max)
           ,@ParentId bigint
           ,@IsDeleted bit
			,@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
			,@Id				bigint output
as

	begin try
		declare	
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@Params					nvarchar(max)
							
		if @Id <= 0
			begin
			-- insert
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			
INSERT INTO [dbo].[[Data_ChecklistDetail]]
           ([ChecklistId]
           ,[Name]
           ,[Value]
           ,[ColumnLink]
           ,[ChecklistDetailTypeId]
           ,[TypeControlId]
           ,[IsDefault]
           ,[IsSendMail]
           ,[MailTemplateId]
           ,[Note]
           ,[ParentId]
           ,[IsDeleted])
		   values (
		   @ChecklistId
           ,@Name
           ,@Value
           ,@ColumnLink
           ,@ChecklistDetailTypeId
           ,@TypeControlId
           ,@IsDefault
           ,@IsSendMail
           ,@MailTemplateId
           ,@Note
           ,@ParentId
           ,@IsDeleted)
			set    @Id			= scope_Identity()'
			end
		else
			begin
				--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			update [dbo].[Data_ChecklistDetail] 
			ChecklistId    =@ChecklistId
           ,Name    =@Name
           ,Value    =@Value
           ,ColumnLink    =@ColumnLink
           ,ChecklistDetailTypeId    =@ChecklistDetailTypeId
           ,TypeControlId    =@TypeControlId
           ,IsDefault    =@IsDefault
           ,IsSendMail    =@IsSendMail
           ,MailTemplateId    =@MailTemplateId
           ,Note    =@Note
           ,ParentId    =@ParentId
           ,IsDeleted    =@IsDeleted
		   where Id = @Id'
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '@ChecklistId bigint
			,@Name nvarchar(2000)
           ,@Value nvarchar(max)
           ,@ColumnLink nvarchar(50)
           ,@ChecklistDetailTypeId bigint
           ,@TypeControlId bigint
           ,@IsDefault bit
           ,@IsSendMail bit
           ,@MailTemplateId bigint
           ,@Note nvarchar(max)
           ,@ParentId bigint
           ,@IsDeleted bit
			,@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
			,@Id				bigint'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
		EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, 
		@ChecklistId
		,@Name
		,@Value
		,@ColumnLink
		,@ChecklistDetailTypeId
		,@TypeControlId
		,@IsDefault
		,@IsSendMail
		,@MailTemplateId
		,@Note
		,@ParentId
		,@IsDeleted
		,@DbName
		,@Id 
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Checklist_Update_ChecklistDetail: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Checklist_Update_ChecklistDetail', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Update_SaveChecklist]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

Create procedure[dbo].[Checklist_Update_SaveChecklist]
	@Name nvarchar(500)
           ,@Note nvarchar(max)
           ,@CreatedBy int
           ,@CreatedDate datetime
           ,@UpdatedBy int
           ,@UpdatedDate datetime
           ,@IsDeleted bit
	,@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
	,@Id				bigint output
as

	begin try
		declare	
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@Params					nvarchar(max)
							
		if @Id <= 0
			begin
			-- insert
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			
INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Checklist]
           ([Name]
           ,[Note]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[CreatedDate] 
           ,[IsDeleted])
		   values (@Name
           ,@Note
           ,@CreatedBy
           ,getdate() 
           ,@IsDeleted)
			set    @Id			= scope_Identity()'
			end
		else
			begin
				--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			update [dbo].[Data_Checklist] [Name]=@Name
           ,[Note]=@Note
           ,[UpdatedBy]=@UpdatedBy
           ,[UpdatedDate] =getdate()
           ,[IsDeleted]		=@IsDeleted			
					where Id = @Id'
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '@Name nvarchar(500)
           ,@Note nvarchar(max)
           ,@CreatedBy int
           ,@CreatedDate datetime
           ,@UpdatedBy int
           ,@UpdatedDate datetime
           ,@IsDeleted bit
			,@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
			,@Id				bigint'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @Name
    ,@Note
    ,@CreatedBy
    ,@CreatedDate
    ,@UpdatedBy
    ,@UpdatedDate
    ,@IsDeleted
    ,@DbName
    ,@Id 
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Checklist_Update_SaveChecklist: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Checklist_Update_SaveChecklist', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Checklist_Update_SaveFullChecklist]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Checklist_Update_SaveFullChecklist]
	  @Id BIGINT,
      @Name NVARCHAR(500),
	  @Note NVARCHAR(500),
	  @CreatedBy BIGINT,
	  @UpdatedBy BIGINT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @Checklistdetail ChecklistDetailType READONLY
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	
						 
	

	IF(@Id=0)		
	BEGIN

		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Checklist
						( Name ,
						  Note ,
						  CreatedBy ,
						  CreatedDate ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
				VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(500)
						  @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
						  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - int
						  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
						  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						)

				SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

				DECLARE @ChecklistDetailId BIGINT
				DECLARE @ChecklistId BIGINT
				DECLARE @ChecklistDetailName NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @Value VARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @ColumnLink NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @ChecklistDetailTypeId BIGINT
				DECLARE @TypeControlId BIGINT
				DECLARE @IsDefault BIT
				DECLARE @IsSendMail BIT
				DECLARE @MailTemplateId BIGINT
				DECLARE @NoteChecklistDetail NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @ParentId BIGINT
				DECLARE @ReceiverMailId BIGINT
				DECLARE @AssigneeId NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @AssigneeViewId BIGINT
				DECLARE @Index BIGINT

				DECLARE @Table TABLE (
					ChecklistDetailId BIGINT,
					[Index] BIGINT,
					ParentId BIGINT
				)

				DECLARE CursorChecklistDetail CURSOR FOR
				SELECT Id,ChecklistId,Name,Value,ColumnLink,ChecklistDetailTypeId,TypeControlId,IsDefault,IsSendMail,MailTemplateId,Note,ParentId,ReceiverMailId
				,AssigneeId,AssigneeViewId,[Index] FROM @Checklistdetail

				OPEN CursorChecklistDetail

				FETCH NEXT FROM CursorChecklistDetail
					INTO @ChecklistDetailId,@ChecklistId,@ChecklistDetailName,@Value,@ColumnLink,@ChecklistDetailTypeId,@TypeControlId,@IsDefault,@IsSendMail,@MailTemplateId,@NoteChecklistDetail
					,@ParentId,@ReceiverMailId,@AssigneeId,@AssigneeViewId,@Index

				WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
					BEGIN	
						
						IF(@ParentId=0)
						BEGIN															
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail
									( ChecklistId ,
									  Name ,
									  ColumnLink ,
									  ChecklistDetailTypeId ,
									  TypeControlId ,
									  IsDefault ,
									  IsSendMail ,
									  MailTemplateId ,
									  Note ,
									  ParentId ,
									  IsDeleted
									)

							VALUES  ( @Id , -- ChecklistId - bigint
									  @ChecklistDetailName , -- Name - nvarchar(2000)
									  @ColumnLink , -- ColumnLink - nvarchar(50)
									  @ChecklistDetailTypeId, -- ChecklistDetailTypeId - bigint
									  @TypeControlId , -- TypeControlId - bigint
									  @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
									  @IsSendMail , -- IsSendMail - bit
									  @MailTemplateId, -- MailTemplateId - bigint
									  @NoteChecklistDetail , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									  @ParentId , -- ParentId - bigint
									  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
									)
																									
							SET @ChecklistDetailId =SCOPE_IDENTITY()

							INSERT INTO @Table
									( ChecklistDetailId,
									  [Index],
									  ParentId
									)
							VALUES  ( @ChecklistDetailId , -- ChecklistDetailId - bigint
									  @Index , -- Index - bigint
									  @ParentId  -- ParentId - bigint
									)
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail
									( ChecklistId ,
									  Name ,
									  ColumnLink ,
									  ChecklistDetailTypeId ,
									  TypeControlId ,
									  IsDefault ,
									  IsSendMail ,
									  MailTemplateId ,
									  Note ,
									  ParentId ,
									  IsDeleted
									)

							SELECT   @Id , -- ChecklistId - bigint
									  @ChecklistDetailName , -- Name - nvarchar(2000)
									  @ColumnLink , -- ColumnLink - nvarchar(50)
									  @ChecklistDetailTypeId, -- ChecklistDetailTypeId - bigint
									  @TypeControlId , -- TypeControlId - bigint
									  @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
									  @IsSendMail , -- IsSendMail - bit
									  @MailTemplateId, -- MailTemplateId - bigint
									  @NoteChecklistDetail , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									  T.ChecklistDetailId , -- ParentId - bigint
									  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
							FROM @Table T
							WHERE @ParentId=T.[Index]
																									
							SET @ChecklistDetailId =SCOPE_IDENTITY()
						END	

						IF(@AssigneeId>0)
						BEGIN
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign
							( ChecklistDetailId ,
							  AssigneeId ,
							  AssigneeTypeId ,
							  TypeViewId ,
							  Status ,
							  ParentId ,
							  CreatedBy ,
							  CreatedDate ,
							  IsDeleted
							)
						VALUES ( @ChecklistDetailId  , -- ChecklistDetailId - bigint
							  @AssigneeId , -- AssigneeId - bigint
							  269 , -- AssigneeTypeId - bigint
							  NULL , -- TypeViewId - bigint
							  NULL , -- Status - int
							  NULL , -- ParentId - bigint
							  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - int
							  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
							  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
							)
						END
												
						--IF(@AssigneeViewId>0)
						--BEGIN
						--	INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign
						--		( ChecklistDetailId ,
						--		  AssigneeId ,
						--		  AssigneeTypeId ,
						--		  TypeViewId ,
						--		  Status ,
						--		  ParentId ,
						--		  CreatedBy ,
						--		  CreatedDate ,
						--		  IsDeleted
						--		)
						--	VALUES(@ChecklistDetailId  , -- ChecklistDetailId - bigint
						--		  @AssigneeViewId , -- AssigneeId - bigint
						--		  NULL , -- AssigneeTypeId - bigint
						--		  10441 , -- TypeViewId - bigint
						--		  NULL , -- Status - int
						--		  NULL , -- ParentId - bigint
						--		  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - int
						--		  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
						--		  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						--		)
						--END
						FETCH NEXT FROM CursorChecklistDetail
							INTO @ChecklistDetailId,@ChecklistId,@ChecklistDetailName,@Value,@ColumnLink,@ChecklistDetailTypeId,@TypeControlId,@IsDefault,@IsSendMail,@MailTemplateId,@NoteChecklistDetail
							,@ParentId,@ReceiverMailId,@AssigneeId,@AssigneeViewId,@Index						
					END
				CLOSE CursorChecklistDetail
				DEALLOCATE CursorChecklistDetail	
			'

		SET @params ='@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@Note NVARCHAR(500),@CreatedBy BIGINT,@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@Checklistdetail ChecklistDetailType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@Name,@Note,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@Checklistdetail
    END 
	ELSE
	BEGIN 
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

				UPDATE dbo.Data_Checklist 
						SET Name=@Name,
							Note = @Note,
							UpdatedBy= @UpdatedBy,
							UpdatedDate=GETDATE()
				WHERE Id=@Id

				UPDATE dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE ChecklistId=@Id

				UPDATE DC 
						SET 
							DC.ChecklistId=@Id,
							DC.Name=CL.Name,
							DC.ColumnLink=CL.ColumnLink,
							DC.ChecklistDetailTypeId=CL.ChecklistDetailTypeId,
							DC.TypeControlId=CL.TypeControlId,
							DC.IsDefault=CL.IsDefault,
							DC.IsSendMail=CL.IsSendMail,
							DC.MailTemplateId=CL.MailTemplateId,
							DC.Note =CL.Note,
							DC.ParentId=CL.ParentId,
							DC.IsDeleted=0
				FROM dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail DC 
				INNER JOIN @Checklistdetail CL ON CL.Id=DC.Id AND CL.Id<>0


				UPDATE DCA
					SET DCA.AssigneeId=CLD.AssigneeId
				FROM dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign DCA
				INNER JOIN @Checklistdetail CLD ON CLD.AssignId=DCA.Id
				WHERE CLD.Id<>0

				IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @Checklistdetail WHERE Id=0)>0)
				BEGIN
					DECLARE @ChecklistDetailId BIGINT=0
					DECLARE @ChecklistId BIGINT
					DECLARE @ChecklistDetailName NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @Value VARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @ColumnLink NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @ChecklistDetailTypeId BIGINT
					DECLARE @TypeControlId BIGINT
					DECLARE @IsDefault BIT
					DECLARE @IsSendMail BIT
					DECLARE @MailTemplateId BIGINT
					DECLARE @NoteChecklistDetail NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @ParentId BIGINT
					DECLARE @ReceiverMailId BIGINT
					DECLARE @AssigneeId NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @AssigneeViewId BIGINT
					DECLARE @Index BIGINT

					DECLARE @Table TABLE (
						ChecklistDetailId BIGINT,
						[Index] BIGINT,
						ParentId BIGINT
					)


					DECLARE CursorChecklistDetail CURSOR FOR
					SELECT Id,ChecklistId,Name,Value,ColumnLink,ChecklistDetailTypeId,TypeControlId,IsDefault,IsSendMail,MailTemplateId,Note,ParentId,ReceiverMailId
					,AssigneeId,AssigneeViewId,[Index] FROM @Checklistdetail WHERE Id=0

					OPEN CursorChecklistDetail

					FETCH NEXT FROM CursorChecklistDetail
						INTO @ChecklistDetailId,@ChecklistId,@ChecklistDetailName,@Value,@ColumnLink,@ChecklistDetailTypeId,@TypeControlId,@IsDefault,@IsSendMail,@MailTemplateId,@NoteChecklistDetail
						,@ParentId,@ReceiverMailId,@AssigneeId,@AssigneeViewId,@Index

					WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
						BEGIN	
							IF(@ParentId=0)
							BEGIN			
																				
								INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail
										( ChecklistId ,
										  Name ,
										  ColumnLink ,
										  ChecklistDetailTypeId ,
										  TypeControlId ,
										  IsDefault ,
										  IsSendMail ,
										  MailTemplateId ,
										  Note ,
										  ParentId ,
										  IsDeleted
										)

								VALUES  ( @Id , -- ChecklistId - bigint
										  @ChecklistDetailName , -- Name - nvarchar(2000)
										  @ColumnLink , -- ColumnLink - nvarchar(50)
										  @ChecklistDetailTypeId, -- ChecklistDetailTypeId - bigint
										  @TypeControlId , -- TypeControlId - bigint
										  @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
										  @IsSendMail , -- IsSendMail - bit
										  @MailTemplateId, -- MailTemplateId - bigint
										  @NoteChecklistDetail , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
										  @ParentId , -- ParentId - bigint
										  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
										)
																									
								SET @ChecklistDetailId =SCOPE_IDENTITY()

								INSERT INTO @Table
										( ChecklistDetailId,
										  [Index],
										  ParentId
										)
								VALUES  ( @ChecklistDetailId , -- ChecklistDetailId - bigint
										  @Index , -- Index - bigint
										  @ParentId  -- ParentId - bigint
										)
							END
							ELSE
							BEGIN
								INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail
										( ChecklistId ,
										  Name ,
										  ColumnLink ,
										  ChecklistDetailTypeId ,
										  TypeControlId ,
										  IsDefault ,
										  IsSendMail ,
										  MailTemplateId ,
										  Note ,
										  ParentId ,
										  IsDeleted
										)

								SELECT   @Id , -- ChecklistId - bigint
										  @ChecklistDetailName , -- Name - nvarchar(2000)
										  @ColumnLink , -- ColumnLink - nvarchar(50)
										  @ChecklistDetailTypeId, -- ChecklistDetailTypeId - bigint
										  @TypeControlId , -- TypeControlId - bigint
										  @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
										  @IsSendMail , -- IsSendMail - bit
										  @MailTemplateId, -- MailTemplateId - bigint
										  @NoteChecklistDetail , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
										  T.ChecklistDetailId , -- ParentId - bigint
										  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								FROM @Table T
								WHERE @ParentId=T.[Index]
																									
								SET @ChecklistDetailId =SCOPE_IDENTITY()

								IF(@ChecklistDetailId IS NULL or @ChecklistDetailId=0)
								BEGIN
									INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistDetail
										( ChecklistId ,
										  Name ,
										  ColumnLink ,
										  ChecklistDetailTypeId ,
										  TypeControlId ,
										  IsDefault ,
										  IsSendMail ,
										  MailTemplateId ,
										  Note ,
										  ParentId ,
										  IsDeleted
										)

									VALUES    (@Id , -- ChecklistId - bigint
											  @ChecklistDetailName , -- Name - nvarchar(2000)
											  @ColumnLink , -- ColumnLink - nvarchar(50)
											  @ChecklistDetailTypeId, -- ChecklistDetailTypeId - bigint
											  @TypeControlId , -- TypeControlId - bigint
											  @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
											  @IsSendMail , -- IsSendMail - bit
											  @MailTemplateId, -- MailTemplateId - bigint
											  @NoteChecklistDetail , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
											  @ParentId , -- ParentId - bigint
											  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
											  )
									SET @ChecklistDetailId =SCOPE_IDENTITY()
								END
								
						
								IF(@AssigneeId>0)
								BEGIN
									INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign
									( ChecklistDetailId ,
									  AssigneeId ,
									  AssigneeTypeId ,
									  TypeViewId ,
									  Status ,
									  ParentId ,
									  CreatedBy ,
									  CreatedDate ,
									  IsDeleted
									)
									VALUES ( @ChecklistDetailId  , -- ChecklistDetailId - bigint
										  @AssigneeId , -- AssigneeId - bigint
										  269 , -- AssigneeTypeId - bigint
										  NULL , -- TypeViewId - bigint
										  NULL , -- Status - int
										  NULL , -- ParentId - bigint
										  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - int
										  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
										  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
										)
								END
												
								IF(@AssigneeViewId>0)
								BEGIN
									INSERT INTO dbo.Data_ChecklistAssign
										( ChecklistDetailId ,
										  AssigneeId ,
										  AssigneeTypeId ,
										  TypeViewId ,
										  Status ,
										  ParentId ,
										  CreatedBy ,
										  CreatedDate ,
										  IsDeleted
										)
									VALUES(@ChecklistDetailId  , -- ChecklistDetailId - bigint
										  @AssigneeViewId , -- AssigneeId - bigint
										  NULL , -- AssigneeTypeId - bigint
										  269 , -- TypeViewId - bigint
										  NULL , -- Status - int
										  NULL , -- ParentId - bigint
										  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - int
										  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
										  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
										)
								END
							END	
							
							FETCH NEXT FROM CursorChecklistDetail
								INTO @ChecklistDetailId,@ChecklistId,@ChecklistDetailName,@Value,@ColumnLink,@ChecklistDetailTypeId,@TypeControlId,@IsDefault,@IsSendMail,@MailTemplateId,@NoteChecklistDetail
								,@ParentId,@ReceiverMailId,@AssigneeId,@AssigneeViewId,@Index						
						END
					CLOSE CursorChecklistDetail
					DEALLOCATE CursorChecklistDetail
				END

					
			'
		SET @params ='@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@Note NVARCHAR(500),@CreatedBy BIGINT,@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@Checklistdetail ChecklistDetailType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@Name,@Note,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@Checklistdetail
	END 
	
END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetEven]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
Create PROCEDURE[dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetEven]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY, 

	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			select di.name,o.OrganizationName,0 as type 
,di.Birthday,DATEDIFF(day,cast(getdate() as date),DATEFROMPARTS(year(getdate()),month(di.Birthday),day(di.Birthday))) 

from Data_Staff_Information di inner join Data_Staff_WorkingProcess p on di.CurrentWorkingProcessId=p.Id inner join Data_Organization o on p.OrganizationId=o.id
where DATEDIFF(day,cast(getdate() as date),DATEFROMPARTS(year(getdate()),month(di.Birthday),day(di.Birthday))) =0
union all

select di.name,o.OrganizationName,1 as type

,b.OnboardingDate,DATEDIFF(day,cast(getdate() as date),DATEFROMPARTS(year(getdate()),month(b.OnboardingDate),day(b.OnboardingDate))) 

from Data_Staff_Information di inner join Data_Staff_BoardingProcess b on di.id=b.StaffId
inner join Data_Staff_WorkingProcess p on di.CurrentWorkingProcessId=p.Id inner join Data_Organization o on p.OrganizationId=o.id
 where DATEDIFF(day,cast(getdate() as date),DATEFROMPARTS(year(getdate()),month(b.OnboardingDate),day(b.OnboardingDate)))  =0 '
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect 
		  exec(@SQL )
		----4. Count
		--set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(o.Id) '
		--set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE O.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL 
		--set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Organization', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetImplementation]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetImplementation]
	@StartDate DATE,
	@EndDate DATE,
	@TypeView int ,--0 tháng, 1 -- quý, 2 tuần
	@DbName							VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
				IF object_id(''tempdb.dbo.#resultDate'',''U'') is not null
		DROP TABLE #resultDate
		CREATE TABLE #resultDate(
			StartDate DATETIME,
			EndDate DATETIME,
			DatePeriod int,
		)
		IF (@TypeView=0) -- tháng
		BEGIN
			;WITH dt AS
			(
				SELECT @startDate AS [TheDate]
				UNION All
				SELECT DateAdd(month, 1, TheDate) 
				FROM dt WHERE [TheDate] < @Enddate
			)
			INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod)
			SELECT
				dt.TheDate AS Fromdate,EOMONTH(dt.TheDate) AS ToDate,DatePeriod=MONTH(dt.TheDate)
			FROM
				dt WHERE dt.TheDate<=@Enddate
		END
		ELSE IF  (@TypeView=1) -- quý
		BEGIN
			;With dt AS
			(
				SELECT @startDate AS [TheDate]
				UNION All
				SELECT DateAdd(QUARTER, 1, TheDate) 
				FROM dt WHERE [TheDate] < @Enddate
			)
			INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod)
			SELECT
				dt.TheDate AS Fromdate,EOMONTH(DATEFROMPARTS(year( dt.TheDate),datename(qq,dt.TheDate)*3,1)) AS ToDate,DatePeriod=datename(Quarter, dt.TheDate)
			From dt WHERE dt.TheDate<=@Enddate
		END
		ELSE IF  (@TypeView=2) -- tuần
		BEGIN
			;With dt AS
			(
				SELECT @startDate As [TheDate]
				UNION All
				SELECT DateAdd(week, 1, TheDate) FROM dt WHERE [TheDate] < @Enddate
			)
			INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod)
			SELECT
				dt.TheDate AS Fromdate,DateAdd(day,-1,DateAdd(week, 1, TheDate)) AS ToDate,DatePeriod=datename(WEEK,dt.TheDate)
			FROM dt WHERE dt.TheDate<=@Enddate
		END
		SELECT rd.StartDate
			,rd.EndDate
			,DatePeriod
			,total=sum(iif(w.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) ) 
		FROM Data_Staff_Information s     
		OUTER APPLY #resultDate rd
		OUTER APPLY (SELECT DISTINCT dw.WorkingStatus,StaffId 
					FROM    Data_Staff_WorkingProcess dw 
					WHERE s.id=dw.StaffId 
						AND (
							(isnull( dw.enddate,rd.EndDate)<=rd.EndDate     
								AND isnull( dw.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.StartDate 
								AND dw.StartDate<=rd.EndDate) 
							OR (isnull( dw.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.EndDate 
							AND dw.StartDate<=rd.EndDate 
							AND isnull( dw.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.StartDate )
						) 
		) w
		GROUP BY rd.StartDate,rd.EndDate,DatePeriod	'
	SET @params = '@StartDate DATE,@EndDate DATE, @TypeView int '
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @StartDate,@EndDate, @TypeView 
END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetStaffOnboardOrBirthdayByParentId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetStaffOnboardOrBirthdayByParentId]
	
	@ParentId						BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(MAX)
AS

	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQL					nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			nvarchar(max) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@Delim					nvarchar(100) = '',
		@Params					nvarchar(max)
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		;WITH CTE_StaffParrent(StaffId, ParentId)
			AS(
				SELECT StaffId, ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP 
				WHERE DSP.StaffId = @ParentId AND DSP.ParentId = @ParentId
				UNION 
				SELECT DSP.StaffId, DSP.ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP
				WHERE DSP.ParentId = @ParentId AND DSP.StaffId != @ParentId 
			)
			SELECT cte.StaffId, DSI.Name AS StaffName, Do.OrganizationName,
			CASE
				WHEN MONTH(DSI.Birthday) = MONTH(GETDATE()) AND DAY(DSI.Birthday) = DAY(GETDATE()) THEN 1
				ELSE 0
			END AS IsBirthday ,
			CASE
				WHEN DSW.WorkingprocessTypeId = 71 AND DAY(DSW.StartDate) = DAY(GETDATE()) AND MONTH(DSW.StartDate) = MONTH(GETDATE()) THEN 1
				ELSE 0
			END AS IsOnboard
			FROM CTE_StaffParrent cte
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW ON DSI.CurrentWorkingProcessId = DSW.Id
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Organization DO ON DSW.OrganizationId = DO.Id
			ON cte.StaffId  =  DSI.Id 
			WHERE ISNULL(DSI.IsDeleted,0)=0 AND DSW.WorkingprocessTypeId = 71 AND DAY(DSW.StartDate) = DAY(GETDATE()) AND MONTH(DSW.StartDate) = MONTH(GETDATE()) AND YEAR(DSW.StartDate) = YEAR(GETDATE()) OR (MONTH(DSI.Birthday) = MONTH(GETDATE()) AND DAY(DSI.Birthday) = DAY(GETDATE())) 
			'
			SET @Params = '@ParentId BIGINT'
	PRINT @SQL 
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @ParentId
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@ParentId=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @ParentId)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH





GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetSummary]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetSummary]
	@StartDate DATE,
	@EndDate DATE,
	@StartPeriod DATE,
	@EndPeriod DATE,
	@DbName							VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
			SELECT
			 Total = SUM(IIF(W.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) )
			,TotalOff = SUM(IIF(W.WorkingStatus=9,1,0))
			,Official = SUM(IIF(C.ContractTypeId=55,1,0))
			,Onboard = SUM(IIF(W.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) ) - SUM(IIF(C.ContractTypeId=55,1,0))
			,TotalPeriod = SUM(IIF(W1.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) )
			,TotalOffPeriod = SUM(IIF(W1.WorkingStatus=9,1,0))
			,OfficialPeriod = SUM(IIF(C1.ContractTypeId=55,1,0))
			,OnboardPeriod = SUM(IIF(W1.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) ) - SUM(IIF(C1.ContractTypeId=55,1,0))
		FROM Data_Staff_Information DSI 
		OUTER APPLY ( 
			SELECT TOP 1 * 
			FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW 
			WHERE DSW.StaffId=DSI.ID 
				AND (
						(ISNULL( DSW.EndDate, @Enddate) <= @Enddate     
							AND ISNULL( DSW.EndDate, @Enddate) >= @startDate 
							AND DSW.StartDate <= @Enddate) 
						OR (ISNULL( DSW.EndDate, @Enddate) >= @Enddate 
							AND DSW.StartDate <= @Enddate 
							AND ISNULL( DSW.Enddate, @Enddate) >= @startDate )
					) 
			ORDER BY StartDate desc) W 
		OUTER APPLY ( 
			SELECT TOP 1 * 
			FROM Data_Staff_Contract DSC
			WHERE DSC.StaffId = DSI.Id
				AND (
						(ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate, @Enddate) <= @Enddate     
							AND ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate, @Enddate) >= @StartDate 
							AND DSC.ContractStartDate <= @Enddate) 
						OR (ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate, @Enddate) >= @Enddate 
						AND DSC.ContractStartDate<=@Enddate 
						AND ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate,@Enddate) >= @StartDate )) 
			ORDER BY w.StartDate desc) C 
				OUTER APPLY ( 
			SELECT TOP 1 * 
			FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW 
			WHERE DSW.StaffId=DSI.ID 
				AND (
						(ISNULL( DSW.EndDate, @EndPeriod) <= @EndPeriod     
							AND ISNULL( DSW.EndDate, @EndPeriod) >= @StartPeriod 
							AND DSW.StartDate <= @EndPeriod) 
						OR (ISNULL( DSW.EndDate, @EndPeriod) >= @EndPeriod 
							AND DSW.StartDate <= @EndPeriod 
							AND ISNULL( DSW.Enddate, @EndPeriod) >= @StartPeriod )
					) 
			ORDER BY StartDate desc) W1 
		OUTER APPLY ( 
			SELECT TOP 1 * 
			FROM Data_Staff_Contract DSC
			WHERE DSC.StaffId = DSI.Id
				AND (
						(ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate, @EndPeriod) <= @EndPeriod     
							AND ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate, @EndPeriod) >= @EndPeriod 
							AND DSC.ContractStartDate <= @EndPeriod) 
						OR (ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate, @EndPeriod) >= @EndPeriod 
						AND DSC.ContractStartDate<=@EndPeriod 
						AND ISNULL( DSC.ContractEndDate,@EndPeriod) >= @EndPeriod )) 
			ORDER BY w.StartDate desc) C1  
				'
				PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StartDate DATE,@EndDate DATE, @StartPeriod DATE, @EndPeriod DATE'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @StartDate, @EndDate, @StartPeriod, @EndPeriod
END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetTurnoverrate]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetTurnoverrate]
	@StartDate DATE,
	@EndDate DATE,
	@TypeView int ,--0 tháng, 1 -- quý, 2 tuần
	@DbName							VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
		IF OBJECT_ID(''tempdb.dbo.#resultDate'',''U'') is not null
			DROP TABLE #resultDate

		CREATE TABLE #resultDate(
			StartDate DATETIME,
			EndDate DATETIME,
			DatePeriod int,
			Type int,
			TotalFirst decimal(18,2)
		)
		IF (@TypeView=0) -- tháng
		BEGIN
			;WITH dt As
			(
				SELECT @startDate AS [TheDate]
				Union All
				SELECT DATEADD(month, 1, TheDate) 
				FROM dt 
				WHERE [TheDate] < @Enddate
			)
			INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod,Type)
			SELECT
				dt.TheDate AS StartDate,EOMONTH(dt.TheDate) AS EndDate,DatePeriod=MONTH(dt.TheDate),0
			FROM
				dt WHERE dt.TheDate<=@Enddate
		END
		ELSE IF  (@TypeView=1) -- quý
		BEGIN
			;WITH dt AS
			(
				SELECT @startDate As [TheDate]
				Union All
				SELECT DATEADD(QUARTER, 1, TheDate) FROM dt WHERE [TheDate] < @Enddate
			)
				INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod,Type)
			SELECT
				dt.TheDate AS StartDate,EOMONTH(DATEFROMPARTS(year( dt.TheDate)
				,datename(qq,dt.TheDate)*3,1)) AS EndDate
				,DatePeriod=datename(Quarter, dt.TheDate),0
			FROM
			dt WHERE dt.TheDate<=@Enddate
		END
		ELSE IF  (@TypeView=2) -- tuần
		BEGIN
			;With dt AS
			(
				SELECT @startDate As [TheDate]
				Union All
				Select DATEADD(WEEK, 1, TheDate) FROM dt WHERE [TheDate] < @Enddate
			)
				INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod,Type)
			SELECT
				dt.TheDate AS StartDate
				,DATEADD(day,-1,DATEADD(WEEK, 1, TheDate)) AS EndDate
				,DatePeriod=datename(WEEK,dt.TheDate),0
			FROM dt
			WHERE dt.TheDate<=@Enddate
		END
		INSERT INTO #resultDate (StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod,Type,TotalFirst)
		 select StartDate,
				EndDate,
				DatePeriod,1,TotalFirst=sum(iif(b.WorkingStatusfirst=8,1,0) )
		FROM #resultDate rd
		outer apply (select Distinct w.WorkingStatus as WorkingStatusfirst,staffid
	   from Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w inner join Data_Staff_Information s on w.StaffId=s.id where  w.IsDeleted=0 and
((isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)<=rd.EndDate     
and isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.EndDate and     w.StartDate<=rd.EndDate) 
or (isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.EndDate and     w.StartDate<=rd.EndDate and isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.EndDate )) 
 ) b group by  StartDate,EndDate,DatePeriod

 delete #resultDate  where type=0
			select rd.EndDate,rd.StartDate,DatePeriod,TurnoverRate=iif(cast(sum(iif(a.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) )+TotalFirst as decimal(18,2))/2!=0, cast(sum(iif(a.WorkingStatus=9,1,0)) as decimal(18,2))/(cast(sum(iif(a.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) )+TotalFirst as decimal(18,2))/2),0)
	
	from #resultDate rd
	outer apply (select distinct w.WorkingStatus,staffid--total=sum(iif(w.WorkingStatus=8,1,0) ),totaloff=sum(iif(w.WorkingStatus=9,1,0))   
	from Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w where  
((isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)<=rd.EndDate     
and isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.StartDate and     w.StartDate<=rd.EndDate) 
or (isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.EndDate and     w.StartDate<=rd.EndDate and isnull( w.enddate,rd.EndDate)>=rd.StartDate )) 
 ) a 
 group by rd.EndDate,rd.StartDate,DatePeriod,TotalFirst '
 print @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StartDate DATE,@EndDate DATE, @TypeView int'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @StartDate,@EndDate, @TypeView 
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetWorkingDayChart]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Dashboard_Get_GetWorkingDayChart]
	@StaffId BIGINT,
	@Type INT,
	@Year NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName	VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
	IF(@Type = 0)	 --0 : Công		
		BEGIN		
			 SELECT SUM(TotalWorkingday) AS Total, (''T'' + CAST(MONTH(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX))) AS Month
			 FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary
			 WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND CAST(YEAR(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX)) = @Year
			 GROUP BY YEAR(Date),MONTH(date)
			 ORDER BY MONTH(date) ASC
		 END
	ELSE IF(@Type = 1) --1: Nghỉ phép
		BEGIN
		 SELECT SUM(WorkingdayOvertime) AS Total, (''T'' + CAST(MONTH(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX))) AS Month
			 FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary
			 WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND CAST(YEAR(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX)) = @Year
			 GROUP BY YEAR(Date),MONTH(date)
			 ORDER BY MONTH(date) ASC
		END
	ELSE IF(@Type = 2) --2: Nghỉ phép
		BEGIN
			SELECT COUNT(*) AS Total, (''T'' + CAST(MONTH(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX))) AS Month
			FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement
			WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND CAST(YEAR(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX)) = @Year AND  SupplementTypeId = 371 AND IsCompleted = 1
			GROUP BY YEAR(Date),MONTH(date)
		END
	ELSE IF(@Type = 3) --3: Nghỉ không lương
		BEGIN
			SELECT COUNT(*) AS Total, (''T'' + CAST(MONTH(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX))) AS Month
			FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement
			WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND CAST(YEAR(date) AS NVARCHAR(MAX)) = @Year AND  SupplementTypeId = 372 AND IsCompleted = 1
			GROUP BY YEAR(Date),MONTH(date)
		END
	'
	SET @params = '@StaffId INT,@Type INT,@Year DATE'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @StaffId, @Type, @Year
END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Data_Staff_Certificate_Update_Staff_Certificate]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
create PROCEDURE[dbo].[Data_Staff_Certificate_Update_Staff_Certificate]
	@StaffId bigint
    ,@TypeId bigint
    ,@Name nvarchar(500)
    ,@FromDate date
    ,@ToDate date
    ,@RankId bigint
    ,@IssuedBy nvarchar(1000)
    ,@Point decimal(18,2)
    ,@Note nvarchar(1000)
    ,@IsDeleted bit
	,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
	,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT
as
 
begin try

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 

	 

		if @Id <= 0
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Certificate]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[TypeId]
           ,[Name]
           ,[FromDate]
           ,[ToDate]
           ,[RankId]
           ,[IssuedBy]
           ,[Point]
           ,[Note]
           ,[IsDeleted])
     VALUES
			(
			@StaffId
           ,@TypeId
           ,@Name
           ,@FromDate
           ,@ToDate
           ,@RankId
           ,@IssuedBy
           ,@Point
           ,@Note
           ,@IsDeleted)	

			SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
			 '
		END	 
		else
		begin
		SET  @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				update dbo.Data_Staff_Certificate
				 set  
						[StaffId]=@StaffId
					   ,[TypeId]=@TypeId
					   ,[Name]=@Name
					   ,[FromDate]=@FromDate
					   ,[ToDate]=@ToDate
					   ,[RankId]=@RankId
					   ,[IssuedBy]=@IssuedBy
					   ,[Point]=@Point
					   ,[Note]=@Note
					   ,[IsDeleted]=@IsDeleted
						 where id=@Id

				'
		end
			PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '	@StaffId bigint
					   ,@TypeId bigint
					   ,@Name nvarchar(500)
					   ,@FromDate date
					   ,@ToDate date
					   ,@RankId bigint
					   ,@IssuedBy nvarchar(1000)
					   ,@Point decimal(18,2)
					   ,@Note nvarchar(1000)
					   ,@IsDeleted bit
						,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
						,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,
			@StaffId
           ,@TypeId
           ,@Name
           ,@FromDate
           ,@ToDate
           ,@RankId
           ,@IssuedBy
           ,@Point
           ,@Note
           ,@IsDeleted ,@DbName, @Id OUTPUT 
	
   
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Data_Staff_Certificate_Update_Staff_Certificate: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Certificate_Update_Staff_Certificate', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
GO

	--end catch
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships_Get_GetData_Staff_Relationships]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
Create PROCEDURE[dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships_Get_GetData_Staff_Relationships]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord	INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query

			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			select
			[AutoID]
			  ,[StaffID]
			  ,[RelationshipID]
			  ,[Name]
			  ,[BirthDay]
			  ,[Phone]
			  ,[Status]
			  ,[IsEmergency]
			  ,[Deduction]
			  ,[DeductionCode]
			  ,[DeductionFrom]
			  ,[DeductionTo]
			  ,[Note]
			  ,[CreatedDate]
			  ,[CreatedBy]
			  ,[ModifiedBy]
			  ,[ModifiedDate]
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships] w'
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 and w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy --+ 
	  --' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + ' 
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE  w.IsDeleted = 0 and w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Data_Staff_Relationships_Get_GetData_Staff_Relationships: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Relationships', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Data_User__Update_SaveDataUser]

	@UserName				NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@Password				NVARCHAR(MAX)
AS 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		UPDATE dbo.Data_User
		SET UserName = @UserName , Password = @Password , UpdatedDate = GETDATE()
		WHERE UserName = ''Admin''
		'
	SET @params = '@UserName NVARCHAR(MAX), @Password NVARCHAR(MAX) '
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @UserName, @Password

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Email_Get_GetEmail]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Email_Get_GetEmail]
	@IsMailWelcomeKit BIT,
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY
as
 
BEGIN

	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DbName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			IF(@IsMailWelcomeKit=1)	
			BEGIN
				SELECT  DSE.Id,
					DSE.Name,
					DSE.Title,
					DSE.ContentTemplate,
					DSE.Note,
					DSE.MailTo,
					DSE.MailCc,
					DSE.MailBcc,
					CountAttach=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Attachment WHERE RecordId=DSE.Id)		
				FROM dbo.Data_Setting_Email DSE
				WHERE DSE.IsDeleted=0 AND DSE.IsMailWelcomeKit=1
				ORDER BY DSE.Id DESC
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				SELECT  DSE.Id,
					DSE.Name,
					DSE.Title,
					DSE.ContentTemplate,
					DSE.Note,
					DSE.MailTo,
					DSE.MailCc,
					DSE.MailBcc,
					CountAttach=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Attachment WHERE RecordId=DSE.Id)		
			FROM dbo.Data_Setting_Email DSE
			WHERE DSE.IsDeleted=0
			ORDER BY DSE.Id DESC
			END
				
			
		'
	SET @params = '@IsMailWelcomeKit BIT,@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@IsMailWelcomeKit,@BaseParam

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Email_Get_GetEmailById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Email_Get_GetEmailById]
	@Id BIGINT,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
				SELECT  DSE.Id,
					DSE.Name,
					DSE.Title,
					DSE.ContentTemplate,
					DSE.MailTo,
					DSE.MailCc,
					DSE.MailBcc,
					DSE.Note,
					CountAttach=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Attachment WHERE RecordId=DSE.Id)	
			FROM dbo.Data_Setting_Email DSE
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Attachment DA on DA.RecordId=DSE.Id
			WHERE DSE.Id=@Id AND DSE.IsDeleted=0
			ORDER BY DSE.Id DESC
		'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Email_Update_SaveEmailTemplate]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Email_Update_SaveEmailTemplate]
	  @Id BIGINT,
      @Name NVARCHAR(500),
	  @Title NVARCHAR(500),
	  @ContentTemplate NVARCHAR(MAX),
	  @MailTo NVARCHAR(500),
	  @MailCc NVARCHAR(500),
	  @MailBcc NVARCHAR(500),
	  @CreatedBy BIGINT,
	  @AttachmentType AttachmentType READONLY,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500)
as
	
 
BEGIN	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	
	 
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				IF(@Id=0)
				BEGIN
					INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Setting_Email
							( Name ,
							  Title ,
							  ContentTemplate ,
							  MailTo ,
							  MailCc ,
							  MailBcc ,
							  Note ,
							  CreatedBy ,
							  CreatedDate ,
							  IsDeleted
							)
					VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(max)
							  @Title, -- Title - nvarchar(max)
							  @ContentTemplate , -- ContentTemplate - nvarchar(max)
							  @MailTo , -- MailTo - nvarchar(max)
							  @MailCc , -- MailCc - nvarchar(max)
							  @MailBcc , -- MailBcc - nvarchar(max)
							  NULL , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
							  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - bigint
							  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
							  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
							)

					SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()
					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @AttachmentType)>0)
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Attachment
								( FileName ,
								  DisplayFileName ,
								  FileExtension ,
								  FileSize ,
								  RecordId ,
								  DataType ,
								  IsDeleted,
								  CreatedDate
								)
						SELECT    AT.DisplayFileName, -- FileName - nvarchar(max)
								  AT.FileName , -- DisplayFileName - nvarchar(max)
								  AT.FileExtension , -- FileExtension - nvarchar(50)
								  AT.FileSize , -- FileSize - float
								  @Id , -- RecordId - bigint
								  ''Email'' , -- DataType - nvarchar(200)
								  0,  -- IsDeleted - bit
								  GETDATE()
						FROM @AttachmentType AT
					END
				END	
				ELSE
				BEGIN

					UPDATE dbo.Data_Setting_Email 
							SET 
								[Name]=@Name,
								[Title]=@Title,
								[ContentTemplate]=@ContentTemplate,
								[MailTo] =@MailTo,
								[MailCc]=@MailCc,
								[MailBcc]=@MailBcc,
								[UpdatedBy]=@CreatedBy,
								[UpdatedDate]=GETDATE(),
								[IsDeleted]=0
					WHERE Id=@Id

					UPDATE dbo.Data_Attachment SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE RecordId=@Id AND DataType=''Email''

					UPDATE DA
						SET DA.IsDeleted=0
					FROM dbo.Data_Attachment DA
					INNER JOIN @AttachmentType AT ON AT.Id=DA.Id
					WHERE AT.Id<>0 

					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @AttachmentType WHERE Id=0)>0)
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Attachment
								( FileName ,
								  DisplayFileName ,
								  FileExtension ,
								  FileSize ,
								  RecordId ,
								  DataType ,
								  IsDeleted,
								  CreatedDate
								)
						SELECT    AT.DisplayFileName , -- FileName - nvarchar(max)
								  AT.FileName , -- DisplayFileName - nvarchar(max)
								  AT.FileExtension , -- FileExtension - nvarchar(50)
								  AT.FileSize , -- FileSize - float
								  @Id , -- RecordId - bigint
								  ''Email'' , -- DataType - nvarchar(200)
								  0,  -- IsDeleted - bit
								  GETDATE()
						FROM @AttachmentType AT
					END

				END		
			'
		SET @params = '@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@Title NVARCHAR(500),@ContentTemplate NVARCHAR(MAX),@MailTo NVARCHAR(500),@MailCc NVARCHAR(500),@MailBcc NVARCHAR(500),
		@CreatedBy BIGINT,@AttachmentType AttachmentType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params ,@Id,@Name,@Title,@ContentTemplate,@MailTo,@MailCc,@MailBcc,@CreatedBy,@AttachmentType
	END 


	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Del_DeleteOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

CREATE procedure[dbo].[Organization_Del_DeleteOrganization]
	
	@Id								bigint,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							bigint,
	@RoleID							int,
	@Result							int output
as

	begin try
		declare	
		@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
		@Params					nvarchar(max)
		--Check right


		--Update
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
					
						DECLARE @Count BIGINT=(SELECT 
											COUNT(DSI.Id)
										FROM Data_Staff_Information DSI
										INNER JOIN Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW on DSW.StaffId=DSI.Id
										WHERE DSW.WorkingStatus=8 and DSW.OrganizationId=@Id)
						print @Count
						IF(@Count>0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT * FROM Data_Organization WHERE Id=@Id
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							UPDATE Data_Organization SET IsDeleted=1,UpdatedBy=@UserID,UpdateDate=GETDATE() WHERE Id=@Id
						END						
					'

					SET @Params = '@Id bigint,@UserID BIGINT'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params,@Id,@UserID
			 set @Result = 1
	end try

	begin catch
		set @Result = 0
		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Organization_Organization_Del: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@Userid=' + convert(varchar, @UserID) + ', @ID=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Organization_Organization_Del', 'DEL', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Get_CheckOrganizationType]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Get_CheckOrganizationType]
	@ListData ListDataSelectedId READONLY,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as					
						
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

						DECLARE @Data Table(
							[Type] BIGINT
						)	
						
						INSERT INTO @Data ([Type]) 
									SELECT  DO.OrganizationType
									FROM dbo.Data_Organization DO
									INNER JOIN @ListData L ON L.Id=DO.Id

						
						IF((SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT [Type])) 
						FROM @Data)>1)
						BEGIN
							SELECT DO.Id ,DO.OrganizationName
							FROM dbo.Data_Organization DO
							INNER JOIN @ListData L ON L.Id=DO.Id
						END	
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							SELECT TOP 1 DO.Id ,DO.OrganizationName,DO.OrganizationType
							FROM dbo.Data_Organization DO
							INNER JOIN @ListData L ON L.Id=DO.Id
						END
																		
					'
	SET @params = '@ListData ListDataSelectedId READONLY'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@ListData

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Get_GetAllOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Get_GetAllOrganization]
@DbName NVARCHAR(MAX)
AS
BEGIN TRY
		declare	
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX)
			SET	@SQL	= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
					O.[Id]
			    ,	O.[OrganizationName]
				,	O.[ParentId]
				,	(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Data_Organization O1 WHERE O1.ParentId =  O.Id) AS NumberOfChild
			FROM [dbo].[Data_Organization] O 
			WHERE O.IsDeleted = 0 
				'
	 EXEC(@SQL)
END TRY

BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Organization_Get_GetAllOrganization: ' + error_message()
		SET @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=1'

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Organization_Get_GetAllOrganization', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Get_GetAllOrganizationForDropDown]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Get_GetAllOrganizationForDropDown]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
			     O.[Id]
			    ,O.[OrganizationName]
			 --   ,O.[OrganizationCode]
			 --   ,O.[OrderNo]
			    ,O.[ParentId]
			 --,O.[Status]
			 --   ,O.[OrganizationType]
			 --   ,O.[Email]
			 --   ,O.[Phone]
			 --,O.[Branch]
			 --   ,O.[CurrencyTypeID]
			 --   ,O.[CreatedBy]
			 --   ,O.[CreatedDate]
			 --   ,O.[UpdatedBy]
			 --   ,O.[UpdateDate]
			    ,O.[IsDeleted]'
	  set @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Organization] O '
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE O.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		 ' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 
		  exec(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(o.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE O.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL 
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Organization_GetAllOrganizationForDropDown: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Organization_GetAllOrganizationForDropDown', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Get_GetOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Get_GetOrganization]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
			     O.[Id]
			    ,O.[OrganizationName]
			    ,O.[OrganizationCode]
			    ,O.[OrderNo]
			    ,O.[ParentId]
				,O.[Status]
			    ,O.[OrganizationType]
			    ,O.[Email]
			    ,O.[Phone]
				,O.[Branch]
			    ,O.[CurrencyTypeID]
			    ,O.[CreatedBy]
			    ,O.[CreatedDate]
			    ,O.[UpdatedBy]
			    ,O.[UpdateDate]
			    ,O.[IsDeleted]'
	  set @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Organization] O '
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE O.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		 ' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 
		  exec(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(o.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE O.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL 
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Organization', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
