CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Organization_Get_GetOrganizationById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	--BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX),		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX)
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		
		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT * FROM  [dbo].[Data_Organization] 
			WHERE Id = @Id ' 
	SET @Params = '@Id BIGINT'
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @Id
	--END TRY

	--BEGIN CATCH
	--	DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
	--			@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
	--			@SessionId				INT,
	--			@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

	--	SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
	--	SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Organization_Get_GetOrganizationById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
	--	SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
	--	SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
	--	EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Organization_Get_GetOrganizationById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	--END CATCH




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Get_GetParentOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Get_GetParentOrganization]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@Id		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
	  SET @SQL= N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		
			;WITH ace(Id, OrganizationName, ParentId, OrganizationType) AS (
				SELECT o.Id, OrganizationName, o.ParentId, o.OrganizationType AS Type FROM dbo.Data_Organization o 
				WHERE o.Id= '+CAST(@Id AS NVARCHAR(20))+' AND o.IsDeleted = 0
				UNION ALL
				SELECT o1.Id, o1.OrganizationName,o1.ParentId, o1.OrganizationType FROM ace a,dbo.Data_Organization o1
				WHERE a.ParentId = o1.Id AND o1.IsDeleted = 0
			)
			SELECT * FROM ace
			'
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Organization_Get_GetOrganizationByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Organization_Get_GetOrganizationByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Get_SearchOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Get_SearchOrganization]
	@LanguageId					BIGINT,
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				DECLARE @data TABLE(
					id BIGINT
				)
				INSERT INTO @data (id) 
				SELECT O.Id
				FROM dbo.Data_Organization O
				INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = O.Id
				WHERE L.DataType = ''Organization'' AND L.PropertyName = ''OrganizationName'' AND L.LanguageId = 1 AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')

				;WITH Organization AS(
					SELECT O.*
					FROM dbo.Data_Organization O
					WHERE O.Id in (SELECT Id FROM @data)
					UNION ALL
					SELECT O.*
					FROM dbo.Data_Organization O,Organization
					WHERE Organization.Id=O.ParentId)


					SELECT DISTINCT  * FROM Organization
				'
	SET @params = '@SearchKey NVARCHAR(MAX), @LanguageId BIGINT'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @SearchKey, @LanguageId
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Update_Merger]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Update_Merger]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@ListData ListDataSelectedId READONLY,
	@ToOrganizationaID BIGINT
	,@DecisionNo nvarchar(50)
    ,@WorkingStatus bigint
    ,@DecisionDate datetime
    ,@StartDate datetime
    ,@EndDate datetime
	,@Note nvarchar(max) 
	,@OrganizationName	NVARCHAR(500),
    @OrganizationCode	NVARCHAR(500),
    @OrderNo			BIGINT,
    @ParentId			BIGINT,
	@Status				BIGINT,
    @OrganizationType	BIGINT,	
    @Email				NVARCHAR(500),	
    @Phone				NVARCHAR(500),	
    @Branch				BIGINT,
    @CurrencyTypeId		BIGINT,
	@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
AS

		
		DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	,@CreatedBy bigint
		select @CreatedBy=UserId from @BaseParam
		
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
					
					if (@ToOrganizationaID>0)
					begin
						DECLARE @Count BIGINT
						SELECT @Count=COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Organization WHERE OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode AND Id<>@ToOrganizationaID
						IF(@Count>0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Organization WHERE Id=@ToOrganizationaID
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							
							UPDATE dbo.Data_Organization 
								SET 
									OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode,
									OrderNo=@OrderNo,
									ParentId=@ParentId,
									Status=@Status,
									OrganizationType=OrganizationType,
									Branch=@Branch,
									CurrencyTypeID=@CurrencyTypeId
							WHERE Id=@ToOrganizationaID

							UPDATE dbo.Data_Organization 
								SET IsDeleted=1
							WHERE Id in (select id from @ListData WHERE id<>@ToOrganizationaID)  

							UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET 
								Note=@Note,
								EndDate=dateadd(day,-1,GETDATE()) 
								WHERE OrganizationId in (select id from @ListData WHERE id<>@ToOrganizationaID)  AND EndDate IS NULL

							INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess]
							   ([StaffId]
							   ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]
							   ,[DecisionNo]
							   ,[WorkingStatus]
							   ,[DecisionDate]
							   ,[StartDate]
							   ,[EndDate]
							   ,[ContractId]
							   ,[OrganizationId]
							   ,[OfficeId]
							   ,[PositionId]
							   ,[ClassificationId]
							   ,[StaffLevelId]
							   ,[ManagerId]
							   ,[HRManagerId]
							   ,[PolicyId]
							   ,[CurrencyId]
							   ,[BasicPay]
							   ,[EfficiencyBonus]
							   ,[PaymentForm]
							   ,[PaymentMethod]
							   ,[SalaryNote]
							   ,[Description]
							   ,[Note]
							   ,[IsDeleted]
							   ,[Status]
							   ,[ShiftId]
							   ,[CreatedDate]
							   ,[CreatedBy])
						select 
								p.StaffId,
								p.[WorkingprocessTypeId]
								,@DecisionNo
								,@WorkingStatus
								,@DecisionDate
								,@StartDate
								,@EndDate
								,p.[ContractId]
								,@ToOrganizationaID
								,p.[OfficeId]
								,p.[PositionId]
								,p.[ClassificationId]
								,p.[StaffLevelId]
								,p.[ManagerId]
								,p.[HRManagerId]
								,p.[PolicyId]
								,p.[CurrencyId]
								,p.[BasicPay]
								,p.[EfficiencyBonus]
								,p.[PaymentForm]
								,p.[PaymentMethod]
								,p.[SalaryNote]
								,p.[Description]
								,@Note
								,0
								,p.[Status]
								,p.[ShiftId] 
								,getdate()
								,@CreatedBy
								 from Data_Staff_Information a 
								inner join Data_Staff_WorkingProcess p on a.CurrentWorkingProcessId=p.Id 
								inner join @ListData d on p.OrganizationId=d.id

								UPDATE Data_Staff_Information 
									SET CurrentWorkingProcessId = c.id 
								from Data_Staff_Information a 
								inner join Data_Staff_WorkingProcess p on a.CurrentWorkingProcessId=p.Id 
								inner join @ListData d on p.OrganizationId=d.id AND d.Id<>@ToOrganizationaID
								outer apply (select top 1 * 
											from Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
											where w.staffid=a.Id order by StartDate desc  ) c

								

						END
						
					end
					else
					begin
						DECLARE  @Id BIGINT
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Organization
									( OrganizationName ,
									  OrganizationCode ,
									  ParentId ,
									  OrganizationType ,
									  CurrencyTypeID ,
									  CreatedBy ,
									  CreatedDate,
									  IsDeleted,
									  Branch,
									  Status
										)
										select 
										 @OrganizationName , 
										  @OrganizationCode ,
										  @ParentId , 
										  @OrganizationType ,
										  @CurrencyTypeID , 
										  @CreatedBy ,
										  GETDATE() , 
										  0, 
										  @Branch,
										  @Status
										from @BaseParam
								
								SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

						 INSERT INTO dbo.Data_LocalizedData
									 ( DataId ,
									   DataType ,
									   LanguageId ,
									   PropertyName ,
									   PropertyValue ,
									   IsDefault ,
									   CreatedBy ,
									   CreatedDate ,
									   UpdatedBy ,
									   UpdatedDate ,
									   IsDeleted
									 )
							 VALUES  ( @Id , -- DataId - bigint
									   ''Organization'' , -- DataType - nvarchar(max)
									   1 , -- LanguageId - bigint
									   ''OrganizationName'' , -- PropertyName - nvarchar(max)
									   @OrganizationName , -- PropertyValue - nvarchar(500)
									   1 , -- IsDefault - bit
									   @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - bigint
									   GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime       
									   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
									 )

					UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET 
								Note=@Note,
								EndDate=dateadd(day,-1,GETDATE()) 
								WHERE 
					OrganizationId in (select id from @ListData)  AND EndDate IS NULL

								
					INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess]
							   ([StaffId]
							   ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]
							   ,[DecisionNo]
							   ,[WorkingStatus]
							   ,[DecisionDate]
							   ,[StartDate]
							   ,[EndDate]
							   ,[ContractId]
							   ,[OrganizationId]
							   ,[OfficeId]
							   ,[PositionId]
							   ,[ClassificationId]
							   ,[StaffLevelId]
							   ,[ManagerId]
							   ,[HRManagerId]
							   ,[PolicyId]
							   ,[CurrencyId]
							   ,[BasicPay]
							   ,[EfficiencyBonus]
							   ,[PaymentForm]
							   ,[PaymentMethod]
							   ,[SalaryNote]
							   ,[Description]
							   ,[Note]
							   ,[IsDeleted]
							   ,[Status]
							   ,[ShiftId]
							   ,[CreatedDate]
							   ,[CreatedBy])
						select 
								p.StaffId,
								p.[WorkingprocessTypeId]
								,@DecisionNo
								,@WorkingStatus
								,@DecisionDate
								,@StartDate
								,@EndDate
								,p.[ContractId]
								,@Id
								,p.[OfficeId]
								,p.[PositionId]
								,p.[ClassificationId]
								,p.[StaffLevelId]
								,p.[ManagerId]
								,p.[HRManagerId]
								,p.[PolicyId]
								,p.[CurrencyId]
								,p.[BasicPay]
								,p.[EfficiencyBonus]
								,p.[PaymentForm]
								,p.[PaymentMethod]
								,p.[SalaryNote]
								,p.[Description]
								,@Note
								,0
								,p.[Status]
								,p.[ShiftId] 
								,getdate()
								,@CreatedBy
								 from Data_Staff_Information a 
								inner join Data_Staff_WorkingProcess p on a.CurrentWorkingProcessId=p.Id 
								inner join @ListData d on p.OrganizationId=d.id

								UPDATE Data_Staff_Information 
									SET CurrentWorkingProcessId = c.id 
								from Data_Staff_Information a 
								inner join Data_Staff_WorkingProcess p on a.CurrentWorkingProcessId=p.Id 
								inner join @ListData d on p.OrganizationId=d.id
								outer apply (select top 1 * 
											from Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
											where w.staffid=a.Id order by StartDate desc  ) c
					end
					 										
				'
		SET @params = '@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,@ListData ListDataSelectedId READONLY,@ToOrganizationaID BIGINT,@DecisionNo nvarchar(50),@WorkingStatus bigint,@DecisionDate datetime,
		  @StartDate datetime,@EndDate datetime,@Note nvarchar(max),@OrganizationName NVARCHAR(500),@OrganizationCode NVARCHAR(500),@OrderNo BIGINT
		  ,@ParentId BIGINT,@Status	BIGINT,@OrganizationType BIGINT,@Email NVARCHAR(500),@Phone	NVARCHAR(500),@Branch BIGINT,@CurrencyTypeId BIGINT,@CreatedBy bigint
		  '
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@BaseParam,@ListData,@ToOrganizationaID,@DecisionNo,@WorkingStatus,@DecisionDate,@StartDate,@EndDate,@Note,
		@OrganizationName,@OrganizationCode,@OrderNo,@ParentId,@Status,@OrganizationType,@Email,@Phone,@Branch,@CurrencyTypeId,@CreatedBy
    
	--end try
	

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'Organization_Update_Merger: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@ToOrganizationaID=' + @ToOrganizationaID

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProOrganization_Update_Merger', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	--end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Update_SaveMergerOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Update_SaveMergerOrganization]
	  @Id BIGINT,
	  @OrganizationCode NVARCHAR(500),
	  @OrganizationName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @ParentId BIGINT,
	  @OrganizationType BIGINT,
	  @Status BIGINT,
	  @Branch BIGINT,
	  @CurrencyTypeID BIGINT,
	  @Note NVARCHAR(500),
	  @CreatedBy BIGINT,
	  @UpdatedBy BIGINT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @UserId BIGINT,
	  @RoleId BIGINT,
	  @LanguageId NVARCHAR(500),
	  @listOrganizationId NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
		DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	 
		
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
					
					DECLARE @Count INT				
					SELECT @Count=COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Organization WHERE OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode and Id<>@Id
					IF(@Count>0)
					BEGIN
						SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Organization WHERE OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode and Id<>@Id
					END
					ELSE
					BEGIN
						IF(@Id<>0)
						BEGIN							
							UPDATE dbo.Data_Organization SET IsDeleted=1,UpdatedBy=@UpdatedBy,UpdateDate=GETDATE() 
							WHERE '','' + @listOrganizationId + '','' LIKE ''%,'' + CAST(Id AS NVARCHAR) + '',%''

							UPDATE dbo.Data_Organization SET OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode
														,[Status]=@Status
														,ParentId=@ParentId
														,CurrencyTypeID=@CurrencyTypeID
														,OrganizationType=@OrganizationType
														,Branch=@Branch
														,UpdatedBy=@UpdatedBy
														,UpdateDate=GETDATE()
														WHERE Id= @Id

							UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET OrganizationId=@Id,Note=@Note WHERE '','' + @listOrganizationId + '','' LIKE ''%,'' + CAST(OrganizationId AS NVARCHAR) + '',%'' AND EndDate IS NULL AND StartDate IS NOT NULL	
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							UPDATE dbo.Data_Organization SET IsDeleted=1,UpdatedBy=@UpdatedBy,UpdateDate=GETDATE() 
							WHERE '','' + @listOrganizationId + '','' LIKE ''%,'' + CAST(Id AS NVARCHAR) + '',%''
							
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Organization
								( OrganizationName ,
								  OrganizationCode ,
								  ParentId ,
								  OrganizationType ,
								  CurrencyTypeID ,
								  CreatedBy ,
								  CreatedDate,
								  IsDeleted,
								  Branch,
								  Status
									)
							VALUES  ( @OrganizationName , -- OrganizationName - nvarchar(max)
									  @OrganizationCode , -- OrganizationCode - nvarchar(max)
									  @ParentId , -- ParentId - bigint
									  @OrganizationType , -- OrganizationType - bigint
									  @CurrencyTypeID , -- CurrencyTypeId - bigint
									  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - bigint
									  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
									  0,  -- IsDeleted - bit
									  @Branch,
									  @Status
									)
							SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()
						
							

							DECLARE @TableData TABLE(
									  Id BIGINT,
									  StaffId BIGINT,
									  WorkingprocessTypeId BIGINT,
									  DecisionNo nvarchar(50),
									  WorkingStatus BIGINT,
									  DecisionDate DATETIME,
									  StartDate DATETIME,
									  EndDate DATETIME,
									  ContractId BIGINT,
									  OrganizationId BIGINT,
									  OfficeId BIGINT,
									  PositionId BIGINT,
									  ClassificationId BIGINT,
									  StaffLevelId BIGINT,
									  ManagerId BIGINT,
									  PolicyId BIGINT,
									  CurrencyId BIGINT,
									  BasicPay DECIMAL,
									  EfficiencyBonus DECIMAL,
									  Note nvarchar(max),
									  IsDeleted BIT
							)

							INSERT INTO @TableData
									( StaffId ,
									  WorkingprocessTypeId ,
									  DecisionNo ,
									  WorkingStatus ,
									  DecisionDate ,
									  StartDate ,
									  EndDate ,
									  ContractId ,
									  OrganizationId ,
									  OfficeId ,
									  PositionId ,
									  ClassificationId ,
									  StaffLevelId ,
									  ManagerId ,
									  PolicyId ,
									  CurrencyId ,
									  BasicPay ,
									  EfficiencyBonus ,
									  Note ,
									  IsDeleted
									)
							SELECT   DSW.StaffId, -- StaffId - int
									  DSW.WorkingprocessTypeId , -- WorkingprocessTypeId - int
									  DSW.DecisionNo , -- DecisionNo - nvarchar(50)
									  DSW.WorkingStatus , -- WorkingStatus - int
									  GETDATE() , -- DecisionDate - datetime
									  GETDATE() , -- StartDate - datetime
									  NULL , -- EndDate - datetime
									  DSW.ContractId , -- ContractId - nvarchar(50)
									  DSW.OrganizationId , -- OrganizationId - int
									  DSW.OfficeId , -- OfficeId - int
									  DSW.PositionId , -- PositionId - int
									  DSW.ClassificationId , -- ClassificationId - int
									  DSW.StaffLevelId , -- StaffLevelId - int
									  DSW.ManagerId , -- ManagerId - int
									  DSW.PolicyId , -- PolicyId - int
									  DSW.CurrencyId , -- CurrencyId - int
									  DSW.BasicPay , -- BasicPay - decimal
									  DSW.EfficiencyBonus , -- EfficiencyBonus - decimal
									  DSW.Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									  DSW.IsDeleted  -- IsDeleted - bit
							FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW WHERE '','' + @listOrganizationId + '','' LIKE ''%,'' + CAST(OrganizationId AS NVARCHAR) + '',%'' AND EndDate IS NULL 

							UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET Note=@Note,EndDate=GETDATE() WHERE '','' + @listOrganizationId + '','' LIKE ''%,'' + CAST(OrganizationId AS NVARCHAR) + '',%'' AND EndDate IS NULL	

							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess
									( StaffId ,
									  WorkingprocessTypeId ,
									  DecisionNo ,
									  WorkingStatus ,
									  DecisionDate ,
									  StartDate ,
									  EndDate ,
									  ContractId ,
									  OrganizationId ,
									  OfficeId ,
									  PositionId ,
									  ClassificationId ,
									  StaffLevelId ,
									  ManagerId ,
									  PolicyId ,
									  CurrencyId ,
									  BasicPay ,
									  EfficiencyBonus ,
									  Note ,
									  IsDeleted
									)
							SELECT    TD.StaffId , -- StaffId - int
									  TD.WorkingprocessTypeId , -- WorkingprocessTypeId - int
									  TD.DecisionNo , -- DecisionNo - nvarchar(50)
									  TD.WorkingStatus , -- WorkingStatus - int
									  NULL , -- DecisionDate - datetime
									  GETDATE() , -- StartDate - datetime
									  NULL , -- EndDate - datetime
									  TD.ContractId , -- ContractId - nvarchar(50)
									  @Id , -- OrganizationId - int
									  TD.OfficeId , -- OfficeId - int
									  TD.PositionId , -- PositionId - int
									  TD.ClassificationId , -- ClassificationId - int
									  TD.StaffLevelId , -- StaffLevelId - int
									  TD.ManagerId , -- ManagerId - int
									  TD.PolicyId , -- PolicyId - int
									  TD.CurrencyId , -- CurrencyId - int
									  TD.BasicPay , -- BasicPay - decimal
									  TD.EfficiencyBonus , -- EfficiencyBonus - decimal
									  @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									  0  -- IsDeleted - bit  
							FROM @TableData TD
												
						END						
					END													
				'
		SET @params = '@listOrganizationId NVARCHAR(500),@OrganizationCode NVARCHAR(500),@Status BIGINT,@ParentId BIGINT,@CurrencyTypeID BIGINT,@OrganizationType BIGINT,@Branch BIGINT,@Id BIGINT,@Note NVARCHAR(500),@CreatedBy BIGINT,@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@OrganizationName NVARCHAR(500)'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@listOrganizationId,@OrganizationCode,@Status,@ParentId,@CurrencyTypeID,@OrganizationType,@Branch,@Id,@Note,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@OrganizationName
     
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Organization_Update_SaveOrganization]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Update_SaveOrganization]
	@Id					BIGINT,
    @OrganizationName	NVARCHAR(500),
    @OrganizationCode	NVARCHAR(500),
    @OrderNo			BIGINT,
    @ParentId			BIGINT,
	@Status				BIGINT,
    @OrganizationType	BIGINT,	
    @Email				NVARCHAR(500),	
    @Phone				NVARCHAR(500),	
    @Branch				BIGINT,
    @CurrencyTypeId		BIGINT,
    @CreatedBy			BIGINT,
    @UpdatedBy			BIGINT,
	@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 
	
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						DECLARE @Count INT
					
						SELECT @Count=COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Organization WHERE OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode
						IF(@Count>0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Organization WHERE OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							IF(@Id=0)
							BEGIN
								INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Organization
									( OrganizationName ,
									  OrganizationCode ,
									  OrderNo ,
									  ParentId ,
									  OrganizationType ,
									  Email ,
									  Phone ,
									  CurrencyTypeID ,
									  CreatedBy ,
									  CreatedDate ,
									  UpdatedBy ,
									  UpdateDate ,
									  IsDeleted,
									  Branch,
									  Status
									)
							VALUES  ( @OrganizationName , -- OrganizationName - nvarchar(max)
									  @OrganizationCode , -- OrganizationCode - nvarchar(max)
									  @OrderNo , -- OrderNo - int
									  @ParentId , -- ParentId - bigint
									  @OrganizationType , -- OrganizationType - bigint
									  @Email , -- Email - nvarchar(128)
									  @Phone, -- Phone - nvarchar(50)
									  @CurrencyTypeId , -- CurrencyTypeId - bigint
									  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - bigint
									  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
									  @UpdatedBy , -- UpdatedBy - bigint
									  GETDATE() , -- UpdateDate - datetime
									  0,  -- IsDeleted - bit
									  @Branch,
									  @Status
									)
								END

								SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

								 INSERT INTO dbo.Data_LocalizedData
									 ( DataId ,
									   DataType ,
									   LanguageId ,
									   PropertyName ,
									   PropertyValue ,
									   IsDefault ,
									   CreatedBy ,
									   CreatedDate ,
									   UpdatedBy ,
									   UpdatedDate ,
									   IsDeleted
									 )
							 VALUES  ( @Id , -- DataId - bigint
									   ''Organization'' , -- DataType - nvarchar(max)
									   1 , -- LanguageId - bigint
									   ''OrganizationName'' , -- PropertyName - nvarchar(max)
									   @OrganizationName , -- PropertyValue - nvarchar(500)
									   1 , -- IsDefault - bit
									   @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - bigint
									   GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime       
									   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
									 )
							ELSE
							BEGIN
								UPDATE dbo.Data_Organization 
													SET	OrganizationName=@OrganizationName
														,OrganizationCode=@OrganizationCode
														,ParentId=@ParentId
														,OrganizationType=@OrganizationType
														,Branch=@Branch
														,Status=@Status
														,CurrencyTypeId=@CurrencyTypeId
														,UpdatedBy = @UpdatedBy
														,UpdateDate=GETDATE()
								WHERE Id=@Id 

								UPDATE dbo.Data_LocalizedData
									SET PropertyValue=@OrganizationName
								WHERE DataId=@Id AND  DataType=''Organization'' AND LanguageId=1
							END							
						END						
					'
		SET @params = '@OrganizationName NVARCHAR(500),@OrganizationCode NVARCHAR(500),@OrderNo BIGINT, @ParentId BIGINT,
		@OrganizationType BIGINT,@Email NVARCHAR(500), @Phone NVARCHAR(500),@Branch BIGINT,@CurrencyTypeId BIGINT,@CreatedBy BIGINT,
		@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@DbName NVARCHAR(500),@Status BIGINT,@Id BIGINT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@OrganizationName,@OrganizationCode,@OrderNo,@ParentId,@OrganizationType,@Email,
		@Phone,@Branch,@CurrencyTypeId,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@DbName,@Status,@Id
	
END
GO

GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Organization_Update_SavePersonnelTransfer]
	  @StaffId BIGINT,
	  @OrganizationId BIGINT,
	  @Note NVARCHAR(500),
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN

	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	 
		BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET EndDate=GETDATE() WHERE EndDate IS NULL and StaffId=@StaffId
				
				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess
						( StaffId ,
						  WorkingprocessTypeId ,
						  DecisionNo ,
						  WorkingStatus ,
						  DecisionDate ,
						  StartDate ,
						  EndDate ,
						  ContractId ,
						  OrganizationId ,
						  OfficeId ,
						  PositionId ,
						  ClassificationId ,
						  StaffLevelId ,
						  ManagerId ,
						  PolicyId ,
						  CurrencyId ,
						  BasicPay ,
						  EfficiencyBonus ,
						  Note ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
				VALUES  ( @StaffId, -- StaffId - int
						  NULL , -- WorkingprocessTypeId - int
						  NULL , -- DecisionNo - nvarchar(50)
						  1 , -- WorkingStatus - int
						  NULL , -- DecisionDate - datetime
						  GETDATE() , -- StartDate - datetime
						  NULL , -- EndDate - datetime
						  NULL , -- ContractId - nvarchar(50)
						  @OrganizationId , -- OrganizationId - int
						  NULL , -- OfficeId - int
						  NULL , -- PositionId - int
						  NULL , -- ClassificationId - int
						  NULL , -- StaffLevelId - int
						  NULL , -- ManagerId - int
						  NULL , -- PolicyId - int
						  NULL , -- CurrencyId - int
						  NULL , -- BasicPay - decimal
						  NULL , -- EfficiencyBonus - decimal
						  @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
						  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						)		
				'
		SET @params = '@StaffId BIGINT,@OrganizationId BIGINT,@Note NVARCHAR(500)'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId,@OrganizationId,@Note
    END 

	
END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Permission_Del_DeletePermissionByDataId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Permission_Del_DeletePermissionByDataId]
	@DataId						BIGINT,
	@DataTypeName				NVARCHAR(500),
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						DECLARE @DataTypeId BIGINT =(SELECT Id FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE Name=@DataTypeName)
						DELETE FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission where DataId=@DataId and DataTypeId= @DataTypeId		
						IF(@DataTypeName=''Role'')
						BEGIN
							DELETE FROM dbo.Data_Role WHERE Id=@DataId
						END			
					'
	SET @params = '@DataId BIGINT,@DataTypeName NVARCHAR(500)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@DataId,@DataTypeName

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Permission_Get_GetPermissionByRoleId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Permission_Get_GetPermissionByRoleId]
	@RoleId			BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
							SELECT SM.id as MenuId
									,DP.id as PermissionId
									,DMP.id,DMP.IsDeleted 							
									,SM.MenuName
									,DP.PermissionName
									,IIF(DSRP.Id IS NULL,0,1) AS IsCheck
									,SM.ParentId AS MenuParentId								
							FROM System_Menu SM							
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Menu_Permission DMP ON DMP.MenuId=SM.Id
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Permission DP ON DP.Id=DMP.PermissionId							
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission DSRP ON DSRP.MenuPermissionId=DMP.Id AND DSRP.IsDeleted=0  AND DSRP.DataId=@RoleId AND DSRP.DataTypeId=270
							WHERE SM.IsDeleted=0						
					'

	SET @params = '@RoleId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@RoleId

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Permission_Get_GetPermissionByStaffId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Permission_Get_GetPermissionByStaffId]
	@StaffId			BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM Data_Staff_Role_Permission WHERE DataId=@StaffId AND DataTypeId=269)>0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT SM.id as MenuId
									,DP.id as PermissionId
									,DMP.id,DMP.IsDeleted 							
									,SM.MenuName
									,DP.PermissionName
									,IIF(DSRP.Id IS NULL,0,1) AS IsCheck
									,SM.ParentId AS MenuParentId								
							FROM System_Menu SM							
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Menu_Permission DMP ON DMP.MenuId=SM.Id
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Permission DP ON DP.Id=DMP.PermissionId							
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission DSRP ON DSRP.MenuPermissionId=DMP.Id AND DSRP.IsDeleted=0  AND DSRP.DataId=@StaffId AND DSRP.DataTypeId=269
							WHERE SM.IsDeleted=0	
						END	
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_StaffRole WHERE StaffId=@StaffId)>0)
							BEGIN
								DECLARE @RoleId BIGINT=(SELECT TOP 1 IIF(RoleId=NULL,0,RoleId) FROM dbo.Data_StaffRole WHERE StaffId=@StaffId)
								IF(@RoleId<>0)
									SELECT SM.id as MenuId
											,DP.id as PermissionId
											,DMP.id,DMP.IsDeleted 							
											,SM.MenuName
											,DP.PermissionName
											,IIF(DSRP.Id IS NULL,0,1) AS IsCheck
											,SM.ParentId AS MenuParentId								
									FROM System_Menu SM							
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Menu_Permission DMP ON DMP.MenuId=SM.Id
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Permission DP ON DP.Id=DMP.PermissionId							
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission DSRP ON DSRP.MenuPermissionId=DMP.Id AND DSRP.IsDeleted=0  AND DSRP.DataId=@RoleId AND DSRP.DataTypeId=270
									WHERE SM.IsDeleted=0
								
							END
							ELSE
								BEGIN
									SELECT SM.id as MenuId
										,DP.id as PermissionId
										,DMP.id,DMP.IsDeleted 							
										,SM.MenuName
										,DP.PermissionName
										,IIF(DSRP.Id IS NULL,0,1) AS IsCheck
										,SM.ParentId AS MenuParentId								
										FROM System_Menu SM							
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Menu_Permission DMP ON DMP.MenuId=SM.Id
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Permission DP ON DP.Id=DMP.PermissionId							
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission DSRP ON DSRP.MenuPermissionId=DMP.Id AND DSRP.IsDeleted=0  AND DSRP.DataId=@StaffId AND DSRP.DataTypeId=269
									WHERE SM.IsDeleted=0
								END	
						END
																
					'
	SET @params = '@StaffId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Permission_Update_SavePermission]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Permission_Update_SavePermission]
	  @DataId BIGINT,
      @DataTypeName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @Name NVARCHAR(500),
	  @Description NVARCHAR(500),
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @MenuPermission MenuPermissionType READONLY
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	
							 
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

				DECLARE @DataTypeId BIGINT=(SELECT Id FROM System_MasterData WHERE Name=@DataTypeName)
				IF(@DataId<>0)
				BEGIN					
					IF((SELECT COUNT(DataId) FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission WHERE DataId=@DataId and DataTypeId=@DataTypeId) >0)
					BEGIN
						DELETE FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission WHERE DataId=@DataId and DataTypeId=@DataTypeId
					END	
					INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission
						( DataId ,
						  DataTypeId ,
						  MenuPermissionId ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
					SELECT    @DataId, -- DataId - bigint
							  @DataTypeId, -- DataTypeId - bigint
							  MP.PermissionId , -- MenuPermissionId - bigint
							  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
					FROM @MenuPermission MP	
					
					IF(@DataTypeName=''Role'')
					BEGIN
						UPDATE dbo.Data_Role
								SET Name=@Name,
									Description=@Description
						WHERE Id=@DataId
					END	
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					IF(@DataTypeName=''Role'')
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Role
								( Name, Description, IsDeleted )
						VALUES  ( @Name, -- Name - nvarchar(1000)
								  @Description, -- Description - nvarchar(max)
								  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								  )
						SET @DataId=SCOPE_IDENTITY()
					END	

					INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission
						( DataId ,
						  DataTypeId ,
						  MenuPermissionId ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
					SELECT    @DataId, -- DataId - bigint
							  @DataTypeId, -- DataTypeId - bigint
							  MP.PermissionId , -- MenuPermissionId - bigint
							  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
					FROM @MenuPermission MP
				END														
			'
		SET @params ='@DataId BIGINT,@DataTypeName NVARCHAR(500), @Name NVARCHAR(500),@Description NVARCHAR(500),@MenuPermission MenuPermissionType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@DataId,@DataTypeName,@Name,@Description,@MenuPermission
	
END
GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipeline]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipeline]
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT DP.Id,
								DP.Name,
								DP.Description,
								DP.MenuId,
								DPS.PositionId,
								DPM.PipelineStepId,
								DPS.PipelineName as PipelineStepName
						FROM dbo.Data_Pipeline DP
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id=DP.MenuId
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineId = DP.Id 
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS ON DPS.Id = DPM.PipelineStepId and DPS.IsDeleted=0
						LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMD ON SMD.Id = DPS.PositionId
						WHERE DP.IsDeleted=0
						ORDER BY SMD.OrderNo, DPS.OrderNo
					'
	SET @params = ''
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params

END

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineByMenuName]
	@MenuName			NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
				USE [Hrm_system]			
			SELECT  
				DP.Id,
				DP.Name
			FROM dbo.Data_Pipeline DP
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DP.MenuId AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1
			WHERE SM.MenuName = @MenuName AND DP.IsDefault = 1
		'

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineStepByMenuName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineStepByMenuName]
	@MenuName			NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@StaffId			BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
			SELECT  
				DPS.Id,
				DPS.PipelineName AS PipelineStepName, 
				DPS.PositionId,
				DPS.PipelineSymbol AS PipelineStepSymbol,
				DPS.PipelineRule,
				DP.Id AS PipelineId,
				SMD.Name AS PositionName
			FROM dbo.Data_Pipeline DP
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineId = DP.Id
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS ON DPS.Id = DPM.PipelineStepId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMD ON SMD.Id = DPS.PositionId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DP.MenuId AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1
			WHERE SM.MenuName = @MenuName AND DP.IsDefault=1
			ORDER BY SMD.OrderNo, DPS.OrderNo
			--ORDER BY ISNULL(DSP.Date,''2099-01-01'') ASC
		'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@MenuName NVARCHAR(MAX), @StaffId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @MenuName, @StaffId

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineStepByPipelineId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineStepByPipelineId]
	@PipelineId			BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
			SELECT  
				DPS.Id,
				DPS.PipelineName AS PipelineStepName, 
				DPS.PositionId,
				DPS.PipelineSymbol AS PipelineStepSymbol,
				DP.Id AS PipelineId,
				SMD.Name as PositionName,
				DPS.PipelineRule
			FROM dbo.Data_Pipeline DP
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineId = DP.Id
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS ON DPS.Id = DPM.PipelineStepId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMD ON SMD.Id = DPS.PositionId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DP.MenuId
			WHERE DP.Id=@PipelineId and DPS.IsDeleted=0
			ORDER BY SMD.OrderNo, DPS.OrderNo
		'
	SET @params = '@PipelineId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @PipelineId

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineStepByStaffId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Pipeline_Get_GetPipelineStepByStaffId]
	@PipelineId			BIGINT,
	@StaffId			BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'		
			IF(@PipelineId<>0)
			BEGIN
					SELECT DPS.Id,
							DPS.PipelineName AS PipelineStepName, 
							DPS.PositionId,
							DPS.PipelineSymbol AS PipelineStepSymbol,
							DPS.PipelineRule,
							DP.Id AS PipelineId,						
							DSP.Date AS PipelineDate,
							DSP.Id AS PipelineStaffStatusId ,
							DPS.OrderNo
					FROM dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS
					INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineStepId = DPS.Id
					INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Pipeline DP ON DPM.PipelineId = DP.Id
					LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus DSP ON DSP.PipelineStepId=DPS.Id AND DSP.StaffId=@StaffId 
					WHERE DPM.PipelineId=@PipelineId 
					ORDER BY DPS.OrderNo
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				SELECT  
						DPS.Id,
						DPS.PipelineName AS PipelineStepName, 
						DPS.PositionId,
						DPS.PipelineSymbol AS PipelineStepSymbol,
						DPS.PipelineRule,
						DP.Id AS PipelineId,
						SMD.Name AS PositionName,
						DSP.Date AS PipelineDate,
						DSP.Id AS PipelineStaffStatusId,
						DPS.OrderNo
					FROM dbo.Data_Pipeline DP
					INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineId = DP.Id
					INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS ON DPS.Id = DPM.PipelineStepId
					INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMD ON SMD.Id = DPS.PositionId
					INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DP.MenuId AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1
					LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus DSP ON DSP.PipelineStepId = DPS.Id AND DSP.StaffId = @StaffId 
					WHERE DP.IsDefault=1
					ORDER BY DPS.OrderNo
			END	
		'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@PipelineId BIGINT,@StaffId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@PipelineId, @StaffId

END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Pipeline_Update_SavePipeline]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Pipeline_Update_SavePipeline]
	  @Id BIGINT,
      @Name NVARCHAR(500),
	  @MenuId BIGINT,
	  @Description NVARCHAR(500),
	  @IsDefault BIT,
	  @CreatedBy BIGINT,
	  @UpdatedBy BIGINT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @PipelineStep PipelineStepType READONLY
AS
 
BEGIN
	SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @PipelineStep WHERE Id=0
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 
	IF(@Id=0)		
	BEGIN

		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				
				IF(@IsDefault=1)
				BEGIN
					UPDATE dbo.Data_Pipeline SET IsDefault=0
				END

				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Pipeline
						( MenuId ,
						  Name ,
						  Description ,
						  IsDefault ,
						  CreatedBy ,
						  CreatedDate ,
						  UpdatedBy ,
						  UpdatedDate ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
				VALUES  ( @MenuId , -- MenuId - bigint
						  @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(max)
						  @Description , -- Description - nvarchar(max)
						  @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
						  @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - int
						  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
						  NULL , -- UpdatedBy - int
						  NULL , -- UpdatedDate - datetime
						  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						)				
				SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

				DECLARE @PipelineStepId BIGINT
				DECLARE @PipelineStepName NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @PositionId BIGINT
				DECLARE @PipelineStepSymbol NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @PipelineRule NVARCHAR(500)
				DECLARE @OrderNo BIGINT


				DECLARE CursorPipeline CURSOR FOR
				SELECT Id,PipelineStepName,PositionId,PipelineStepSymbol,PipelineRule,OrderNo FROM @PipelineStep

				OPEN CursorPipeline

				FETCH NEXT FROM CursorPipeline
					INTO @PipelineStepId,@PipelineStepName,@PositionId,@PipelineStepSymbol,@PipelineRule,@OrderNo

				WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
					BEGIN					
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_PipelineStep
							( PositionId,
							  PipelineName,
							  PipelineSymbol,
							  PipelineRule,
							  Description,
							  OrderNo,
							  IsDefault,
							  CreatedBy,
							  CreatedDate,
							  IsDeleted
							)
						VALUES  ( @PositionId, -- PositionId - int
								  @PipelineStepName, -- PipelineName - nvarchar(1000)
								  @PipelineStepSymbol, -- PipelineSymbol - nvarchar(50)
								  @PipelineRule, -- PipelineRule - nvarchar(100)
								  NULL, -- Description - nvarchar(max)
								  @OrderNo, -- OrderNo - int
								  0, -- IsDefault - bit
								  @CreatedBy, -- CreatedBy - int
								  GETDATE(), -- CreatedDate - datetime
								  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								)
																									
						SET @PipelineStepId=SCOPE_IDENTITY()	

						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_PipelineMapper
								( PipelineId, PipelineStepId )
						VALUES  ( @Id, -- PipelineId - bigint
								  @PipelineStepId  -- PipelineStepId - bigint
								 )

						FETCH NEXT FROM CursorPipeline
							INTO @PipelineStepId,@PipelineStepName,@PositionId,@PipelineStepSymbol,@PipelineRule,@OrderNo
						
					END
				CLOSE CursorPipeline
				DEALLOCATE CursorPipeline
	
			'

		SET @params ='@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@MenuId BIGINT,@Description NVARCHAR(500),@IsDefault BIT,@CreatedBy BIGINT,@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@PipelineStep PipelineStepType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@Name,@MenuId,@Description,@IsDefault,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@PipelineStep
    END 
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

				IF(@IsDefault=1)
				BEGIN
					UPDATE dbo.Data_Pipeline SET IsDefault=0
				END

				DECLARE @PipelineId BIGINT=(SELECT TOP(1) PipelineId FROM @PipelineStep )

				UPDATE dbo.Data_Pipeline SET 
							 MenuId=@MenuId,
							 Name=@Name,
							 Description=@Description,
							 IsDefault=@IsDefault,
							 UpdatedBy=@UpdatedBy,
							 UpdatedDate=GETDATE()
						WHERE Id=@Id

				UPDATE DPS
						SET DPS.IsDeleted=1
				FROM dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS 
				INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineStepId = DPS.Id
				INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Pipeline DP ON DP.Id=DPM.PipelineId
				WHERE DP.MenuId=@MenuId and DP.Id=@PipelineId

				UPDATE DPS
						SET 
							DPS.PositionId=PST.PositionId,
							DPS.PipelineName=PST.PipelineStepName,
							DPS.PipelineSymbol=PST.PipelineStepSymbol,
							DPS.PipelineRule=PST.PipelineRule,
							DPS.Description=NULL,
							DPS.OrderNo=PST.OrderNo,
							UpdatedBy=@UpdatedBy,
							UpdatedDate=GETDATE(),
							DPS.IsDeleted=0
				FROM dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS 
				INNER JOIN @PipelineStep PST ON PST.Id = DPS.Id

				IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @PipelineStep WHERE Id=0)>0 )
				BEGIN
					
					DECLARE @PipelineStepId BIGINT
					DECLARE @PipelineStepName NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @PositionId BIGINT
					DECLARE @PipelineStepSymbol NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @PipelineRule NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @OrderNo BIGINT

					DECLARE CursorPipeline CURSOR FOR
					SELECT Id,PipelineStepName,PositionId,PipelineStepSymbol,PipelineRule,OrderNo FROM @PipelineStep WHERE Id=0

					OPEN CursorPipeline

					FETCH NEXT FROM CursorPipeline
					INTO @PipelineStepId,@PipelineStepName,@PositionId,@PipelineStepSymbol,@PipelineRule,@OrderNo

					WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
						BEGIN					
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_PipelineStep
								( PositionId,
								  PipelineName,
								  PipelineSymbol,
								  PipelineRule,
								  Description,
								  OrderNo,
								  IsDefault,
								  CreatedBy,
								  CreatedDate,
								  IsDeleted
								)
						VALUES  ( @PositionId, -- PositionId - int
								  @PipelineStepName, -- PipelineName - nvarchar(1000)
								  @PipelineStepSymbol, -- PipelineSymbol - nvarchar(100)
								  @PipelineRule, -- PipelineRule - nvarchar(100)
								  NULL, -- Description - nvarchar(max)
								  @OrderNo, -- OrderNo - int
								  0, -- IsDefault - bit
								  @CreatedBy, -- CreatedBy - int
								  GETDATE(), -- CreatedDate - datetime
								  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								)
																									
							SET @PipelineStepId=SCOPE_IDENTITY()	

							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_PipelineMapper
									( PipelineId, PipelineStepId )
							VALUES  ( @Id, -- PipelineId - bigint
									  @PipelineStepId  -- PipelineStepId - bigint
									 )

							FETCH NEXT FROM CursorPipeline
								INTO @PipelineStepId,@PipelineStepName,@PositionId,@PipelineStepSymbol,@PipelineRule,@OrderNo
						
						END
					CLOSE CursorPipeline
					DEALLOCATE CursorPipeline
				END

			'
		SET @params ='@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@MenuId BIGINT,@Description NVARCHAR(500),@IsDefault BIT,@CreatedBy BIGINT,@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@PipelineStep PipelineStepType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@Name,@MenuId,@Description,@IsDefault,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@PipelineStep
    END 
	
END
GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Role_Get_GetRoleByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Role_Get_GetRoleByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord	INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			SELECT sr.[Id]
				,sr.[RoleId]
				,sr.[StaffId]
				,sr.[Description]
				,sr.[IsDeleted]
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_StaffRole] sr'
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE sr.IsDeleted = 0 and sr.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy --+ 
	  --' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(sr.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE sr.IsDeleted = 0 and sr.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Role_Get_GetRoleByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Role_Get_GetRoleByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Role_Get_SearchRole]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Role_Get_SearchRole]
	@LanguageId					BIGINT,
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						SELECT 
							R.* 
						FROM dbo.Data_Role R
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = R.Id
						WHERE L.DataType = ''Role'' AND ((L.PropertyName = ''Name''  AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')) or (L.PropertyName = ''Description''  AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')) ) and L.LanguageId = @LanguageId	
				'	
	SET @params = '@SearchKey NVARCHAR(MAX), @LanguageId BIGINT'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @SearchKey, @LanguageId
END


GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Bonus_Discipline_Update_Staff_Bonus_Discipline]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Bonus_Discipline_Update_Staff_Bonus_Discipline]
	@StaffId bigint
    ,@TypeId bigint
    ,@GroupId bigint
    ,@DecisionNo nvarchar(max)
    ,@Content nvarchar(max)
    ,@ActionId bigint
    ,@Amount decimal(18,4)
    ,@CurrencyId bigint
    ,@SignDate datetime
    ,@ApplyDate datetime
    ,@Note nvarchar(max)
    ,@CreatedDate datetime
    ,@CreatedBy bigint
    ,@UpdatedBy bigint
    ,@UpdatedDate datetime
    ,@IsDeleted bit
	,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
	,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT
as
 
begin try

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 

		if @Id <= 0
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline]
				   ([StaffId]
				   ,[TypeId]
				   ,[GroupId]
				   ,[DecisionNo]
				   ,[Content]
				   ,[ActionId]
				   ,[Amount]
				   ,[CurrencyId]
				   ,[SignDate]
				   ,[ApplyDate]
				   ,[Note]
				   ,[CreatedDate]
				   ,[CreatedBy] 
				   ,[IsDeleted])
			 VALUES
					(@StaffId
					,@TypeId
					,@GroupId
					,@DecisionNo
					,@Content
					,@ActionId
					,@Amount
					,@CurrencyId
					,@SignDate
					,@ApplyDate
					,@Note
					,getdate()
					,@CreatedBy 
					,@IsDeleted)	

			SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
			 '
		END	 
		else
		begin
		SET  @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				update dbo.Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline
				 set  
						[StaffId]=@StaffId
				   ,[TypeId]	 =@TypeId
				   ,[GroupId]	 =@GroupId
				   ,[DecisionNo] =@DecisionNo
				   ,[Content]	 =@Content
				   ,[ActionId]	 =@ActionId
				   ,[Amount]	 =@Amount
				   ,[CurrencyId] =@CurrencyId
				   ,[SignDate]	 =@SignDate
				   ,[ApplyDate]	 =@ApplyDate
				   ,[Note]		 =@Note
				   ,[CreatedDate]=getdate()
				   ,[CreatedBy]  =@CreatedBy 
				   ,[IsDeleted]	 =@IsDeleted
						 where id=@Id

				'
		end
			PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '@StaffId bigint
						,@TypeId bigint
						,@GroupId bigint
						,@DecisionNo nvarchar(max)
						,@Content nvarchar(max)
						,@ActionId bigint
						,@Amount decimal(184)
						,@CurrencyId bigint
						,@SignDate datetime
						,@ApplyDate datetime
						,@Note nvarchar(max)
						,@CreatedBy bigint
						,@UpdatedBy bigint
						,@IsDeleted bit
						,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
						,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,			          
		   @StaffId
		   ,@TypeId
		   ,@GroupId
		   ,@DecisionNo
		   ,@Content
		   ,@ActionId
		   ,@Amount
		   ,@CurrencyId
		   ,@SignDate
		   ,@ApplyDate
		   ,@Note
		   ,@UpdatedBy
		   ,@CreatedBy 
		   ,@IsDeleted
		    ,@DbName, @Id OUTPUT 
	
   
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline_Update_Staff_Bonus_Discipline: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline_Update_Staff_Bonus_Discipline', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Del_DeleteStaffInformation]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

Create procedure[dbo].[Staff_Del_DeleteStaffInformation]
	
	@StaffID								bigint,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							bigint,
	@RoleID							int,
	@Result							int output
as

	begin try
		declare	
		@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
		@Params					nvarchar(max)
		--Check right


		--Update
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			update  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information_Del] 
           ,[IsDeleted]=1						
			where StaffID = @StaffID'

					SET @Params = '@StaffID bigint'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params,@StaffID
			 set @Result = 1
	end try

	begin catch
		set @Result = 0
		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Data_Staff_Information_Del: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@StaffID=' + convert(varchar, @UserID) + ', @ID=' + convert(varchar, @StaffID)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information_Del', 'DEL', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch




GO

create PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Experience_Update_Staff_Experience]
	@StaffId bigint
    ,@FromDate date
    ,@ToDate date
    ,@OfficePositionID bigint
    ,@OfficeRoleID bigint
    ,@CompanyName nvarchar(max)
    ,@Salary decimal(18,4)
    ,@CurrencyId bigint
    ,@Note nvarchar(max)
    ,@IsDeleted bit	
	,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
	,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT
as
 
begin try

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 

	 

		if @Id <= 0
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				INSERT INTO dbo.@Data_Staff_Experience
           (StaffId
           ,FromDate
           ,ToDate
           ,OfficePositionID
           ,OfficeRoleID
           ,CompanyName
           ,Salary
           ,CurrencyId
           ,Note
           ,IsDeleted)
			values(@StaffId
           ,@FromDate
           ,@ToDate
           ,@OfficePositionID
           ,@OfficeRoleID
           ,@CompanyName
           ,@Salary
           ,@CurrencyId
           ,@Note
           ,@IsDeleted)	

			SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
			 '
		END	 
		else
		begin
		SET  @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				update dbo.Data_Staff_Experience set  
						StaffId=@StaffId 
					   ,FromDate=@FromDate 
					   ,ToDate=@ToDate 
					   ,OfficePositionID=@OfficePositionID 
					   ,OfficeRoleID=@OfficeRoleID 
					   ,CompanyName=@CompanyName 
					   ,Salary=@Salary 
					   ,CurrencyId=@CurrencyId 
					   ,Note=@Note 
					   ,IsDeleted=@IsDeleted 
						 where id=@Id

				'
		end
			PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '	 @StaffId bigint
						,@FromDate date
						,@ToDate date
						,@OfficePositionID bigint
						,@OfficeRoleID bigint
						,@CompanyName nvarchar(max)
						,@Salary decimal(18,4)
						,@CurrencyId bigint
						,@Note nvarchar(max)
						,@IsDeleted bit	
						,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
						,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,
		@StaffId
           ,@FromDate
           ,@ToDate
           ,@OfficePositionID
           ,@OfficeRoleID
           ,@CompanyName
           ,@Salary
           ,@CurrencyId
           ,@Note
           ,@IsDeleted  ,@DbName, @Id OUTPUT 
	
   
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Experience_Update_Staff_Experience: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Experience_Update_Staff_Experience', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_CheckStaffInfoByStaffCode]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE procedure[dbo].[Staff_Get_CheckStaffInfoByStaffCode]
	
	@StaffCode						NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							INT
AS
BEGIN TRY 
	DECLARE
		@SQL					nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			nvarchar(max) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@Delim					nvarchar(100) = '',
		@Params					nvarchar(max) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT TOP 1 [Id]
      ,[StaffCode]
      ,[Name]
      ,[Birthday]
      ,[GenderId]
      ,[CurrentWorkingProcessId]
      ,[Email]
      ,[Phone]
      ,[PhoneCompany]
      ,[Skype]
      ,[IdentityNumber]
      ,[IdIssuedDate]
      ,[IdIssuedBy]
      ,[TaxId]
      ,[TaxDate]
      ,[TaxBy]
      ,[UserName]
      ,[BankNumber]
      ,[BankAccount]
      ,[BankName]
      ,[BankBranch]
      ,[Address]
      ,[ContactAddress]
      ,[NationalId]
      ,[ProvinceId]
      ,[Domicile]
      ,[ProvinceDomicile]
      ,[NationalDomicile]
      ,[LinkFacebook]
      ,[ImageLink]
      ,[EmailCompany]
      ,[PresentationContactName]
      ,[PresentationContactPhone]
      ,[Note]
      ,[IsSendCheckList]
      ,[SendCheckListDate]
      ,[SendCheckListBy]
      ,[TimeLateLimit]
      ,[TimeLeaveEarlyLimit]
      ,[TimekeepingForm]
      ,[HRAdditionId]
      ,[AdditionManagerId]
      ,[IsDeleted]
      ,[EthnicityId]
      ,[MaritalStatus]
      ,[IsActivated]
	  ,Id AS UserId
  FROM [Hrm_System].[dbo].[Data_Staff_Information]
			  WHERE StaffCode = ''' + @StaffCode+'''' + @WhereSQL 

			PRINT @SQL
			--SET @Params = '@StaffId BIGINT'
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL --, @Params,@StaffId
END TRY

BEGIN CATCH
	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
			@SessionId				int,
			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_CheckStaffInfoByStaffCode: ' + error_message()
	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	set @AddlInfo					= '@UserName=' + convert(varchar, @StaffCode)
	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_CheckStaffInfoByStaffCode', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

end catch




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetAllStaffForDropDown]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetAllStaffForDropDown]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 1,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' s.Name desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

		set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT s.Id,s.Name +'' - ''+ ISNULL(o.OrganizationName,'''') AS ''Name'' , w.ClassificationId'
		set @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Information s 
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w ON w.Id = s.CurrentWorkingProcessId AND ISNULL(w.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Organization o ON w.OrganizationId = o.Id AND ISNULL(o.IsDeleted,0) = 0'
		set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(s.IsDeleted,0) = 0 ' +
		' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy
	PRINT @SQL
		  exec(@SQL )


	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetAllStaffForDropDown: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetAllStaffForDropDown', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetApprovedBySaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetApprovedBySaff]
    @ListApprovedSaffs NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @DbName NVARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
		        IF ( ( SELECT   COUNT(DISTINCT DSR.RoleId) AS CountOf
				   FROM     dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_StaffRole DSR ON DSR.StaffId = DSI.Id
				   WHERE    DSI.Id IN ( SELECT  *
										FROM    dbo.splitstring(@ListApprovedSaffs, '','') )
							AND DSI.IsDeleted = 0
				 ) = 1 )
				BEGIN
					DECLARE @RoleId BIGINT = ( SELECT TOP 1
														RoleId
											   FROM     dbo.Data_StaffRole
											   WHERE    StaffId IN (
														SELECT  *
														FROM    dbo.splitstring(@ListApprovedSaffs,
																		  '','') )
											 );
					DECLARE @RequestActionId BIGINT;
					DECLARE @NextRequestStatusId BIGINT;
					IF ( @RoleId = 4 OR @RoleId = 1 )
						BEGIN
							SET @RequestActionId = 368;
							SET @NextRequestStatusId = 334;
						END
					IF ( @RoleId = 3 OR @RoleId = 5)
						BEGIN
							SET @RequestActionId = 368;
							SET @NextRequestStatusId = 336;
						END
					SELECT  DISTINCT DSI.Id, Name = DSI.Name + IIF(DR.Name IS NULL, '''', '' - '' + DR.Name) + IIF(SMD.Name IS NULL, '''', '' - '' + SMD.Name)  + IIF(DO.OrganizationName IS NULL, '''', '' - '' + DO.OrganizationName),
									Temp.NextRequestStatusId AS NextRequestStatusId
							FROM    dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSWP ON DSWP.Id = DSI.CurrentWorkingProcessId
									LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMD ON DSWP.PositionId = SMD.Id
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Organization DO ON DO.Id = DSWP.OrganizationId
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_StaffRole DSR ON DSR.StaffId = DSI.Id
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Role DR ON DR.Id = DSR.RoleId
									OUTER APPLY ( SELECT    DWSC.NextRequestStatusId
												  FROM      dbo.Data_StaffRole DSR
															LEFT JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.RequesterId = DSR.RoleId
												  WHERE     DSR.StaffId = ( SELECT TOP 1
																		  Name
																		  FROM
																		  dbo.splitstring(@ListApprovedSaffs,
																		 '','')
																		  )
															AND DWSC.RequestActionId = @RequestActionId
															AND DWSC.NextRequestStatusId = @NextRequestStatusId
															AND DWSC.IsDeleted = 0
												) Temp
							WHERE   DSI.IsDeleted = 0
									AND DSI.Id NOT IN (
									SELECT  *
									FROM    dbo.splitstring(@ListApprovedSaffs, '','') )
									AND DSR.RoleId IN (2,3,5,6,8) 
				END
			ELSE
				BEGIN
					PRINT ( ''vkl'' )
				END 
					'
		PRINT(@ExeQuery)
        SET @params = ' @ListApprovedSaffs NVARCHAR(500) ,
						@DbName NVARCHAR(500)
						'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@ListApprovedSaffs,@DbName
	
    END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetApprovedSaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetApprovedSaff] @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'			
						SELECT  DSI.Id ,
								Name = DSI.Name + IIF(SMD.Name IS NULL, '''', '' - '' + SMD.Name)
								+ IIF(DR.Name IS NULL, '''', '' - '' + DR.Name)
								+ IIF(DO.OrganizationName IS NULL, '''', '' - '' + DO.OrganizationName)
						FROM    dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
								LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSWP ON DSWP.Id = DSI.CurrentWorkingProcessId
								LEFT JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SMD ON DSWP.PositionId = SMD.Id
								LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Organization DO ON DO.Id = DSWP.OrganizationId
								LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_StaffRole DSR ON DSR.StaffId = DSI.Id
								LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Role DR ON DR.Id = DSR.RoleId
						WHERE   DSI.IsDeleted = 0
						ORDER BY DSI.Id 
					'
        SET @params = ''
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params

    END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetBonusDisciplineByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetBonusDisciplineByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@Type			BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord    INT OUTPUT
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT bd.[Id]
				  ,bd.[StaffId]
				  ,bd.[TypeId]
				  ,bd.[GroupId]
				  ,bd.[DecisionNo]
				  ,bd.[Content]
				  ,bd.[ActionId]
				  ,bd.[Amount]
				  ,bd.[CurrencyId]
				  ,bd.[SignDate]
				  ,bd.[ApplyDate]
				  ,bd.[Note]
				  ,bd.[PaySamePeriod]
				  ,bd.[Status]
				  ,bd.[CreatedDate]
				  ,bd.[CreatedBy]
				  ,bd.[UpdatedBy]
				  ,bd.[UpdatedDate]
				  ,bd.[IsDeleted]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline] bd '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE bd.IsDeleted = 0 
			AND bd.TypeId = '+CAST(@Type AS NVARCHAR)+'
			AND bd.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
		' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(bd.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE wbd.IsDeleted = 0 
			AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetBonusDisciplineByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetBonusDisciplineByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetCurrentStaffContractByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			SELECT TOP 1 c.[Id]
				  ,c.[StaffId]
				  ,c.[ContractTypeId]
				  ,c.[ContractTime]
				  ,c.[ContractCode]
				  ,c.[Name]
				  ,c.[ContractStartDate]
				  ,c.[ContractEndDate]
				  ,c.[ContractNote]
				  ,c.[ContractStatus]
				  ,c.[CreateBy]
				  ,c.[CreateDate]
				  ,c.[ModifiedBy]
				  ,c.[ModifiedDate]
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].Data_Staff_Information s
			  INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w ON  w.Id = s.CurrentWorkingProcessId AND w.Status = 50 AND w.IsDeleted = 0
			  INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Contract c ON  w.ContractId = c.Id and c.ContractStatus = 50 
			  '
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE c.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetDataUserByUserName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
