SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

CREATE procedure[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetDataUserByUserName]
	
	@UserName						NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							INT
AS
BEGIN TRY 
	DECLARE
		@SQL					nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			nvarchar(max) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@Delim					nvarchar(100) = '',
		@Params					nvarchar(max) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT top 1 u.[Id]
				  ,u.[StaffId] AS UserId
				  ,u.[UserName]
				  ,u.[DisplayName]
				  ,u.[Password]
				  ,u.[UserType]
				  ,u.[Status]
				  ,u.[LanguageId]
				  ,u.[IsActivate]
				  --,u.[IsLocked]
				  --,u.[LockedDate]
				  --,u.[LockedBy]
				  --,u.[ForgotCode]
				  --,u.[ForgotExpired]
				  ,u.[CreatedDate]
				  ,u.[CreatedBy]
				  ,u.[UpdatedDate]
				  ,u.[UpdatedBy]
				  ,u.[IsDeleted]
			  FROM [dbo].[Data_User] u
			  WHERE u.UserName = ''' + @UserName+'''' + @WhereSQL
				+' ORDER BY u.CreatedDate DESC '

			PRINT @SQL
			--SET @Params = '@StaffId BIGINT'
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL --, @Params,@StaffId
END TRY

BEGIN CATCH
	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
			@SessionId				int,
			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetDataUserByUserName: ' + error_message()
	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	set @AddlInfo					= '@UserName=' + convert(varchar, @UserName)
	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetDataUserByUserName', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

end catch




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetHealthInsuranceByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetHealthInsuranceByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT [Id]
			  ,[StaffId]
			  ,[InsuranceCode]
			  ,[InsuranceNumber]
			  ,[TypeId]
			  ,[PlaceHealthCare]
			  ,[IssuedDate]
			  ,[StartDate]
			  ,[EndDate]
			  ,[Status]
			  ,[Note]
			  ,[CreatedBy]
			  ,[CreatedDate]
			  ,[UpdatedBy]
			  ,[UpdatedDate]
			  ,[IsDeleted]
		  
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_HealthInsurance]'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE IsDeleted = 0 
			AND StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
		' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(bd.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetHealthInsuranceByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetHealthInsuranceByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByMenuName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByMenuName]
	@BaseParam			BaseParamType READONLY,
	@MenuName			NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@TotalRecord		INT OUTPUT 
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = ' DSI.Id DESC ',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight				NVARCHAR(MAX)
		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,'DSI.Id DESC')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(INT,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(INT,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query
		 SET @SQL=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
						SELECT 
							DSI.Id,
							DSI.Name,
							DSI.Phone,
							DSI.Email,
							DSI.Birthday,
							DSB.OnboardingDate,
							DSB.Note AS OnboardingNote,
							DSP.PipelineId,
							DSP.PipelineStepId,
							WP.PositionId AS OfficePositionId,
							DSB.IsSendWelcomeKit,
							DSB.IsSendChecklist,
							(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Data_ChecklistDetail DCD WHERE ChecklistId = DSB.CurrentChecklistId) AS TotalCurrentChecklistChild,
							(SELECT COUNT(*) 
									FROM Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail DSCD 
									INNER JOIN Data_ChecklistDetail DCD ON DSCD.ChecklistDetailId = DCD.Id AND DCD.ChecklistId = DSB.CurrentChecklistId
									WHERE DSCD.StaffId = DSI.Id AND DSCD.IsFinish = 1) AS TotalCurrentCheckListDetailCompleted
						FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_BoardingProcess DSB ON DSB.StaffId = DSI.Id
						--INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus DSP ON DSP.StaffId = DSI.Id
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus WHERE StaffId=DSI.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DSP
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Pipeline DP ON DP.Id=DSP.PipelineId AND DP.IsDefault=1
						LEFT JOIN Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON WP.StaffId = DSI.Id 
								AND WP.StartDate = (
									SELECT MAX(WPm.StartDate)
									FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WPm 
									WHERE WPm.StaffId = DSI.Id
								)
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON DP.MenuId = SM.Id AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1 AND SM.MenuName = ''' + CAST(@MenuName AS NVARCHAR) + '''
						WHERE DSI.IsDeleted = 0 ' + @WhereSQL + '
						ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ '
						OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  
						FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '  
		PRINT(@SQL)
		 EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		 SET @SQLCount =  N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
					SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DSI.Id)
					FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
					INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_BoardingProcess DSB ON DSB.StaffId = DSI.Id
						--INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus DSP ON DSP.StaffId = DSI.Id
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus WHERE StaffId=DSI.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DSP
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Pipeline DP ON DP.Id=DSP.PipelineId AND DP.IsDefault=1
						LEFT JOIN Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON WP.StaffId = DSI.Id 
								AND WP.StartDate = (
									SELECT MAX(WPm.StartDate)
									FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WPm 
									WHERE WPm.StaffId = DSI.Id
								)
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON DP.MenuId = SM.Id AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1 AND SM.MenuName = ''' + CAST(@MenuName AS NVARCHAR) + '''
				'
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + ' WHERE DSI.IsDeleted = 0 ' + @WhereSQL 	
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@MenuName NVARCHAR(MAX), @TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		EXECUTE sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec, @MenuName, @TotalRecord  output
	--END TRY
	--BEGIN CATCH
	--	DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
	--			@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
	--			@SessionId				INT,
	--			@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)
	--	SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
	--	SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByMenuName: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
	--	SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
	--	SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy
	--	EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByMenuName', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	--END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByStaffIdAndMenuName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByStaffIdAndMenuName]
	@BaseParam			BaseParamType READONLY,
	@MenuName			NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@StaffId			BIGINT,
	@TotalRecord		INT OUTPUT 
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = ' DSI.Id DESC ',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight				NVARCHAR(MAX)
		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,'DSI.Id DESC')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(INT,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(INT,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query
		 SET @SQL=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
						SELECT 
							DSB.OnboardingDate,
							DSP.PipelineId,
							DSP.PipelineStepId
						FROM  dbo.Data_Staff_BoardingProcess DSB 
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 PipelineId, PipelineStepId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus WHERE StaffId=DSB.StaffId ORDER BY Id DESC) DSP
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Pipeline DP ON DP.Id=DSP.PipelineId AND DP.IsDefault=1
						LEFT JOIN Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON WP.StaffId = DSB.StaffId
								AND WP.StartDate = (
									SELECT MAX(WPm.StartDate)
									FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WPm 
									WHERE WPm.StaffId = StaffId
								)
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON DP.MenuId = SM.Id AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1 AND SM.MenuName = ''' + CAST(@MenuName AS NVARCHAR) + '''
						WHERE DSB.IsDeleted = 0 ' + @WhereSQL + '
							AND DSB.StaffId = '+ CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR)   
		PRINT(@SQL)
		 EXEC(@SQL )
		
	--END TRY
	--BEGIN CATCH
	--	DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
	--			@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
	--			@SessionId				INT,
	--			@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)
	--	SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
	--	SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByMenuName: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
	--	SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
	--	SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy
	--	EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetPipelineStepStaffByMenuName', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	--END CATCH
	 

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord	INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY r.id) AS OrderNo
			  ,r.[StaffId]
			  ,r.[Id]
			  ,r.[RelationshipId]
			  ,r.[Name]
			  ,r.[BirthDay]
			  ,r.[Phone]
			  ,r.[Status]
			  ,r.[IsEmergency]
			  ,r.[Deduction]
			  ,r.[DeductionCode]
			  ,r.[DeductionFrom]
			  ,r.[DeductionTo]
			  ,r.[Note]
			  ,r.[CreatedDate]
			  ,r.[CreatedBy]
			  ,r.[UpdatedBy]
			  ,r.[UpdatedDate]
			  ,r.[IsDeleted]
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships] r '
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE r.IsDeleted = 0 and r.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY r.id),' + @OrderBy + 
	  ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(r.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE r.IsDeleted = 0 and r.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetSalaryDetailById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetSalaryDetailById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT  
			   w.[Id]
			  ,w.[StaffId]
			  ,w.[DecisionDate]
			  ,w.[StartDate]
			  ,w.[EndDate]
			  ,w.[OrganizationId]
			  ,w.[PolicyId]
			  ,w.[CurrencyId]
			  ,w.[BasicPay]
			  ,w.[EfficiencyBonus]
			  ,w.[PaymentForm]
			  ,w.[PaymentMethod]
			  ,w.[SalaryNote]
			  ,w.[Description]
			  ,w.[Note]
			  ,w.[SalaryNote]
			  ,w.[CurrencyId]
			  ,w.[Status]  '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(w.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND w.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetSalaryDetailById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetSalaryDetailById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetSocialInsuranceByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/

GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetSocialInsuranceByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT [Id]
			  ,[StaffId]
			  ,[TypeId]
			  ,[InsuranceCode]
			  ,[InsuranceNumber]
			  ,[FamilyCode]
			  ,[PlaceHold]
			  ,[UnionAmount]
			  ,[CurrencyId]
			  ,[DateReturn]
			  ,[Status]
			  ,[RateCompany]
			  ,[RatePerson]
			  ,[MonthStart]
			  ,[StartDate]
			  ,[EndDate]
			  ,[Note]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_SocialInsurance] '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' where StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY StartDate DESC, EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetSocialInsuranceByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetSocialInsuranceByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query

			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		DECLARE @DateTimeMaxValue DATETIME = ''9999-12-31''
		DECLARE @DateTimeMinValue DATETIME = ''1900-01-01''
			SELECT	
				 DSI.[Id]
			    ,DSI.[StaffCode]
			    ,DSI.[Name]
			    ,DSI.[Birthday]
			    ,DSI.[GenderId]
				,DSI.[Email]
			    ,DSI.[Phone]
			    ,DSI.[IdentityNumber]
				,DSI.[IdIssuedDate]
			    ,DSI.[IdIssuedBy]
			    ,DSI.[TaxId]
			    ,DSI.[TaxDate]
			    ,DSI.[TaxBy]
			    ,DSI.[UserName]
			    ,DSI.[BankNumber]
				,DSI.[BankName]
				,DSI.[Address]
				,DSI.[ContactAddress]
				,DSI.[NationalId]
				,DSI.[LinkFacebook]
				,DSI.[ImageLink]
				,DSI.[EmailCompany]
				,DSI.[PresentationContactName]
				,DSI.[PresentationContactPhone]
				,DSI.[Note]
				,S1.[Name] AS ManagerName
				,WP.PositionId AS OfficePositionId
				,O.Id AS OrganizationId
				,CT.ContractTypeId
				,WP.WorkingStatus AS StatusId ' 

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] DSI 
	  LEFT JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess] WP ON DSI.[CurrentWorkingProcessId] = WP.id  
	  JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_Contract] CT ON WP.[ContractId] = CT.id
	  LEFT JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] S1 ON WP.ManagerId = S1.Id 
	  LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Organization O ON WP.OrganizationId = O.Id
	  '
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE  DSI.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
	  ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  PRINT @SQL
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' DECLARE @DateTimeMaxValue DATETIME = ''9999-12-31'' DECLARE @DateTimeMinValue DATETIME = ''1900-01-01''  SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DSI.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DSI.IsDeleted = 0' +@WhereSQL 
		PRINT(@dynamicsql)
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowanceById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT a.[Id]
			  ,a.[WorkingProcessId]
			  ,a.[StaffId]
			  ,a.[Name]
			  ,a.[AllowanceType]
			  ,a.[Status]
			  ,a.[Amount]
			  ,a.[CurrencyId]
			  ,a.[Content]
			  ,a.[Note]
			  ,a.[Status]
			  ,a.[StartDate]
			  ,a.[EndDate] '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance a '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(a.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND a.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowanceById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowanceById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowanceByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT b.[Id]
				  ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY b.id) AS OrderNo
				  ,b.[Name]
				  ,b.[StaffId]
				  ,b.[Amount]
				  ,b.[AllowanceType]
				  ,b.[CurrencyId]
				  ,b.[Content]
				  ,b.[Note]
				  ,b.[Status]
				  ,b.[StartDate]
				  ,b.[EndDate]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Allowance] b
			--JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information s ON s.Id = b.StaffId AND s.id = b.StaffId 
			'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(b.IsDeleted,0) = 0 -- AND ISNULL(s.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
			AND b.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY b.StartDate DESC, b.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowance: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowanceByWorkingprocess]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@WorkingprocessId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT b.[Id]
				  ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY b.id) AS OrderNo
				  ,b.[Name]
				  ,b.[StaffId]
				  ,b.[Amount]
				  ,b.[AllowanceType]
				  ,s.[CurrencyId]
				  ,b.[Content]
				  ,b.[Note]
				  ,b.[Status]
				  ,b.[StartDate]
				  ,b.[EndDate]
				  ,b.[TaxExemption]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Allowance] b
			JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information s ON s.Id = b.StaffId AND s.id = b.StaffId 
			'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(b.IsDeleted,0) = 0 -- AND ISNULL(s.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
			AND b.WorkingprocessId = '+CAST(@WorkingprocessId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY Id ASC, b.StartDate DESC, b.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffAllowanceByWorkingprocess: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,

	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT a.[Id]
				  ,a.[WorkingProcessId]
				  ,a.[StaffId]
				  ,a.[BenefitType]
				  ,a.[Amount]
				  ,a.[CurrencyId]
				  ,a.[Content]
				  ,a.[Note]
				  ,a.[Status]
				  ,a.[StartDate]
				  ,a.[EndDate]
				  ,a.[IsDeleted] '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Benefits a '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(a.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND a.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT b.[Id]
				  ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY b.id) AS OrderNo
				  ,b.[WorkingProcessId]
				  ,b.[StaffId]
				  ,b.[BenefitType]
				  ,b.[Amount]
				  ,b.[CurrencyId]
				  ,b.[Content]
				  ,b.[Note]
				  ,b.[Status]
				  ,b.[StartDate]
				  ,b.[EndDate]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Benefits] b
			--JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information s ON s.Id = b.StaffId AND s.ID = b.StaffId
			'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(b.IsDeleted,0) = 0 -- AND ISNULL(s.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
			AND b.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY b.StartDate DESC, b.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitByWorkingprocess]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@WorkingProcessId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT b.[Id]
				  ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY b.id) AS OrderNo
				  ,b.[WorkingProcessId]
				  ,b.[StaffId]
				  ,b.[BenefitType]
				  ,b.[Amount]
				  ,s.[CurrencyId]
				  ,b.[Content]
				  ,b.[Note]
				  ,b.[Status]
				  ,b.[StartDate]
				  ,b.[EndDate]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Benefits] b
			JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information s ON s.Id = b.StaffId AND s.ID = b.StaffId
			'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(b.IsDeleted,0) = 0 -- AND ISNULL(s.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
			AND b.WorkingProcessId = '+CAST(@WorkingProcessId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY Id ASC, b.StartDate DESC, b.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBenefitByWorkingprocess', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH

GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffBonusDisciplineById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT a.[Id]
			  ,a.[StaffId]
			  ,a.[TypeId]
			  ,a.[GroupId]
			  ,a.[DecisionNo]
			  ,a.[Content]
			  ,a.[ActionId]
			  ,a.[Amount]
			  ,a.[CurrencyId]
			  ,a.[SignDate]
			  ,a.[ApplyDate]
			  ,a.[PaySamePeriod]
			  ,a.[Note]
			  ,a.[Status]
			  ,a.[CreatedDate]
			  ,a.[CreatedBy]
			  ,a.[UpdatedBy]
			  ,a.[UpdatedDate] '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline a '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(a.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND a.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBonusDisciplineById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffBonusDisciplineById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffByOrganizationId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffByOrganizationId]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@ParentId				BIGINT,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		PRINT @FilterField
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		--set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,'DSI.Id desc')
		set		@OrderBy				= 'S.Id desc'
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' and '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
					 N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' +'
					 DECLARE @DateTimeMaxValue DATETIME = ''9999-12-31''
					 DECLARE @DateTimeMinValue DATETIME = ''1900-01-01''
					;WITH ACE(Id,ParentId) AS(
					SELECT O.Id,O.ParentId
					FROM dbo.Data_Organization O
					WHERE O.Id='+CAST(@ParentId AS NVARCHAR)+'
					UNION ALL
					SELECT O.Id,O.ParentId
					FROM dbo.Data_Organization O,ACE
					WHERE ACE.Id=O.ParentId
				)'

	  --set @SQLFrom='SELECT 
			--			--DSI.Id,DSI.Name,DSI.StatusId,DSI.Address
			--			DSI.*
			--			FROM ACE A
			--			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW ON A.Id=DSW.OrganizationId AND DSW.EndDate IS  NULL AND DSW.StartDate IS NOT NULL
			--			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id =DSW.StaffID '
			
		SET	@SQLFrom						= 
			N'
			SELECT	
				 S.[Id]
			    ,S.[StaffCode]
			    ,S.[Name]
			    ,S.[Birthday]
			    ,S.[GenderId]
				,S.[Email]
			    ,S.[Phone]
			    ,S.[IdentityNumber]
				,S.[IdIssuedDate]
			    ,S.[IdIssuedBy]
			    ,S.[TaxId]
			    ,S.[TaxDate]
			    ,S.[TaxBy]
			    ,S.[UserName]
			    ,S.[BankNumber]
				,S.[BankName]
				,S.[Address]
				,S.[ContactAddress]
				,S.[NationalId]
				,S.[LinkFacebook]
				,S.[ImageLink]
				,S.[EmailCompany]
				,S.[PresentationContactName]
				,S.[PresentationContactPhone]
				,S.[Note]
				,S1.[Name] AS ManagerName
				,WP.PositionId AS OfficePositionId
				,WP.OfficeId AS OfficeId
				,ContractTypeId=(select top 1 ContractTypeId from Data_Staff_Contract dc where dc.staffid=s.id order by ContractStartDate desc)
				,WP.WorkingStatus AS StatusId 
				,RoleId=(select top 1 DSR.RoleId from Data_StaffRole DSR where DSR.staffid=s.id order by id desc)
				,WP.OrganizationId 
			FROM ACE A
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON A.Id=WP.OrganizationId 
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information S ON S.Id =WP.StaffID   and S.[CurrentWorkingProcessId] = WP.id  
			LEFT JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] S1 ON WP.ManagerId = S1.Id 
			' 

	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE  S.IsDeleted = 0  ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		 ' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 print @SQL
		  exec(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		

		--set @SQLCount= @SQLSelect + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DSI.Id) FROM ACE A
		--				INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSW ON A.Id=DSW.OrganizationId AND DSW.EndDate IS  NULL AND DSW.StartDate IS NOT NULL
		--				INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id =DSW.StaffID '
		
		set @SQLCount= @SQLSelect  + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(S.Id) 
												FROM ACE A
												INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON A.Id=WP.OrganizationId 
												INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information S ON S.Id =WP.StaffID   and S.[CurrentWorkingProcessId] = WP.id  
												LEFT JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] S1 ON WP.ManagerId = S1.Id '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + ' WHERE S.IsDeleted = 0' + @WhereSQL 
		
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Organization', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffByParentId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffByParentId]
	
	@ParentId						BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(MAX)
AS

	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQL					nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			nvarchar(max) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@Delim					nvarchar(100) = '',
		@Params					nvarchar(max)
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			;WITH CTE_StaffParrent(StaffId, ParentId)
			AS(
				SELECT StaffId, ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP 
				WHERE DSP.StaffId = @ParentId AND DSP.ParentId = @ParentId
				UNION 
				SELECT DSP.StaffId, DSP.ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP
				WHERE DSP.ParentId = @ParentId AND DSP.StaffId != @ParentId 
			)
			SELECT * FROM CTE_StaffParrent cte
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI
			ON cte.StaffId  =  DSI.Id 
			WHERE ISNULL(DSI.IsDeleted,0)=0
			'
			SET @Params = '@ParentId BIGINT'
	PRINT @SQL 
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @ParentId
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@ParentId=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @ParentId)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH





GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffCertificate]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT
				  c.[Id]
				  ,c.[StaffId]
				  ,c.[TypeId]
				  ,c.[Name]
				  ,c.[IssuedDate]
				  ,c.[FromDate]
				  ,c.[ToDate]
				  ,c.[RankId]
				  ,c.[IssuedBy]
				  ,c.[Point]
				  ,c.[Note]
				  ,c.[IsDeleted]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Certificate] c '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(c.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
			AND c.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY c.FromDate DESC, c.ToDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffCertificate: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffCertificate', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffCertificateById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT a.[Id]
			  ,a.[StaffId]
			  ,a.[TypeId]
			  ,a.[Name]
			  ,a.[IssuedDate]
			  ,a.[FromDate]
			  ,a.[ToDate]
			  ,a.[RankId]
			  ,a.[IssuedBy]
			  ,a.[Point]
			  ,a.[Note]
			  ,a.[IsDeleted] '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Certificate] a '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(a.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND a.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffCertificateById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffCertificateById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffExperience]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT
				  [Id]
				  ,[StaffId]
				  ,[FromDate]
				  ,[ToDate]
				  ,[OfficePositionID]
				  ,[OfficeRoleID]
				  ,[CompanyName]
				  ,[Salary]
				  ,[CurrencyId]
				  ,[Note]
				  ,[IsDeleted]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Experience] c '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(c.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
			AND c.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY c.FromDate DESC, c.ToDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffExperienceById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT TOP 2 b.[Id]
			  ,b.[StaffId]
			  ,b.[FromDate]
			  ,b.[ToDate]
			  ,b.[OfficePositionID]
			  ,b.[OfficeRoleID]
			  ,b.[CompanyName]
			  ,b.[Salary]
			  ,b.[CurrencyId]
			  ,b.[Note]
			  ,b.[IsDeleted] '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Experience] a 
			  JOIN [Data_Staff_Experience] b ON b.StaffId = a.StaffId '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(a.IsDeleted,0) = 0 AND b.FromDate <= a.FromDate 
			  AND a.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL +
			  '  ORDER BY b.FromDate DESC  '
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffExperienceById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffExperienceById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffHealthInsurance]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT top 1 h.[Id]
					,h.[StaffId]
					,h.[TypeId]
					,h.[InsuranceCode]
					,h.[InsuranceNumber]
					,h.[PlaceHealthCare]
					,h.[IssuedDate]
					,h.[StartDate]
					,h.[EndDate]
					,h.[Status]
					,h.[Note]
					,h.[CreatedBy]
					,h.[CreatedDate]
					,h.[UpdatedBy]
					,h.[UpdatedDate]
					,h.[IsDeleted]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom=' from dbo.[Data_Staff_HealthInsurance] h  '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' where  ISNULL(h.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			AND h.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY h.StartDate DESC, h.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetHealthInsurance: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetHealthInsurance', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
