/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

CREATE procedure[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffInformationById]
	
	@StaffId						BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							INT
AS
BEGIN TRY 
	DECLARE
		@SQL					nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			nvarchar(max) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@Delim					nvarchar(100) = '',
		@Params					nvarchar(max) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			--DECLARE @ActiveStatus BIGINT = ( SELECT Id FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE GroupId = 45 AND Name = N''Đã duyệt'')
			--DECLARE @DateTimeMaxValue DATETIME = ''9999-12-31''
			--DECLARE @DateTimeMinValue DATETIME = ''1900-01-01''

			SELECT top 1
				s.[Id]
				,s.[StaffCode]
				,s.[Name]
				,s.[Birthday]
				,s.[GenderId]
				,s.[Email]
				,s.[Phone]
				,s.[IdentityNumber]
				,s.[IdIssuedDate]
				,s.[IdIssuedBy]
				,s.[TaxId]
				,s.[TaxDate]
				,s.[TaxBy]
				,u.[UserName]
				,s.[BankNumber]
				,s.[BankAccount]
				,s.[BankName]
				,s.[Address]
				,s.[ContactAddress]
				,s.[Domicile]
				,s.[NationalId]
				,s.[LinkFacebook]
				,s.[ImageLink]
				,s.[EmailCompany]
				,s.[PresentationContactName]
				,s.[PresentationContactPhone]
				,s.[Note]
				,s.[TimeLateLimit]
				,s.[TimeLeaveEarlyLimit]
				,s.[TimekeepingForm]
				,s.[HRAdditionId]
				,s.[AdditionManagerId]
				,s.BankBranch
				,s.PhoneCompany
				,s.EthnicityId
				,s.Skype
				,s.CurrencyId
				,s.IsActivated
				,w.PositionId AS OfficePositionId
				,w.WorkingStatus
				,w.OrganizationId
				,w.ManagerId
				,w.ClassificationId
				,s.MaritalStatus
				,ms.Name AS ManagerName
				,ws.PositionId ManagerOfficePositionId
				,ws.OrganizationId ManagerOrganizationId
				,sctr.ContractTypeId
				,DSP.PipelineStepId
				,DSP.PipelineId
			FROM  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] S
			LEFT JOIN Data_User u on s.Id = u.StaffId
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w ON w.Id = s.CurrentWorkingProcessId AND ISNULL(w.IsDeleted,0) = 0  AND w.Status = 50
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Contract sctr ON w.ContractId = sctr.Id AND sctr.ContractStatus = 50
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information ms ON w.ManagerId = ms.Id
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess ws ON  ws.Id = ms.CurrentWorkingProcessId
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus DSP ON DSP.StaffId = S.Id AND DSP.Date = (
									SELECT MAX(DSPm.Date)
									FROM dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus DSPm
									WHERE DSPm.StaffId = DSP.StaffId
								)
			WHERE s.IsDeleted=0 
				AND s.Id = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) + @WhereSQL
				+' ORDER BY w.StartDate DESC '

			PRINT @SQL
			SET @Params = '@StaffId BIGINT'
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params,@StaffId
END TRY

BEGIN CATCH
	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
			@SessionId				int,
			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffInformationById: ' + error_message()
	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	set @AddlInfo					= '@StaffId=' + convert(varchar, @StaffId)
	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffInformationById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

end catch




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

CREATE procedure[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById]
	
	@StaffId						BIGINT,
	@Date							DATETIME = GETDATE,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							INT
AS

	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQL					nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			nvarchar(max) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max) = '',
		@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max) = '',
		@Delim					nvarchar(100) = '',
		@Params					nvarchar(max)
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END


		--select
		SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			DECLARE @DateTimeMaxValue DATETIME = ''9999-12-31''
			DECLARE @DateTimeMinValue DATETIME = ''1900-01-01''
			DECLARE @Result TABLE(
				StaffId BIGINT,
				ParentId BIGINT
			)
			;WITH Down(StaffId, ParentId)
			AS(
				SELECT StaffId, ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP 
				WHERE DSP.StaffId = @StaffId AND DSP.StaffId != DSP.ParentId AND DSP.Type = 1
					AND @Date BETWEEN ISNULL(DSP.FromDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(DSP.ToDate, @DateTimeMaxValue)
				UNION ALL
				SELECT DSP.StaffId, DSP.ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP, Down T
				WHERE T.StaffId = DSP.ParentId AND DSP.StaffId != DSP.ParentId AND DSP.Type = 1
					AND @Date BETWEEN ISNULL(DSP.FromDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(DSP.ToDate, @DateTimeMaxValue)
			)
			INSERT INTO @Result
			SELECT StaffId, ParentId FROM Down
			
			;WITH Up(StaffId, ParentId)
			AS(
				SELECT StaffId, ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP 
				WHERE DSP.StaffId = @StaffId AND DSP.StaffId != DSP.ParentId AND DSP.Type = 1
					AND @Date BETWEEN ISNULL(DSP.FromDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(DSP.ToDate, @DateTimeMaxValue)
				UNION ALL
				SELECT DSP.StaffId, DSP.ParentId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP, Up T
				WHERE T.ParentId = DSP.StaffId AND DSP.StaffId != DSP.ParentId AND DSP.Type = 1
					AND @Date BETWEEN ISNULL(DSP.FromDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(DSP.ToDate, @DateTimeMaxValue)
			)
			INSERT INTO @Result
			SELECT U.StaffId, U.ParentId FROM Up U
			LEFT JOIN @Result R ON R.ParentId = U.ParentId AND R.StaffId = U.StaffId
			WHERE R.StaffId IS NULL
			SELECT 
				DSI.*, 
				WP.PositionId AS OfficePositionId,
				R.ParentId, 
				(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM @Result Rm WHERE Rm.ParentId =  R.StaffId) AS NumberOfChild
			FROM @Result R
			INNER JOIN Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id = R.StaffId
			LEFT JOIN Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON WP.StaffId = R.StaffId 
								AND WP.StartDate = (
									SELECT MAX(WPm.StartDate)
									FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WPm 
									WHERE WPm.StaffId = R.StaffId
								)
			WHERE-- DSI.isdelete=0 and
			 R.StaffId != 0 ' + @WhereSQL + '
			ORDER BY R.StaffId'
			SET @Params = '@StaffId BIGINT, @Date DateTime'
	PRINT @SQL 
	-- EXEC select data with param
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @StaffId, @Date
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@StaffId=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @StaffId)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffParentById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH





GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffSalary]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffSalary]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			DECLARE @DateTimeMaxValue DATETIME = ''9999-12-31''
			DECLARE @DateTimeMinValue DATETIME = ''1900-01-01''
			DECLARE @ActiveId BIGINT = (SELECT id FROM dbo.System_MasterData  WHERE Name  = N''Đã duyệt'')

			SELECT w.[Id]
			  ,w.[StaffId]
			  ,w.[CurrencyId]
			  ,w.[BasicPay]
			  ,w.[EfficiencyBonus]
			  ,w.[PaymentForm]
			  ,w.[PaymentMethod]
			  ,w.[Description]
			  ,w.[Note]
			  ,w.[SalaryNote]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess] w 
			JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information s on w.Id = s.CurrentWorkingProcessId '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 AND s.IsDeleted = 0 
			AND w.Status = @ActiveId
			AND s.Id = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY w.StartDate DESC, w.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffSalary: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffSalary', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffSocialInsurance]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT TOP 1 [Id]
			  ,[StaffId]
			  ,[TypeId]
			  ,[InsuranceCode]
			  ,[InsuranceNumber]
			  ,[FamilyCode]
			  ,[PlaceHold]
			  ,[UnionAmount]
			  ,[CurrencyId]
			  ,[DateReturn]
			  ,[Status]
			  ,[RateCompany]
			  ,[RatePerson]
			  ,[MonthStart]
			  ,[StartDate]
			  ,[EndDate]
			  ,[Note]
			'
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_SocialInsurance] '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' where StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY StartDate DESC, EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetSocialInsurance: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetSocialInsurance', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffWorkingDayMachineByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetStaffWorkingDayMachineByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord	INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY m.id) AS OrderNo
			  ,m.[Id]
			  ,m.[StaffId]
			  ,m.[WorkingDayMachineId]
			  ,m.[SSN]
			  ,m.[Note]
			  ,m.[CreatedBy]
			  ,m.[CreatedDate]
			  ,m.[UpdatedBy]
			  ,m.[UpdatedDate]
			  ,m.[IsDeleted]
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingDay_Machine] m '
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE m.IsDeleted = 0 and m.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY m.id),' + @OrderBy + 
	  ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(m.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE m.IsDeleted = 0 and m.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetStaffWorkingDayMachineByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetStaffWorkingDayMachineByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetSttaffInformation]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_GetSttaffInformation]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT s.[AutoId]
				  ,s.[StaffId]
				  ,s.[StaffCode]
				  ,s.[Name]
				  ,s.[BirthDay]
				  ,s.[GenderID]
				  ,s.[Email]
				  ,s.[Phone]
				  ,s.[PhoneEx]
				  ,s.[Mobile]
				  ,s.[Status]
				  ,s.[OfficePositionID]
				  ,s.[IdentityNumber]
				  ,s.[IDIssuedDate]
				  ,s.[IDIssuedBy]
				  ,s.[TaxID]
				  ,s.[TaxDate]
				  ,s.[TaxBy]
				  ,s.[AccountName]
				  ,s.[BankNumber]
				  ,s.[BankName]
				  ,s.[CountryID]
				  ,s.[ProvinceID]
				  ,s.[Address]
				  ,s.[ContactAddress]
				  ,s.[ContactCountryID]
				  ,s.[ContactProvinceID]
				  ,s.[NationId]
				  ,s.[LinkFacebook]
				  ,s.[ImageLink]
				  ,s.[EmailCompany]
				  ,s.[EmailPersonal]
				  ,s.[ContactName]
				  ,s.[ContactPhone]
				  ,s.[Note]
				  ,s.[IsDeleted]'
	  set @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] s '
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE s.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		 ' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 
		  exec(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(o.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE s.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL 
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@ItemCount INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetWorkingProcessDetailById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Staff_Get_GetWorkingProcessDetailById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT  
			   w.[Id]
			  ,w.[StaffId]
			  ,w.[WorkingprocessTypeId]
			  ,w.[DecisionNo]
			  ,w.[WorkingStatus]
			  ,w.[DecisionDate]
			  ,w.[StartDate]
			  ,w.[EndDate]
			  ,w.[ContractId]
			  ,w.[OrganizationId]
			  ,w.[OfficeId]
			  ,w.[PositionId]
			  ,w.[ClassificationId]
			  ,w.[StaffLevelId]
			  ,w.[ManagerId]
			  ,w.[HRManagerId]
			  ,w.[PolicyId]
			  ,w.[CurrencyId]
			  ,w.[BasicPay]
			  ,w.[EfficiencyBonus]
			  ,w.[PaymentForm]
			  ,w.[PaymentMethod]
			  ,w.[SalaryNote]
			  ,w.[Description]
			  ,w.[Note]
			  ,w.[Status]
			  ,w.[ShiftId]
			  ,ct.[ContractTypeId]
			  ,ct.[ContractTime]
			  ,ct.[ContractCode]
			  ,ct.[Name]
			  ,ct.[ContractStartDate]
			  ,ct.[ContractEndDate]
			  ,ct.[ContractNote]
			  ,ct.[ContractStatus] '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w
			  LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Contract ct ON w.ContractId = ct.Id '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(w.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND w.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Get_GetWorkingProcessDetailById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Get_GetWorkingProcessDetailById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH




GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Get_SearchPermissionStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Get_SearchPermissionStaff]
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

					SELECT S.Id,S.Name +'' - ''+ ISNULL(O.OrganizationName,'''') AS ''Name'' , WP.ClassificationId,S.Name
					FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Information S
					LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WP ON WP.Id = s.CurrentWorkingProcessId AND ISNULL(WP.IsDeleted,0) = 0
					LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Organization O ON WP.OrganizationId = O.Id AND ISNULL(O.IsDeleted,0) = 0
					WHERE LOWER(S.Name) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')
				'
	SET @params = '@SearchKey NVARCHAR(MAX)'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @SearchKey
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Information_Update_SaveStaff_Information]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Information_Update_SaveStaff_Information]
		@StaffCode nvarchar(250)
		,@Name nvarchar(250)
		,@Birthday date
		,@GenderId bigint
		,@CurrentWorkingProcessId bigint
		,@Email nvarchar(max)
		,@Phone nvarchar(max)
		,@PhoneCompany nvarchar(max)
		,@Skype nchar(250)
		,@IdentityNumber nvarchar(100)
		,@IdIssuedDate date
		,@IdIssuedBy nvarchar(100)
		,@TaxId nvarchar(100)
		,@TaxDate date
		,@TaxBy nvarchar(100)
		,@UserName nvarchar(max)
		,@BankNumber nvarchar(max)
		,@BankName nvarchar(max)
		,@BankBranch nvarchar(max)
		,@Address nvarchar(max)
		,@ContactAddress nvarchar(max)
		,@NationalId bigint
		,@LinkFacebook nvarchar(max)
		,@ImageLink nvarchar(max)
		,@EmailCompany nvarchar(max)
		,@PresentationContactName nvarchar(max)
		,@PresentationContactPhone nvarchar(max)
		,@Note nvarchar(max)
		,@IsSendCheckList bit
		,@SendCheckListDate datetime
		,@SendCheckListBy datetime
		,@IsDeleted bit
		,@EthnicityId bigint
		,@MaritalStatus BIGINT
        ,@IsOnboarding	BIT = 0
		,@OnboardingDate DATETIME = NULL
		--,@IsActivate	bit
		--,@Status		 bigint
		--,@Password		 NVARCHAR(500)
		--,@LanguageId	bigint
		--,@CreatedDate	datetime
		,@CreatedBy	bigint 
		,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
		,@Id				bigint output


AS 
	begin try
		declare	
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@Params					nvarchar(max)

		if @Id <= 0
			begin
			-- insert
				print (1);
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			
	INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information]
           ([StaffCode]
           ,[Name]
           ,[Birthday]
           ,[GenderId]
           ,[CurrentWorkingProcessId]
           ,[Email]
           ,[Phone]
           ,[PhoneCompany]
           ,[Skype]
           ,[IdentityNumber]
           ,[IdIssuedDate]
           ,[IdIssuedBy]
           ,[TaxId]
           ,[TaxDate]
           ,[TaxBy]
           ,[UserName]
           ,[BankNumber]
           ,[BankName]
           ,[BankBranch]
           ,[Address]
           ,[ContactAddress]
           ,[NationalId]
           ,[LinkFacebook]
           ,[ImageLink]
           ,[EmailCompany]
           ,[PresentationContactName]
           ,[PresentationContactPhone]
           ,[Note]
           ,[IsSendCheckList]
           ,[SendCheckListDate]
           ,[SendCheckListBy]
           ,[IsDeleted]
           ,[EthnicityId]
           ,[MaritalStatus])
     VALUES (
			@StaffCode
           ,@Name
           ,@Birthday
           ,@GenderId
           ,@CurrentWorkingProcessId
           ,@Email
           ,@Phone
           ,@PhoneCompany
           ,@Skype
           ,@IdentityNumber
           ,@IdIssuedDate
           ,@IdIssuedBy
           ,@TaxId
           ,@TaxDate
           ,@TaxBy
           ,@UserName
           ,@BankNumber
           ,@BankName
           ,@BankBranch
           ,@Address
           ,@ContactAddress
           ,@NationalId
           ,@LinkFacebook
           ,@ImageLink
           ,@EmailCompany
           ,@PresentationContactName
           ,@PresentationContactPhone
           ,@Note
           ,@IsSendCheckList
           ,@SendCheckListDate
           ,@SendCheckListBy
           ,@IsDeleted
           ,@EthnicityId
           ,@MaritalStatus)
	SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
	IF(@Id > 0)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_User]
		   ([Id]
		   ,[StaffId]
		   ,[UserName]
		   ,[DisplayName]
		   ,[Password]
		   ,[Status]
		   ,[CreatedDate]
		   ,[CreatedBy]
		   ,[IsDeleted]
		   ,[LanguageId])
		VALUES( @Id
		   ,@Id
		   ,@UserName
		   ,@Name
		   ,@Password
		   ,8
		   ,GETDATE()
		   ,@CreatedBy
		   ,0
		   ,1)
		END
	IF(@IsOnboarding = 1 AND @Id > 0)
	BEGIN
		DECLARE 
			@PipelineId BIGINT = 0,
			@PipelineStepId BIGINT = 0

		SELECT  TOP 1
				@PipelineStepId = DPS.Id,
				@PipelineId = DP.Id AS PipelineId
			FROM dbo.Data_Pipeline DP
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper DPM ON DPM.PipelineId = DP.Id
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineStep DPS ON DPS.Id = DPM.PipelineStepId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DP.MenuId AND SM.IsIncludeMenu = 1
			WHERE SM.MenuName = N''Onboarding'' AND DP.IsDefault = 1
			ORDER BY DPS.OrderNo

		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_BoardingProcess]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[OnboardingDate]
           ,[IsDeleted])
		VALUES
           (@Id
		   ,@OnboardingDate
		   ,0)

		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_PipelineStatus]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[PipelineId]
           ,[PipelineStepId]
           ,[Date]
           ,[Note]
           ,[IsDeleted])
		VALUES (
			@Id
			,@PipelineId
			,@PipelineStepId
			,@OnboardingDate
			,NULL
			,0
		   )
	END
			'
	
			end
		else
			begin
				--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			update  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information]
           set
		   StaffCode=@StaffCode
           ,Name=@Name
           ,Birthday=@Birthday
           ,GenderId=@GenderId
           ,CurrentWorkingProcessId=@CurrentWorkingProcessId
           ,Email=@Email
           ,Phone=@Phone
           ,PhoneCompany=@PhoneCompany
           ,Skype=@Skype
           ,IdentityNumber=@IdentityNumber
           ,IdIssuedDate=@IdIssuedDate
           ,IdIssuedBy=@IdIssuedBy
           ,TaxId=@TaxId
           ,TaxDate=@TaxDate
           ,TaxBy=@TaxBy
           ,UserName=@UserName
           ,BankNumber=@BankNumber
           ,BankName=@BankName
           ,BankBranch=@BankBranch
           ,Address=@Address
           ,ContactAddress=@ContactAddress
           ,NationalId=@NationalId
           ,LinkFacebook=@LinkFacebook
           ,ImageLink=@ImageLink
           ,EmailCompany=@EmailCompany
           ,PresentationContactName=@PresentationContactName
           ,PresentationContactPhone=@PresentationContactPhone
           ,Note=@Note
           ,IsSendCheckList=@IsSendCheckList
           ,SendCheckListDate=@SendCheckListDate
           ,SendCheckListBy=@SendCheckListBy
           ,IsDeleted=@IsDeleted
           ,EthnicityId=@EthnicityId
           ,MaritalStatus=@MaritalStatus				
					where Id = @Id'
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '@StaffCode nvarchar(250)
		,@Name nvarchar(250)
		,@Birthday date
		,@GenderId bigint
		,@CurrentWorkingProcessId bigint
		,@Email nvarchar(max)
		,@Phone nvarchar(max)
		,@PhoneCompany nvarchar(max)
		,@Skype nchar(250)
		,@IdentityNumber nvarchar(100)
		,@IdIssuedDate date
		,@IdIssuedBy nvarchar(100)
		,@TaxId nvarchar(100)
		,@TaxDate date
		,@TaxBy nvarchar(100)
		,@UserName nvarchar(max)
		,@BankNumber nvarchar(max)
		,@BankName nvarchar(max)
		,@BankBranch nvarchar(max)
		,@Address nvarchar(max)
		,@ContactAddress nvarchar(max)
		,@NationalId bigint
		,@LinkFacebook nvarchar(max)
		,@ImageLink nvarchar(max)
		,@EmailCompany nvarchar(max)
		,@PresentationContactName nvarchar(max)
		,@PresentationContactPhone nvarchar(max)
		,@Note nvarchar(max)
		,@IsSendCheckList bit
		,@SendCheckListDate datetime
		,@SendCheckListBy datetime
		,@IsDeleted bit
		,@EthnicityId bigint
		,@MaritalStatus bigint 
		,@Id				bigint  '
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print (@SQL)
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @StaffCode
           ,@Name
           ,@Birthday
           ,@GenderId
           ,@CurrentWorkingProcessId
           ,@Email
           ,@Phone
           ,@PhoneCompany
           ,@Skype
           ,@IdentityNumber
           ,@IdIssuedDate
           ,@IdIssuedBy
           ,@TaxId
           ,@TaxDate
           ,@TaxBy
           ,@UserName
           ,@BankNumber
           ,@BankName
           ,@BankBranch
           ,@Address
           ,@ContactAddress
           ,@NationalId
           ,@LinkFacebook
           ,@ImageLink
           ,@EmailCompany
           ,@PresentationContactName
           ,@PresentationContactPhone
           ,@Note
           ,@IsSendCheckList
           ,@SendCheckListDate
           ,@SendCheckListBy
           ,@IsDeleted
           ,@EthnicityId
           ,@MaritalStatus,@Id

		   
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Information_Update_SaveStaff_Information: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Information_Update_SaveStaff_Information', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch




GO

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
Create PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Relationships_Update_Staff_Relationships]
	@StaffId bigint
    ,@RelationshipId bigint
    ,@Name nvarchar(250)
    ,@BirthDay date
    ,@Phone nvarchar(250)
    ,@Status bigint
    ,@IsEmergency bit
    ,@Deduction bit
    ,@DeductionCode nvarchar(50)
    ,@DeductionFrom datetime
    ,@DeductionTo datetime
    ,@Note nvarchar(max)
    ,@CreatedDate datetime
    ,@CreatedBy bigint
    ,@UpdatedBy bigint
    ,@UpdatedDate datetime
    ,@IsDeleted bit
	,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
	,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT
as
 
	begin try
		declare	
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@Params					nvarchar(max)

		if @Id <= 0
			begin
			-- insert
				print (1);
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[RelationshipId]
           ,[Name]
           ,[BirthDay]
           ,[Phone]
           ,[Status]
           ,[IsEmergency]
           ,[Deduction]
           ,[DeductionCode]
           ,[DeductionFrom]
           ,[DeductionTo]
           ,[Note]
           ,[CreatedDate]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[IsDeleted])
     VALUES (@StaffId
           ,@RelationshipId
           ,@Name
           ,@BirthDay
           ,@Phone
           ,@Status
           ,@IsEmergency
           ,@Deduction
           ,@DeductionCode
           ,@DeductionFrom
           ,@DeductionTo
           ,@Note
           ,getdate()
           ,@CreatedBy
           ,@IsDeleted)
		
			'
	
			end
		else
			begin
				--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			update  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships]
           set
		   StaffId=  @StaffId
           ,RelationshipId    =@RelationshipId
           ,Name    =@Name
           ,BirthDay    =@BirthDay
           ,Phone    =@Phone
           ,Status    =@Status
           ,IsEmergency    =@IsEmergency
           ,Deduction    =@Deduction
           ,DeductionCode    =@DeductionCode
           ,DeductionFrom    =@DeductionFrom
           ,DeductionTo    =@DeductionTo
           ,Note    =@Note
           ,UpdatedDate    =getdate()
           ,UpdatedBy    =@CreatedBy
           ,IsDeleted    =@IsDeleted			
					where Id = @Id'
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '@StaffId bigint
				,@RelationshipId bigint
				,@Name nvarchar(250)
				,@BirthDay date
				,@Phone nvarchar(250)
				,@Status bigint
				,@IsEmergency bit
				,@Deduction bit
				,@DeductionCode nvarchar(50)
				,@DeductionFrom datetime
				,@DeductionTo datetime
				,@Note nvarchar(max)
				,@CreatedDate datetime
				,@CreatedBy bigint
				,@UpdatedBy bigint
				,@UpdatedDate datetime
				,@IsDeleted bit
				,@DbName				NVARCHAR(500)
				,@Id					BIGINT OUTPUT'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print (@SQL)
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, @StaffId
           ,@RelationshipId
           ,@Name
           ,@BirthDay
           ,@Phone
           ,@Status
           ,@IsEmergency
           ,@Deduction
           ,@DeductionCode
           ,@DeductionFrom
           ,@DeductionTo
           ,@Note
           ,@CreatedBy
           ,@IsDeleted,@DbName,@Id

		   
	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'Staff_Relationships_Update_Staff_Relationships: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@UId=' + convert(varchar, @Id)
		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Staff_Relationships_Update_Staff_Relationships', 'UPD', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveBonusDiscipline]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveBonusDiscipline]
		@Id				BIGINT,
		@StaffId		BIGINT,
		@TypeId			BIGINT,
		@GroupId		BIGINT,
		@DecisionNo		NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@Content		NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@ActionId		BIGINT,
		@Amount			decimal(18, 4),
		@CurrencyId		BIGINT,
		@SignDate		DATETIME,
		@ApplyDate		DATETIME,
		@Note			NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@Status			BIGINT,
		@PaySamePeriod	BIT,
		@BaseParam		BaseParamType READONLY
AS 
	BEGIN 
		DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy				VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber				INT = 1,
			@PageSize				INT = 9000000,
			@UserId					BIGINT = 1,
			@RoleId					BIGINT = 1,
			@DBName					NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId				INT = 1

		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END

		DECLARE	
			@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX)

		if ISNULL(@Id,0) <= 0
			begin
			-- insert
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[TypeId]
           ,[GroupId]
           ,[DecisionNo]
           ,[Content]
           ,[ActionId]
           ,[Amount]
           ,[CurrencyId]
           ,[SignDate]
           ,[ApplyDate]
           ,[Note]
           ,[CreatedDate]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[IsDeleted]
           ,[Status]
		   ,PaySamePeriod)
		 VALUES(
			@StaffId
           ,@TypeId
           ,@GroupId
           ,@DecisionNo
           ,@Content
           ,@ActionId
           ,@Amount
           ,@CurrencyId
           ,@SignDate
           ,@ApplyDate
           ,@Note
           ,GETDATE()
           ,@UserId
           ,0
           ,@Status
		   ,@PaySamePeriod
		  )
		
			SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline] WHERE Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
'
			END
		else
			begin
			--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		UPDATE [dbo].[Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline]
		   SET [StaffId]		= @StaffId	
			  ,[TypeId]			= @TypeId
			  ,[GroupId]		= @GroupId
			  ,[DecisionNo]		= @DecisionNo
			  ,[Content]		= @Content
			  ,[ActionId]		= @ActionId
			  ,[Amount]			= @Amount
			  ,[CurrencyId]		= @CurrencyId
			  ,[SignDate]		= @SignDate
			  ,[ApplyDate]		= @ApplyDate
			  ,[Note]			= @Note
			  ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId
			  ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
			  ,[Status]			= @Status
			  ,PaySamePeriod	= @PaySamePeriod
		 WHERE Id = @Id
	SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Bonus_Discipline] WHERE Id = @Id
'
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '	
					@Id				BIGINT,
					@StaffId		BIGINT,
					@TypeId			BIGINT,
					@GroupId		BIGINT,
					@DecisionNo		NVARCHAR(MAX),
					@Content		NVARCHAR(MAX),
					@ActionId		BIGINT,
					@Amount			decimal(18, 4),
					@CurrencyId		BIGINT,
					@SignDate		DATETIME,
					@ApplyDate		DATETIME,
					@Note			NVARCHAR(MAX),
					@Status			BIGINT,
					@PaySamePeriod	BIT,
					@BaseParam		BaseParamType READONLY,
					@UserId			BIGINT 
					'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print (@SQL)
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params
					,@Id			
					,@StaffId	
					,@TypeId		
					,@GroupId	
					,@DecisionNo	
					,@Content	
					,@ActionId	
					,@Amount		
					,@CurrencyId	
					,@SignDate	
					,@ApplyDate	
					,@Note		
					,@Status	
					,@PaySamePeriod	
					,@BaseParam	
					,@UserId

END

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveCertificate]
		@Id				BIGINT,

		@IssuedDate		DATETIME,
		@RankId			BIGINT,
		@IssuedBy		nvarchar(1000),
		@Point			decimal(18, 2),
		@Note			NVARCHAR(MAX),
		@BaseParam		BaseParamType READONLY
AS 
	BEGIN 
		DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy				VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber				INT = 1,
			@PageSize				INT = 9000000,
			@UserId					BIGINT = 1,
			@RoleId					BIGINT = 1,
			@DBName					NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',

		BEGIN

						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,

			)
		VALUES  ( @StaffId ,
				  @Name ,
				  @IssuedDate ,
				  @RankId ,
				  @IssuedBy ,
				  @Point ,
				  @Note ,
				  0)
		
			SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Certificate] WHERE Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

			END
		else

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveContract]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveContract]
	  @StaffId				BIGINT,
	  @ContractTypeId		BIGINT,
	  @ContractTime			BIGINT,
	  @ContractCode			NVARCHAR(250),
	  @ContractStartDate	DATETIME,
	  @ContractEndDate		DATETIME,
	  @ContractStatus		BIGINT,
	  @DbName				NVARCHAR(500),
	  @UserId				BIGINT,
	  @Id					BIGINT OUTPUT

AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE 
		@ExeQuery			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		,@params			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		,@ExeQueryList		NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''	
		 

		IF(ISNULL(@Id,0) = 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Contract
				(
						  StaffId,
						  ContractTypeId ,
						  ContractTime ,
						  ContractCode ,
						  ContractStartDate ,
						  ContractEndDate ,
						  ContractStatus ,
						  CreateBy ,
						  CreateDate
						)
				VALUES  (
						  @StaffId ,
						  @ContractTypeId , -- ContractTypeId - bigint
						  @ContractTime , -- ContractTime - bigint
						  @ContractCode , -- ContractCode - nvarchar(250)
						  @ContractStartDate , -- ContractStartDate - date
						  @ContractEndDate , -- ContractEndDate - date
						  @ContractStatus , -- ContractStatus - bigint
						  @UserId , -- CreateBy - bigint
						  GETDATE()  -- CreateDate - datetime
						)
						SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

				'
		END
			PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '	  @StaffId				BIGINT,
						  @ContractTypeId		BIGINT,
						  @ContractTime			BIGINT,
						  @ContractCode			NVARCHAR(250),
						  @ContractStartDate	DATETIME,
						  @ContractEndDate		DATETIME,
						  @ContractStatus		BIGINT ,
						  @UserId               BIGINT , 
						  @Id					BIGINT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId,@ContractTypeId,@ContractTime,@ContractCode,@ContractStartDate,@ContractEndDate,@ContractStatus, @UserId, @Id OUTPUT
END
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveSocialInsurance]

		@FamilyCode			NVARCHAR(MAX),

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveStaffChecklist]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveStaffChecklist]
	  @StaffId BIGINT,
      @CreatedBy BIGINT,
	  @UpdatedBy BIGINT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
	  @ChecklistDetailType ChecklistDetailType READONLY
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	
						 	
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	

	
INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[ChecklistDetailId]
           ,[Value]
           ,[Note]
           ,[IsFinish]
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[CreatedDate] 
           ,[IsDeleted]) 

		   select @StaffId,id,Value,Note,IsFinished,CreatedBy=@CreatedBy,CreatedDate=getdate(),IsDeleted=0
		   from @ChecklistDetailType a where not exists (select id from Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail bb where bb.staffid=@StaffId and bb.ChecklistDetailId=a.id)

				UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail SET Value=a.Value,IsFinish=a.IsFinished,UpdatedBy=@UpdatedBy,UpdatedDate=GETDATE()   		
				from @ChecklistDetailType a inner join Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail b on a.[Id]=b.ChecklistDetailId 
				where StaffId=@StaffId 	
				  

					DECLARE @strSQL NVARCHAR(Max),@value nvarchar(2000),@param1s NVARCHAR(Max)


					DECLARE CursorChecklistDetail CURSOR FOR
					SELECT  strSQL=''USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']'  + ' update '' + tb.SqlTableName + '' set '' + a.ColumnName +'' =@Value where id='' + cast(b.staffid as varchar) ,b.value  
					FROM Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail b 
					inner join Data_ChecklistDetail cd on cd.Id=b.ChecklistDetailId
					inner join dbo.System_Table_Column a on cd.ColumnLink=a.Id
					inner join System_Table tb on a.TableId=tb.Id
					WHERE StaffId=' + cast(@StaffId as varchar) +'  and b.IsDeleted=0 and cd.[TypeControlId]=276 and b.Value is not null 
 

					OPEN CursorChecklistDetail

					FETCH NEXT FROM CursorChecklistDetail
						INTO @strSQL,@value

					WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
						BEGIN	
						print (@strSQL)
						SET @param1s =''@Value  nvarchar(2000)''
						EXEC sp_executesql @strSQL,@param1s,@Value
						FETCH NEXT FROM CursorChecklistDetail
								INTO @strSQL,@value				
						END
					CLOSE CursorChecklistDetail
					DEALLOCATE CursorChecklistDetail	
			 
					
			'
			print (@ExeQuery)
		SET @params ='@StaffId BIGINT,@CreatedBy BIGINT,@UpdatedBy BIGINT,@ChecklistDetailType ChecklistDetailType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@StaffId,@CreatedBy,@UpdatedBy,@ChecklistDetailType

	
END

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveStaffFull]
		@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
		@WorkingPorcess Data_Staff_WorkingProcessType READONLY,
		@Staff Data_Staff_InformationType READONLY,
		@Role Data_StaffRoleType READONLY,
		@Contract Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
		@StaffWorkingDayMachine Data_Staff_WorkingDay_MachineType READONLY,
		@StaffRelatioship Data_Staff_RelationshipType READONLY,
		@StaffOnboardInfo StaffOnboardInfoType READONLY
AS 
	BEGIN 
		DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy				VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber				INT = 1,
			@PageSize				INT = 9000000,
			@UserId					BIGINT = 1,
			@RoleId					BIGINT = 1,
			@DBName					NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId				INT = 1
		DECLARE 
			@IsOnboarding BIT = 0,
			@PipelineId BIGINT = 0,
			@PipelineStepId BIGINT = 0,
			@OnboardingDate	DATETIME = NULL
		
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @StaffOnboardInfo)
		BEGIN
			SELECT
				 @IsOnboarding		= IsOnboarding 
				,@PipelineId		= PipelineId 
				,@PipelineStepId	= PipelineStepId 
				,@OnboardingDate	= OnboardingDate 
			FROM @StaffOnboardInfo
		END

		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END

		DECLARE	
			@StaffId				BIGINT,
			@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SELECT @StaffId = Id FROM @Staff
		if ISNULL(@StaffId,0) <= 0
			begin
			-- insert
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
DECLARE @WPId BIGINT
DECLARE @ContractId BIGINT
INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information]
	   ([StaffCode]
	   ,[Name]
	   ,[Birthday]
	   ,[GenderId]
	   --,[CurrentWorkingProcessId]
	   ,[Email]
	   ,[Phone]
	   ,[PhoneCompany]
	   ,[Skype]
	   ,[IdentityNumber]
	   ,[IdIssuedDate]
	   ,[IdIssuedBy]
	   ,[TaxId]
	   ,[TaxDate]
	   ,[TaxBy]
	   ,[UserName]
	   ,[BankNumber]
	   ,[BankName]
	   ,[BankBranch]
	   ,[Address]
	   ,[ContactAddress]
	   ,[NationalId]
	   ,[LinkFacebook]
	   ,[ImageLink]
	   ,[EmailCompany]
	   ,[PresentationContactName]
	   ,[PresentationContactPhone]
	   ,[Note]
	   --,[IsSendCheckList]
	   --,[SendCheckListDate]
	   --,[SendCheckListBy]
	   ,[IsDeleted]
	   ,[EthnicityId]
	   ,[MaritalStatus]
	   ,[IsActivated]
	   ,[TimeLateLimit]
	   ,[TimeLeaveEarlyLimit]
	   ,[TimekeepingForm]
	   ,[HRAdditionId]
	   ,[AdditionManagerId]

	   ,[ProvinceId]
	   ,[Domicile]
	   ,[ProvinceDomicile]
	   ,[NationalDomicile]
	   ,[CurrencyId]
	   --,[Status]
	   --,[Password]
	   )
 SELECT [StaffCode]
	   ,[Name]
	   ,[Birthday]
	   ,[GenderId]
	   --,[CurrentWorkingProcessId]
	   ,[Email]
	   ,[Phone]
	   ,[PhoneCompany]
	   ,[Skype]
	   ,[IdentityNumber]
	   ,[IdIssuedDate]
	   ,[IdIssuedBy]
	   ,[TaxId]
	   ,[TaxDate]
	   ,[TaxBy]
	   ,[UserName]
	   ,[BankNumber]
	   ,[BankName]
	   ,[BankBranch]
	   ,[Address]
	   ,[ContactAddress]
	   ,[NationalId]
	   ,[LinkFacebook]
	   ,[ImageLink]
	   ,[EmailCompany]
	   ,[PresentationContactName]
	   ,[PresentationContactPhone]
	   ,[Note]
	   --,[IsSendCheckList]
	   --,[SendCheckListDate]
	   --,[SendCheckListBy]
	   ,0
	   ,[EthnicityId]
	   ,[MaritalStatus]
	   ,[IsActivated]
	   ,[TimeLateLimit]
	   ,[TimeLeaveEarlyLimit]
	   ,[TimekeepingForm]
	   ,[HRAdditionId]
	   ,[AdditionManagerId]
	   ,[ProvinceId]
	   ,[Domicile]
	   ,[ProvinceDomicile]
	   ,[NationalDomicile]
	   ,[CurrencyId]
	   --,[Status]
	   --,[Password]
 FROM @Staff
SET @StaffId = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT Id FROM Data_User WHERE StaffId=@StaffId) AND @StaffId > 0
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_User]
		   ([Id]
		   ,[StaffId]
		   ,[UserName]
		   ,[DisplayName]
		   ,[Password]
		   ,[Status]
		   ,[IsActivate]
		   ,[CreatedDate]
		   ,[CreatedBy]
		   ,[IsDeleted]
		   ,[LanguageId])
	 SELECT @StaffId
		   ,@StaffId
		   ,[UserName]
		   ,[Name]
		   ,[Password]
		   ,8
		   ,[IsActivated]
		   ,GETDATE()
		   ,@UserId
		   ,0
		   ,1
	FROM @Staff
END

IF(@StaffId > 0)
BEGIN
	IF(@IsOnboarding = 1)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_BoardingProcess]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[OnboardingDate]
           ,[IsDeleted])
		VALUES
           (@StaffId
		   ,@OnboardingDate
		   ,0)

		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_PipelineStatus]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[PipelineId]
           ,[PipelineStepId]
           ,[Date]
           ,[Note]
           ,[IsDeleted])
		SELECT 
			@StaffId
		   ,@PipelineId
           ,[PM].[PipelineStepId]
           ,IIF(PT.Id =@PipelineStepId, @OnboardingDate, NULL)
           ,NULL
		   ,0
		FROM dbo.Data_PipelineStep PT
		INNER JOIN dbo.Data_PipelineMapper PM ON PT.Id = PM.PipelineStepId
		WHERE PM.PipelineId = @PipelineId
	END
	INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess]
		   ([StaffId]
		   ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]
		   ,[DecisionNo]
		   ,[WorkingStatus]
		   ,[DecisionDate]
		   ,[StartDate]
		   ,[EndDate]
		   ,[ContractId]
		   ,[OrganizationId]
		   ,[OfficeId]
		   ,[PositionId]
		   ,[ClassificationId]
		   ,[StaffLevelId]
		   ,[ManagerId]
		   ,[HRManagerId]
		   ,[PolicyId]
		   ,[BasicPay]
		   ,[EfficiencyBonus]
		   ,[PaymentForm]
		   ,[PaymentMethod]
		   ,[SalaryNote]
		   ,[Description]
		   ,[Note]
		   ,[IsDeleted]
		   ,[Status]
		   ,[ShiftId]
		   ,[CreatedDate]
		   ,[CreatedBy])

SELECT		@StaffId
		   ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]
		   ,[DecisionNo]
		   ,[WorkingStatus]
		   ,[DecisionDate]
		   ,[StartDate]
		   ,[EndDate]
		   ,[ContractId]
		   ,[OrganizationId]
		   ,[OfficeId]
		   ,[PositionId]
		   ,[ClassificationId]
		   ,[StaffLevelId]
		   ,[ManagerId]
		   ,[HRManagerId]
		   ,[PolicyId]
		   ,[BasicPay]
		   ,[EfficiencyBonus]
		   ,[PaymentForm]
		   ,[PaymentMethod]
		   ,[SalaryNote]
		   ,[Description]
		   ,[Note]
		   ,0
		   ,[Status]
		   ,[ShiftId]
		   ,GETDATE()
		   ,@UserId
	FROM @WorkingPorcess
	SET @WPId = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
	UPDATE [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] SET CurrentWorkingProcessId = @WPId WHERE Id = @StaffId
END
IF(ISNULL(@WPId,0) >0)
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Contract
	   ( StaffId ,
		 ContractTypeId ,
		 ContractTime ,
		 ContractCode ,
		 Name ,
		 ContractStartDate ,
		 ContractEndDate ,
		 ContractNote ,
		 ContractStatus ,
		 CreateBy ,
		 CreateDate ,
		 ModifiedBy ,
		 ModifiedDate
	   )
	SELECT 
		@StaffId ,
		ContractTypeId ,
		ContractTime ,
		ContractCode ,
		Name ,
		ContractStartDate ,
		ContractEndDate ,
		ContractNote ,
		ContractStatus ,
		CreateBy ,
		CreateDate ,
		ModifiedBy ,
		ModifiedDate
	FROM @Contract
	SET @ContractId = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
	UPDATE [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess] SET ContractId = @ContractId WHERE Id = @WPId
END
IF(ISNULL(@StaffId,0)>0)
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO dbo.Data_StaffRole
	(	RoleId ,
		StaffId ,
		Description ,
		IsDeleted
	)
	SELECT 
		RoleId ,
		@StaffId ,
		Description ,
		0
	FROM  @Role
END
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Relationships
        ( StaffId ,
          RelationshipId ,
          Name ,
          BirthDay ,
          Phone ,
          Status ,
          IsEmergency ,
          Deduction ,
          DeductionCode ,
          DeductionFrom ,
          DeductionTo ,
          Note ,
          CreatedDate ,
          CreatedBy ,
          IsDeleted
        )
SELECT @StaffId ,
          RelationshipId ,
          Name ,
          BirthDay ,
          Phone ,
          Status ,
          IsEmergency ,
          Deduction ,
          DeductionCode ,
          DeductionFrom ,
          DeductionTo ,
          Note ,
          GETDATE() ,
          @UserId ,
          0
FROM @StaffRelatioship 
WHERE Id = 0 AND ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0
INSERT INTO Hrm_System.[dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingDay_Machine]
	([StaffId]
	,[WorkingDayMachineId]
	,[SSN]
	,[Note]
	,[CreatedBy]
	,[CreatedDate]
	,[IsDeleted])
SELECT @StaffId
	,[WorkingDayMachineId]
	,[SSN]
	,[Note]
	,@UserId
	,GETDATE()
	,0
FROM @StaffWorkingDayMachine
WHERE Id = 0 AND ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0

SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] WHERE Id = @StaffId
'
			end
		else
			begin
			--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

				UPDATE s
				   SET s.[StaffCode]				= tmp.[StaffCode]					
					  ,s.[Name]						= tmp.[Name]						
					  ,s.[Birthday]					= tmp.[Birthday]					
					  ,s.[GenderId]					= tmp.[GenderId]					
					  ,s.[CurrentWorkingProcessId]	= tmp.[CurrentWorkingProcessId]	
					  ,s.[Email]					= tmp.[Email]						
					  ,s.[Phone]					= tmp.[Phone]						
					  ,s.[PhoneCompany]				= tmp.[PhoneCompany]				
					  ,s.[Skype]					= tmp.[Skype]						
					  ,s.[IdentityNumber]			= tmp.[IdentityNumber]				
					  ,s.[IdIssuedDate]				= tmp.[IdIssuedDate]				
					  ,s.[IdIssuedBy]				= tmp.[IdIssuedBy]					
					  ,s.[TaxId]					= tmp.[TaxId]						
					  ,s.[TaxDate]					= tmp.[TaxDate]					
					  ,s.[TaxBy]					= tmp.[TaxBy]						
					  ,s.[UserName]					= tmp.[UserName]					
					  ,s.[BankNumber]				= tmp.[BankNumber]					
					  ,s.[BankName]					= tmp.[BankName]					
					  ,s.[BankBranch]				= tmp.[BankBranch]					
					  ,s.[Address]					= tmp.[Address]					
					  ,s.[ContactAddress]			= tmp.[ContactAddress]				
					  ,s.[NationalId]				= tmp.[NationalId]					
					  ,s.[LinkFacebook]				= tmp.[LinkFacebook]				
					  ,s.[ImageLink]				= tmp.[ImageLink]					
					  ,s.[EmailCompany]				= tmp.[EmailCompany]				
					  ,s.[PresentationContactName]	= tmp.[PresentationContactName]	
					  ,s.[PresentationContactPhone]	= tmp.[PresentationContactPhone]	
					  ,s.[Note]						= tmp.[Note]						
					  ,s.[IsSendCheckList]			= tmp.[IsSendCheckList]			
					  ,s.[SendCheckListDate]		= tmp.[SendCheckListDate]			
					  ,s.[SendCheckListBy]			= tmp.[SendCheckListBy]			
					  ,s.[IsDeleted]				= tmp.[IsDeleted]					
					  ,s.[EthnicityId]				= tmp.[EthnicityId]				
					  ,s.[MaritalStatus]			= tmp.[MaritalStatus]				
					  ,s.[IsActivated]				= tmp.[IsActivated]				
				FROM  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] s
				INNER JOIN  @Staff tmp ON tmp.Id = s.Id
				WHERE s.Id = @StaffId 

				SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] WHERE Id = @StaffId '
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '	
							@Staff Data_Staff_InformationType READONLY,
							@WorkingPorcess Data_Staff_WorkingProcessType READONLY,
							@Role Data_StaffRoleType READONLY,
							@Contract Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
							@StaffWorkingDayMachine Data_Staff_WorkingDay_MachineType READONLY,
							@StaffRelatioship Data_Staff_RelationshipType READONLY,
							@UserId					BIGINT,
							@StaffId BIGINT ,
							@IsOnboarding BIT = 0,
							@PipelineId BIGINT = 0,
							@PipelineStepId BIGINT = 0,
							@OnboardingDate	DATETIME = NULL'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print (@SQL)
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params,@Staff,@WorkingPorcess,@Role, @Contract,@StaffWorkingDayMachine,@StaffRelatioship, @UserId, @StaffId, @IsOnboarding, @PipelineId, @PipelineStepId, @OnboardingDate

END

	,0
FROM @StaffWorkingDayMachine
WHERE Id = 0 AND ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0

SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] WHERE Id = @StaffId
'
			end
		else
			begin
			--Update
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

				UPDATE s
				   SET s.[StaffCode]				= tmp.[StaffCode]					
					  ,s.[Name]						= tmp.[Name]						
					  ,s.[Birthday]					= tmp.[Birthday]					
					  ,s.[GenderId]					= tmp.[GenderId]					
					  ,s.[CurrentWorkingProcessId]	= tmp.[CurrentWorkingProcessId]	
					  ,s.[Email]					= tmp.[Email]						
					  ,s.[Phone]					= tmp.[Phone]						
					  ,s.[PhoneCompany]				= tmp.[PhoneCompany]				
					  ,s.[Skype]					= tmp.[Skype]						
					  ,s.[IdentityNumber]			= tmp.[IdentityNumber]				
					  ,s.[IdIssuedDate]				= tmp.[IdIssuedDate]				
					  ,s.[IdIssuedBy]				= tmp.[IdIssuedBy]					
					  ,s.[TaxId]					= tmp.[TaxId]						
					  ,s.[TaxDate]					= tmp.[TaxDate]					
					  ,s.[TaxBy]					= tmp.[TaxBy]						
					  ,s.[UserName]					= tmp.[UserName]					
					  ,s.[BankNumber]				= tmp.[BankNumber]					
					  ,s.[BankName]					= tmp.[BankName]					
					  ,s.[BankBranch]				= tmp.[BankBranch]					
					  ,s.[Address]					= tmp.[Address]					
					  ,s.[ContactAddress]			= tmp.[ContactAddress]				
					  ,s.[NationalId]				= tmp.[NationalId]					
					  ,s.[LinkFacebook]				= tmp.[LinkFacebook]				
					  ,s.[ImageLink]				= tmp.[ImageLink]					
					  ,s.[EmailCompany]				= tmp.[EmailCompany]				
					  ,s.[PresentationContactName]	= tmp.[PresentationContactName]	
					  ,s.[PresentationContactPhone]	= tmp.[PresentationContactPhone]	
					  ,s.[Note]						= tmp.[Note]						
					  ,s.[IsSendCheckList]			= tmp.[IsSendCheckList]			
					  ,s.[SendCheckListDate]		= tmp.[SendCheckListDate]			
					  ,s.[SendCheckListBy]			= tmp.[SendCheckListBy]			
					  ,s.[IsDeleted]				= tmp.[IsDeleted]					
					  ,s.[EthnicityId]				= tmp.[EthnicityId]				
					  ,s.[MaritalStatus]			= tmp.[MaritalStatus]				
					  ,s.[IsActivated]				= tmp.[IsActivated]				
				FROM  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] s
				INNER JOIN  @Staff tmp ON tmp.Id = s.Id
				WHERE s.Id = @StaffId 

				SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] WHERE Id = @StaffId '
			end
			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '	
							@Staff Data_Staff_InformationType READONLY,
							@WorkingPorcess Data_Staff_WorkingProcessType READONLY,
							@Role Data_StaffRoleType READONLY,
							@Contract Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
							@StaffWorkingDayMachine Data_Staff_WorkingDay_MachineType READONLY,
							@StaffRelatioship Data_Staff_RelationshipType READONLY,
							@UserId					BIGINT,
							@StaffId BIGINT ,
							@IsOnboarding BIT = 0,
							@PipelineId BIGINT = 0,
							@PipelineStepId BIGINT = 0,
							@OnboardingDate	DATETIME = NULL'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print (@SQL)
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params,@Staff,@WorkingPorcess,@Role, @Contract,@StaffWorkingDayMachine,@StaffRelatioship, @UserId, @StaffId, @IsOnboarding, @PipelineId, @PipelineStepId, @OnboardingDate

END



GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveStaffInformation]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SaveStaffInformation]
		@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
		@Staff Data_Staff_InformationType READONLY,
		@StaffRelatioship Data_Staff_RelationshipType READONLY,
		@StaffWorkingDayMachine Data_Staff_WorkingDay_MachineType READONLY,
		@Role Data_StaffRoleType READONLY
AS 
	BEGIN 
		DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy				VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber				INT = 1,
			@PageSize				INT = 9000000,
			@UserId					BIGINT = 1,
			@RoleId					BIGINT = 1,
			@DBName					NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId				INT = 1

		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END

		DECLARE	
			@StaffId				BIGINT,
			@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
			@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SELECT @StaffId = Id FROM @Staff
		PRINT @StaffId
		if ISNULL(@StaffId,0) > 0
			begin
			-- insert
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
UPDATE S
   SET [StaffCode]					= data.[StaffCode]					
      ,[Name]						= data.[Name]						
      ,[Birthday]					= data.[Birthday]					
      ,[GenderId]					= data.[GenderId]					
      ,[Email]						= data.[Email]						
      ,[Phone]						= data.[Phone]						
      ,[PhoneCompany]				= data.[PhoneCompany]				
      ,[Skype]						= data.[Skype]						
      ,[IdentityNumber]				= data.[IdentityNumber]				
      ,[IdIssuedDate]				= data.[IdIssuedDate]				
      ,[IdIssuedBy]					= data.[IdIssuedBy]					
      ,[TaxId]						= data.[TaxId]						
      ,[TaxDate]					= data.[TaxDate]					
      ,[TaxBy]						= data.[TaxBy]						
      ,[UserName]					= data.[UserName]					
      ,[BankNumber]					= data.[BankNumber]					
      ,[BankName]					= data.[BankName]					
      ,[BankBranch]					= data.[BankBranch]					
      ,[Address]					= data.[Address]					
      ,[ContactAddress]				= data.[ContactAddress]				
      ,[NationalId]					= data.[NationalId]					
      ,[ProvinceId]					= data.[ProvinceId]					
      ,[Domicile]					= data.[Domicile]					
      ,[ProvinceDomicile]			= data.[ProvinceDomicile]			
      ,[NationalDomicile]			= data.[NationalDomicile]			
      ,[LinkFacebook]				= data.[LinkFacebook]				
      ,[ImageLink]					= data.[ImageLink]					
      ,[EmailCompany]				= data.[EmailCompany]				
      ,[PresentationContactName]	= data.[PresentationContactName]	
      ,[PresentationContactPhone]	= data.[PresentationContactPhone]	
      ,[Note]						= data.[Note]						
      --,[IsSendCheckList]			= data.[IsSendCheckList]			
      --,[SendCheckListDate]		= data.[SendCheckListDate]			
      --,[SendCheckListBy]			= data.[SendCheckListBy]			
      ,[TimeLateLimit]				= data.[TimeLateLimit]				
      ,[TimeLeaveEarlyLimit]		= data.[TimeLeaveEarlyLimit]		
      ,[TimekeepingForm]			= data.[TimekeepingForm]			
      ,[HRAdditionId]				= data.[HRAdditionId]				
      ,[AdditionManagerId]			= data.[AdditionManagerId]			
      --,[IsDeleted]					= data.[IsDeleted]					
      ,[EthnicityId]				= data.[EthnicityId]				
      ,[MaritalStatus]				= data.[MaritalStatus]				
      ,[CurrencyId]					= data.[CurrencyId]				
      ,[IsActivated]				= data.[IsActivated]				

FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] S 
JOIN @Staff data ON s.Id = data.Id
WHERE S.Id = @StaffId

UPDATE R
   SET [RoleId]			= data.[RoleId]		
      ,[StaffId]		= data.[StaffId]	
      ,[Description]	= data.[Description]
FROM dbo.Data_StaffRole R 
INNER JOIN @Role data ON R.StaffId = data.StaffId
WHERE r.StaffId = @StaffId

UPDATE SR
   SET 
       SR.[RelationshipId]	= TMP.RelationshipId
      ,SR.[Name]			= TMP.Name
      ,SR.[BirthDay]		= TMP.BirthDay
      ,SR.[Phone]			= TMP.Phone
      ,SR.[Status]			= TMP.Status
      ,SR.[IsEmergency]		= TMP.IsEmergency
      ,SR.[Deduction]		= TMP.Deduction
      ,SR.[DeductionCode]	= TMP.DeductionCode
      ,SR.[DeductionFrom]	= TMP.DeductionFrom
      ,SR.[DeductionTo]		= TMP.DeductionTo
      ,SR.[Note]			= TMP.Note
      ,SR.[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId
      ,SR.[UpdatedDate]		= GETDATE()
      ,SR.[IsDeleted]		= TMP.IsDeleted
FROM Data_Staff_Relationships SR
INNER JOIN @StaffRelatioship TMP ON SR.Id = TMP.Id
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Relationships
        ( StaffId ,
          RelationshipId ,
          Name ,
          BirthDay ,
          Phone ,
          Status ,
          IsEmergency ,
          Deduction ,
          DeductionCode ,
          DeductionFrom ,
          DeductionTo ,
          Note ,
          CreatedDate ,
          CreatedBy ,
          IsDeleted
        )
SELECT @StaffId ,
          RelationshipId ,
          Name ,
          BirthDay ,
          Phone ,
          Status ,
          IsEmergency ,
          Deduction ,
          DeductionCode ,
          DeductionFrom ,
          DeductionTo ,
          Note ,
          GETDATE() ,
          @UserId ,
          0
FROM @StaffRelatioship 
WHERE Id = 0 AND ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0

INSERT INTO Hrm_System.[dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingDay_Machine]
	([StaffId]
	,[WorkingDayMachineId]
	,[SSN]
	,[Note]
	,[CreatedBy]
	,[CreatedDate]
	,[IsDeleted])
SELECT @StaffId
	,[WorkingDayMachineId]
	,[SSN]
	,[Note]
	,@UserId
	,GETDATE()
	,0
FROM @StaffWorkingDayMachine
WHERE Id = 0 AND ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0
UPDATE M
   SET M.[StaffId]		= @StaffId
      ,M.[WorkingDayMachineId] = TMP.[WorkingDayMachineId]
      ,M.[SSN]			= TMP.[SSN]		
      ,M.[Note]			= TMP.[Note]		
      ,M.[UpdatedBy]	= @UserId	
      ,M.[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,M.[IsDeleted]		= TMP.[IsDeleted]	
FROM [Data_Staff_WorkingDay_Machine] M
INNER JOIN @StaffWorkingDayMachine TMP ON M.Id = TMP.Id
SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] WHERE Id = @StaffId
'
			END

			-- set full param
			SET @Params = '	
							@Staff Data_Staff_InformationType READONLY,
							@StaffRelatioship Data_Staff_RelationshipType READONLY,
							@StaffWorkingDayMachine Data_Staff_WorkingDay_MachineType READONLY,
							@Role Data_StaffRoleType READONLY,
							@UserId					BIGINT,
							@StaffId BIGINT  '
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print (@SQL)
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params,@Staff, @StaffRelatioship, @StaffWorkingDayMachine,@Role, @UserId, @StaffId

END



GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Staff_Update_SendStaffChecklist]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Staff_Update_SendStaffChecklist]
	  @StaffId BIGINT,
	  @UserId BIGINT,
	  @ChecklistId BIGINT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500)
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	
						 	
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
	IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail WHERE StaffId = @StaffId) = 0)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail]
           ([StaffId]
           ,[ChecklistDetailId]
		   ,IsFinish
           ,[CreatedBy]
           ,[CreatedDate] 
           ,[IsDeleted]) 	
	SELECT @StaffId, CD.Id, 0, @UserId, GETDATE(), 0 
	FROM Data_ChecklistDetail CD
	WHERE CD.ChecklistId = @ChecklistId
	END
	IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Staff_BoardingProcess WHERE StaffId = @StaffId) > 0)
	BEGIN
	UPDATE dbo.Data_Staff_BoardingProcess 
	SET IsSendChecklist = 1, CurrentChecklistId = @ChecklistId, SendChecklistBy = @UserId, SendChecklistDate = GETDATE()
	WHERE StaffId = @StaffId
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
	INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_BoardingProcess(StaffId,IsSendChecklist, CurrentChecklistId, SendChecklistBy, SendChecklistDate)
	VALUES(@StaffId, 1, @ChecklistId, @UserId, GETDATE())
	END
	SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_ChecklistDetail WHERE StaffId = @StaffId
	'
		SET @params ='@StaffId BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT,  @ChecklistId BIGINT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@StaffId,@UserId, @ChecklistId

	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[StaffRelationShips_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[StaffRelationShips_Get_GetRelationShipsByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord	INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY r.id) AS Id
			  ,r.[StaffId]
			  ,r.[RelationshipId]
			  ,r.[Name]
			  ,r.[BirthDay]
			  ,r.[Phone]
			  ,r.[Status]
			  ,r.[IsEmergency]
			  ,r.[Deduction]
			  ,r.[DeductionCode]
			  ,r.[DeductionFrom]
			  ,r.[DeductionTo]
			  ,r.[Note]
			  ,r.[CreatedDate]
			  ,r.[CreatedBy]
			  ,r.[UpdatedBy]
			  ,r.[UpdatedDate]
			  ,r.[IsDeleted]
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Relationships] r '
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE r.IsDeleted = 0 and r.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy + 
	  ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(r.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE r.IsDeleted = 0 and r.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'StaffRelationShips_Get_GetRelationShipsStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'StaffRelationShips_Get_GetRelationShipsStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Del_DeleteMasterData]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Del_DeleteMasterData]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DataType			VARCHAR(500),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						IF((SELECT IsDisbleEditing FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE Id=@Id)=0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT IsDisbleEditing FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE Id=@Id
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							DELETE FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE Id=@Id
							DELETE FROM dbo.Data_LocalizedData WHERE DataId=@Id and DataType=@DataType
							
						END

								
					'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT,@DataType	VARCHAR(500)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id,@DataType	

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Full_Authentication]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Full_Authentication]
	@UserName				VARCHAR(500),
	@PassWord				VARCHAR(500) ,
	@DbName					VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN

	--SELECT * FROM dbo.[System_User] WHERE UserName=@UserName AND Password=@PassWord

	--DECLARE @SQL NVARCHAR(500)

	--SET @SQL = N'(SELECT * FROM ' +'[' + @DbName+']' + '.dbo.Sec_User where UserName=' + '''' + CAST(@UserName AS NVARCHAR)+ '''' + ' and Password='+  '''' + CAST(@PassWord AS NVARCHAR) + ''')' 
	--SET @SQL=@SQL+ 'exec sp_executesql @SQL'

	--PRINT @SQL

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT u.[Id]
			  ,u.[StaffId] as UserId
			  ,u.[UserName]
			  ,u.[DisplayName]
			  ,u.[Password]
			  ,u.[UserType]
			  ,u.[Status]
			  ,u.[LanguageId]
			  ,u.[IsActivate]
			  ,u.[IsLocked]
			  ,u.[LockedDate]
			  ,u.[LockedBy]
			  ,u.[ForgotCode]
			  ,u.[ForgotExpired]
			  ,u.[CreatedDate]
			  ,u.[CreatedBy]
			  ,u.[UpdatedDate]
			  ,u.[UpdatedBy]
			  ,u.[IsDeleted] 
			  ,SI.[CurrencyId] 
			  ,DSR.RoleId
			  FROM dbo.[Data_User] u 
			  LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_StaffRole DSR on DSR.StaffId=u.StaffId
			  LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI on SI.Id=u.StaffId
			  where u.UserName=' + '''' + CAST(@UserName AS VARCHAR)+ '''' + ' and u.Password='+  '''' + @PassWord + '''

		'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Full_GetColumnValidationByTable]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Full_GetColumnValidationByTable]
	@TableName					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT 
							DCV.*,
							STC.ColumnName
						FROM dbo.Data_Column_Validation DCV
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Table_Column STC ON STC.Id = DCV.ColumnId
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Table ST ON ST.Id = STC.TableId
						WHERE ST.TableName = @TableName
					'
	SET @params = '@TableName NVARCHAR(MAX)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @TableName

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Full_GetLanguage]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Full_GetLanguage]
	@DbName				NVARCHAR(MAX)
as
 
BEGIN	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT Id, Name, LanguageCulture, ImageName FROM System_Language ORDER BY DisplayOrder
		'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery
END
