/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Full_GetPermission]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Full_GetPermission]
	@StaffId				BIGINT,
	@DbName					VARCHAR(500)
AS 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
				SM.MenuName,
				DP.PermissionName	 
			FROM  dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission DSRP
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Menu_Permission DMP ON DMP.Id = DSRP.MenuPermissionId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DMP.MenuId
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Permission DP ON DP.Id = DMP.PermissionId
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP ON DSP.StaffId = DSRP.DataId AND DSP.ParentId = @StaffId
			WHERE DSRP.IsDeleted = 0 AND DSRP.DataTypeId = 269
			UNION
			
			SELECT 
				SM.MenuName,
				DP.PermissionName	 
			FROM  dbo.Data_Staff_Role_Permission DSRP
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Menu_Permission DMP ON DMP.Id = DSRP.MenuPermissionId
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Menu SM ON SM.Id = DMP.MenuId
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Permission DP ON DP.Id = DMP.PermissionId
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_StaffRole DSR ON DSR.RoleId = DSRP.DataId AND DSR.StaffId = @StaffId
			WHERE DSRP.IsDeleted = 0 AND DSRP.DataTypeId = 270
		'
	SET @params = '@StaffId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @StaffId

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Full_GetResources]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Full_GetResources]
	@LanguageId				BIGINT,
	@DbName				NVARCHAR(MAX)
as
 
BEGIN	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			IF @LanguageId = 0 SET @LanguageId = 1
			SELECT DISTINCT ResourceName, ResourceValue FROM System_LocaleStringResource WHERE LanguageId = @LanguageId
		'
	SET @params = N'@LanguageId BIGINT';
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @LanguageId
END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetAllMasterData]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[System_Get_GetAllMasterData]
	@FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
	@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
	@PageNumber			INT = 1,
	@PageSize			INT = 20,
	@GroupId			INT,
	@LanguageCode		INT,
	@DBName				NVARCHAR(50),
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @StartIndex BIGINT, @EndIndex BIGINT, @cSql NVARCHAR(MAX), @cBeginSql NVARCHAR(MAX), @cSqlFrom NVARCHAR(MAX), @WhereSQL NVARCHAR(MAX),@vcWhereStatus NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @Delim	nvarchar(100)
	DECLARE @dynamicparamdec NVARCHAR(2000)

	SELECT @PageNumber = ISNULL(@PageNumber, 1), @PageSize = ISNULL(@PageSize, 50)
	SELECT @StartIndex = ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
	SELECT @EndIndex = @PageNumber * @PageSize

	IF(@FilterField<>'')
	BEGIN
		SET @FilterField= @FilterField + ' and  GroupId<>0'
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		IF(@GroupId=0)
		BEGIN
			SET @FilterField= 'GroupId=0'
        END 
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @FilterField= 'GroupId = '+CAST(@GroupId AS NVARCHAR)
        END 
    END		
	 
	SET @cSqlFrom = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'SELECT 
													SMD.Id,
													SMD.Name,
													SMD.Description,
													SMD.Value,
													SMD.Color,
													SMD.GroupId,
													SMD.OrderNo
													FROM dbo.System_MasterData SMD														
												'
	DECLARE @CountSql NVARCHAR(MAX) =N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(SMD.Id) FROM dbo.System_MasterData  SMD'

	SELECT @cSql = @cSqlFrom  + iif(@FilterField != '',ISNULL(+ ' ' +'WHERE ' + @FilterField, ''),'') + ' order by Id desc  '+ ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
	print (@cSql)
	exec(@cSql )
		SELECT  @cSql = ''
	SELECT @cSql =   @CountSql +' '+iif(@FilterField != '',ISNULL('WHERE ' + @FilterField, ''),'')
	print (@cSql)
	SET @dynamicparamdec = N'@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT,@GroupId INT, @LanguageCode INT'
	exec sp_executesql @cSql, @dynamicparamdec, @TotalRecord OUTPUT,@GroupId,@LanguageCode
	
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetAllMasterDataByGroupId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetAllMasterDataByGroupId]
	@ListId LongType READONLY,
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				SELECT 
					M.*
				FROM dbo.System_MasterData M 
				INNER JOIN @ListId LN ON M.GroupId = LN.Value
				WHERE ISNULL(M.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
				ORDER BY ISNULL(M.OrderNo,10000) ASC
			'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@ListId LongType READONLY'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @ListId
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetAllMasterDataByGroupName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetAllMasterDataByGroupName]
	@ListName StringType READONLY,
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				SELECT 
					M.*, 
					Mm.Name as GroupName 
				FROM dbo.System_MasterData M 
				INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData Mm ON M.GroupId = Mm.Id
				INNER JOIN @ListName LN ON LN.Value = Mm.Name 
				WHERE ISNULL(M.IsDeleted,0) = 0 
				ORDER BY M.OrderNo ASC
			'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@ListName StringType READONLY'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @ListName
END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetColumnByTableName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetColumnByTableName]
	@TableName			NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT 
							STC.ColumnName
						FROM dbo.System_Table_Column STC
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Table ST ON ST.Id = STC.TableId AND ST.TableName = @TableName
						WHERE STC.IsDeleted=0 AND ST.IsDeleted = 0
						ORDER BY STC.OrderNo
					'
	SET @params = '@TableName NVARCHAR(MAX)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @TableName

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetMasterDataByGroupId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetMasterDataByGroupId]
	@GroupId					BIGINT ,
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	IF(@GroupId=0)
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				SELECT 
					SMD.Id,
					SMD.Name,
					SMD.Description,
					SMD.Value,
					SMD.Color
			FROM dbo.System_MasterData SMD
			WHERE SMD.GroupId = 0 AND SMD.IsDeleted = 0
			ORDER BY SMD.OrderNo ASC
				'
		SET @params = '@GroupId BIGINT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @GroupId
	END
	ELSE 
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
				SMD.Id,
				SMD.Name,
				SMD.Description,
				SMD.Value,
				SMD.Color
			FROM dbo.System_MasterData SMD	
			WHERE SMD.GroupId = @GroupId AND SMD.IsDeleted = 0		
			ORDER BY SMD.OrderNo ASC			
			'
	SET @params = '@GroupId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @GroupId
	END  		
	
END


GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetMasterDataByName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetMasterDataByName]
	@Name						NVARCHAR(100) ,
	@LanguageId					BIGINT ,
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				DECLARE @Id bigint=(SELECT Id FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE Name=@Name and GroupId=0)

				USE [Hrm2.0]
				DECLARE	@return_value int

				EXEC	@return_value = [dbo].[System_Get_GetMasterDataByGroupId]
						@GroupId = @Id,
						@DbName = @DbName				
				SELECT	@return_value				
			'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@LanguageId BIGINT, @Name NVARCHAR(100),@DbName NVARCHAR(100)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @LanguageId,@Name,@DbName
END

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetTable]
	@TableName				VARCHAR(500),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN


	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetTableColumn]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetTableColumn]
	@TableName			NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@IsUpdatingField	BIT = 0,
	@ColumnId			BIGINT,
	@DbName				NVARCHAR(500) 
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT 
							STC.*, ST.SqlAlias
					    FROM dbo.System_Table_Column STC
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_Table ST ON ST.Id = STC.TableId
						WHERE ST.TableName = @TableName 
							AND (ISNULL(@ColumnId, 0) = 0 OR STC.Id = @ColumnId)
							AND (ISNULL(@IsUpdatingField, 0) = 0 OR STC.IsUpdatingField = @IsUpdatingField)
							AND STC.IsDeleted=0
						ORDER BY OrderNo ASC
					'
	SET @params = '@TableName NVARCHAR(MAX), @IsUpdatingField BIT, @ColumnId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @TableName, @IsUpdatingField, @ColumnId
END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetTableConfig]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetTableConfig]
	@TableId			VARCHAR(500),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500),
	@UserId BIGINT
as
 
BEGIN

	--SELECT * FROM dbo.[System_User] WHERE UserName=@UserName AND Password=@PassWord

	--DECLARE @SQL NVARCHAR(500)

	--SET @SQL = N'(SELECT * FROM ' +'[' + @DbName+']' + '.dbo.Sec_User where UserName=' + '''' + CAST(@UserName AS NVARCHAR)+ '''' + ' and Password='+  '''' + CAST(@PassWord AS NVARCHAR) + ''')' 
	--SET @SQL=@SQL+ 'exec sp_executesql @SQL'

	--PRINT @SQL

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT * FROM dbo.[User_TableConfig] where TableId=' + '''' + CAST(@TableId AS VARCHAR)+ ''' AND UserId = ' + CAST(@UserId AS VARCHAR) + '
		'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetTableConfigByTableName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GetTableConfigByTableName]
	@TableName			VARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500),
	@UserId BIGINT
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
			SELECT * FROM dbo.[User_TableConfig] UTC
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Table ST ON UTC.TableId = ST.Id
			WHERE ST.TableName=@TableName AND UTC.UserId = @UserId
		'
	SET @params = '@TableName VARCHAR(MAX), @UserId BIGINT'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @TableName, @UserId
END
GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GetTableConfigDefaultByTableName]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[System_Get_GetTableConfigDefaultByTableName]
	@TableName			VARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
AS
 
BEGIN

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT * FROM dbo.[System_TableConfigDefault] STC
			INNER JOIN dbo.System_Table ST ON STC.TableId = ST.Id
			WHERE ST.TableName = @TableName
		'
	SET @params = '@TableName VARCHAR(MAX)'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @TableName
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_GlobalSearchStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_GlobalSearchStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType	READONLY,
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@TotalRecord				INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query

			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT	
				 S.[Id]
			    ,S.[Name]
				,S.[Email]
			    ,S.[Phone]
				,S.[Address]
			    ' 
	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] S 	  
	  '
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE  S.IsDeleted = 0 AND (S.Name LIKE N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'' OR S.Phone LIKE N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'' OR S.Email LIKE N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')  
	  ' + @WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
	  ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(S.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE S.IsDeleted = 0 AND (S.Name LIKE N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'' OR S.Phone LIKE N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'' OR S.Email LIKE N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')  
		' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GlobalSearchStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'System_Get_GlobalSearchStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_MasterData]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[System_Get_MasterData]
	@FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
	@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
	@PageNumber			INT = 1,
	@PageSize			INT = 20,
	@GroupId			INT,
	@LanguageCode		INT,
	@DBName				NVARCHAR(50),
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @StartIndex BIGINT, @EndIndex BIGINT, @cSql NVARCHAR(MAX), @cBeginSql NVARCHAR(MAX), @cSqlFrom NVARCHAR(MAX), @WhereSQL NVARCHAR(MAX),@vcWhereStatus NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @Delim	nvarchar(100)
	DECLARE @dynamicparamdec NVARCHAR(2000)

	SELECT @PageNumber = ISNULL(@PageNumber, 1), @PageSize = ISNULL(@PageSize, 50)
	SELECT @StartIndex = ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
	SELECT @EndIndex = @PageNumber * @PageSize

	IF(@FilterField<>'')
	BEGIN
		SET @FilterField= @FilterField + ' and  SMD.GroupId<>0'
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		IF(@GroupId=0)
		BEGIN
			SET @FilterField= 'and SMD.GroupId=0'
        END 
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @FilterField= 'and SMD.GroupId = '+CAST(@GroupId AS NVARCHAR)
        END 
    END		
	 
	SET @cSqlFrom = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'SELECT 
													SMD.Id,
													SMD.Name,
													SMD.Description,
													SMD.Value,
													SMD.Color,
													SMD.GroupId,
													SMD.OrderNo
													FROM dbo.System_MasterData SMD														
												'
	DECLARE @CountSql NVARCHAR(MAX) =N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(SMD.Id) FROM dbo.System_MasterData  SMD'

	SELECT @cSql = @cSqlFrom  + iif(@FilterField != '',ISNULL(+ ' ' +'WHERE SMD.IsDeleted=0 ' + @FilterField, ''),'') + ' order by SMD.OrderNo ASC   '+ ' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
	print (@cSql)
	exec(@cSql )
		SELECT  @cSql = ''
	SELECT @cSql =   @CountSql +' '+iif(@FilterField != '',ISNULL('WHERE SMD.IsDeleted=0 ' + @FilterField, ''),'')
	print (@cSql)
	SET @dynamicparamdec = N'@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT,@GroupId INT, @LanguageCode INT'
	exec sp_executesql @cSql, @dynamicparamdec, @TotalRecord OUTPUT,@GroupId,@LanguageCode
	
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Get_SearchMasterData]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Get_SearchMasterData]
	@IsCategory					BIT,
	@LanguageId					BIGINT,
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN
	--SELECT * FROM Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData WHERE LanguageId=@LanguageCode AND GroupId=0 AND IsActive=1
	DECLARE @GroupIdQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) = 'GroupId <> 0'
	IF (@IsCategory = 1)
	BEGIN
		SET @GroupIdQuery = 'GroupId = 0'
	END
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				SELECT 
					T.* 
				FROM dbo.System_MasterData T
				INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = T.Id
				WHERE L.DataType = ''MasterData'' AND L.PropertyName = ''Name'' AND L.LanguageId = @LanguageId AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'') AND T.'+ @GroupIdQuery
	SET @params = '@SearchKey NVARCHAR(MAX), @LanguageId BIGINT'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @SearchKey, @LanguageId
END


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Update_SaveListMasterData]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Update_SaveListMasterData]
	  @Id BIGINT,
      @GroupId BIGINT,
      @Name NVARCHAR(500),
      @Value NVARCHAR(500),
      @Description NVARCHAR(500),
      @OrderNo BIGINT,	
      @LanguageId BIGINT,
      @IsActive	BIT,
      @IsDeleted BIT ,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(100),
	  @Color NVARCHAR(20),
	  @DataType  NVARCHAR(100),
	  @CreatedBy BIGINT,
	  @LocalizedMasterData LocalizedDataType READONLY
as
 
BEGIN

	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	 
		BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
					IF(@Id=0)
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO dbo.System_MasterData(GroupId,Name,Value,[Description],OrderNo,IsActive,IsDeleted,Color,IsDisbleEditing)
						Values(@GroupId,@Name,@Value,@Description,1,1,0,@Color,1)

						SET	 @Id	= scope_Identity()
								
						IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @LocalizedMasterData)>0)
						BEGIN
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_LocalizedData
								( DataId ,
								  DataType,
								  LanguageId,
								  PropertyName,
								  PropertyValue,
								  isDefault,
								  CreatedBy,
								  CreatedDate,
								  IsDeleted						 
								)
							SELECT  @Id,
									LMD.DataType,
									LMD.LanguageId,
									LMD.PropertyName ,
									LMD.PropertyValue ,
									IIF(LMD.LanguageId=@LanguageId,1,0),
									LMD.CreatedBy,
									GETDATE(),
									0									
							FROM @LocalizedMasterData LMD
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData LMD1 on LMD1.DataId=@Id and LMD1.LanguageId=LMD.LanguageId and LMD1.DataType=@DataType and LMD1.IsDeleted=0
							WHERE ISNULL(LMD1.Id,0)=0				
						END
						--IF(GroupId=0)
						--BEGIN
							
						--END
					END	
					ELSE
					BEGIN

						UPDATE dbo.System_MasterData SET Name=@Name
														,Value=@Value
														,Description=@Description
														,OrderNo=@OrderNo
														,GroupId=@GroupId
														,Color=@Color
						WHERE Id=@Id

						--UPDATE Data_LocalizedData SET IsDeleted=1,UpdatedBy=@CreatedBy,UpdatedDate=GETDATE() WHERE DataId=@Id and DataType=@DataType

						DELETE Data_LocalizedData WHERE DataId=@Id and DataType=@DataType

						--UPDATE DLD 
						--	DLD.PropertyValue=DLDT.PropertyName,
						--	DLD.UpdatedBy=@CreatedBy,
						--	DLD.UpdatedDate=GETDATE()
						--FROM Data_LocalizedData DLD
						--LEFT JOIN @LocalizedMasterData DLDT on DLDT.DataType=DLD.DataType and DLDT.LanguageId=DLD.LanguageId and DLDT.DataId=@Id
						--WHERE DLDT.

						IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @LocalizedMasterData)>0)
						BEGIN
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_LocalizedData
								( DataId ,
								  DataType,
								  LanguageId,
								  PropertyName,
								  PropertyValue,
								  isDefault,
								  CreatedBy,
								  CreatedDate,
								  IsDeleted						 
								)
							SELECT  @Id,
									LMD.DataType,
									LMD.LanguageId,
									LMD.PropertyName ,
									LMD.PropertyValue ,
									IIF(LMD.LanguageId=@LanguageId,1,0),
									LMD.CreatedBy,
									GETDATE(),
									0									
							FROM @LocalizedMasterData LMD
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData LMD1 on LMD1.DataId=@Id and LMD1.LanguageId=LMD.LanguageId and LMD1.DataType=@DataType and LMD1.IsDeleted=0
							WHERE ISNULL(LMD1.Id,0)=0							
						END

					END			
			'
		SET @params = '@LocalizedMasterData LocalizedDataType READONLY,@GroupId BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@Value NVARCHAR(500),@Description NVARCHAR(500),@OrderNo BIGINT,@Color NVARCHAR(20),@DataType NVARCHAR(500),@CreatedBy BIGINT,@Id bigint,@LanguageId BIGINT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @LocalizedMasterData,@GroupId,@Name,@Value,@Description,@OrderNo,@Color,@DataType,@CreatedBy,@Id,@LanguageId
    END 

	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Update_SaveMasterData]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Update_SaveMasterData]
	  @Id BIGINT,
      @GroupId BIGINT,
      @Name NVARCHAR(500),
      @Value NVARCHAR(500),
      @Description NVARCHAR(500),
      @OrderNo BIGINT,	
      @LanguageId	BIGINT,
      @IsActive	BIT,
      @IsDeleted BIT ,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(100),
	  @Color NVARCHAR(20)
as
 
BEGIN

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	 
	IF(@Id=0)		
	BEGIN

		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				INSERT INTO dbo.System_MasterData(GroupId,Name,Value,[Description],OrderNo,IsActive,IsDeleted,Color)
				VALUES('+CAST(@GroupId AS NVARCHAR)+',N'''+IIF(@Name IS NULL,N'',@Name)+''',N'''+IIF(@Value IS NULL,N'',@Value)+''',N'''+IIF(@Description IS NULL,N'',@Description)+''','+CAST(@OrderNo AS NVARCHAR)+','+CAST(1 AS NVARCHAR)+','+CAST(0 AS NVARCHAR)+',N'''+IIF(@Color IS NULL,N'',@Color)+''')
				DECLARE @Id bigint
				SET @Id= scope_Identity()

				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_LocalizedData
					( DataId ,
					  DataType ,
					  LanguageId ,
					  PropertyName ,
					  PropertyValue ,
					  CreatedBy ,
					  CreatedDate ,
					  UpdatedBy ,
					  UpdatedDate ,
					  IsDeleted
					)
			VALUES  ( @Id , -- DataId - bigint
					  ''MasterData'' , -- DataType - nvarchar(max)
					  '+CAST(@LanguageId AS NVARCHAR)+' , -- LanguageId - bigint
					   N''Name'', -- PropertyName - nvarchar(max)
					  N'''+IIF(@Name IS NULL,N'',@Name)+''', -- PropertyValue - nvarchar(500)
					  1 , -- CreatedBy - bigint
					  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
					  1 , -- UpdatedBy - bigint
					  GETDATE() , -- UpdatedDate - datetime
					  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
					)
				SELECT * FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE GroupId=0 AND  Id=@Id				
			'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery
    END 
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			UPDATE Hrm_System.dbo.System_MasterData
				SET GroupId='+CAST(@GroupId AS NVARCHAR)+',
					Name='''+@Name+''',
					Value='''+@Value+''',
					[Description]='''+@Description+''',
					OrderNo='+CAST(@OrderNo AS NVARCHAR)+',
					IsActive='+CAST(@IsActive AS NVARCHAR)+',
					IsDeleted='+CAST(@IsDeleted AS NVARCHAR)+',
					ColorId='''+@Color+''',
			WHERE	Id= '+CAST(@Id AS NVARCHAR)+'
			SELECT * FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE GroupId=0 AND  Id= '+CAST(@Id AS NVARCHAR)+'
			'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery
    END
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[System_Update_SaveUserTableConfig]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[System_Update_SaveUserTableConfig]
	@TableName			VARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500),
	@UserId BIGINT,
	@QueryData NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@FilterData NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@ConfigData NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@IsFilter NVARCHAR(MAX)
AS
 --@IsFilter = '1': filter
 --@IsFilter = '0': showhide column 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
		DECLARE @TableId BIGINT = 0;
			SET @TableId  = (SELECT ST.Id FROM dbo.System_Table ST WHERE ST.TableName = @TableName)
			IF(@IsFilter = ''1'')
			BEGIN
			IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM User_TableConfig WHERE TableId =  @TableId AND UserId = @UserId) > 0 )
			BEGIN
			UPDATE dbo.User_TableConfig
			SET QueryData = @QueryData,
				FilterData = REPLACE(@FilterData,''{{HOTFIX_QUOTE}}'',''\"''),
				UpdatedDate = GETDATE(),
				UpdatedBy = @UserId
			WHERE TableId = @TableId AND UserId = @UserId
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				INSERT INTO dbo.User_TableConfig
						( UserId ,
						  TableId ,
						  ConfigData ,
						  QueryData,
						  FilterData ,
						  CreatedDate ,
						  CreatedBy ,
						  UpdatedDate ,
						  UpdatedBy ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
				SELECT @UserId,@TableId, STC.ConfigData, @QueryData,REPLACE(@FilterData,''{{HOTFIX_QUOTE}}'',''\"''), GETDATE(), @UserId, NULL, NULL, 0
				FROM dbo.System_TableConfigDefault STC
				WHERE STC.TableId = @TableId
			END
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
			IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM User_TableConfig WHERE TableId =  @TableId AND UserId = @UserId) > 0 )
			BEGIN
			UPDATE dbo.User_TableConfig
			SET ConfigData = @ConfigData,
				UpdatedDate = GETDATE(),
				UpdatedBy = @UserId
			WHERE TableId = @TableId AND UserId = @UserId
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				INSERT INTO dbo.User_TableConfig
						( UserId ,
						  TableId ,
						  ConfigData ,
						  CreatedDate ,
						  CreatedBy ,
						  UpdatedDate ,
						  UpdatedBy ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
				SELECT @UserId,@TableId, @ConfigData, GETDATE(), @UserId, NULL, NULL, 0
				FROM dbo.System_TableConfigDefault STC
				WHERE STC.TableId = @TableId
			END
			END


			SELECT @TableId AS TableId
		'
	SET @params = '@TableName VARCHAR(MAX), @UserId BIGINT, @QueryData NVARCHAR(MAX), @FilterData NVARCHAR(MAX), @ConfigData NVARCHAR(MAX), @IsFilter NVARCHAR(MAX)'
	PRINT @ExeQuery
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @TableName, @UserId, @QueryData, @FilterData, @ConfigData, @IsFilter 
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Systerm_Update_SaveDataCustomer]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Systerm_Update_SaveDataCustomer]
@Name NVARCHAR(MAX),
@Phone NVARCHAR(MAX),
@Email NVARCHAR(MAX),
@DbName NVARCHAR(MAX)
as
BEGIN
IF((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dbo.Data_Customer DC WHERE LOWER(DC.DbName) = LOWER(@DbName)) = 0 )
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Customer 
		        ( Name ,
		          Phone ,
		          Email ,
		          DbName ,
		          CreatedDate ,
		          IsActive ,
		          IsDeleted
		        )
		VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(max)
		          @Phone , -- Phone - nvarchar(max)
		          @Email , -- Email - nvarchar(max)
		          @DbName , -- DbName - nvarchar(50)
		          GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
		          1 , -- IsActive - bit
		          0  -- IsDeleted - bit
		        )
		SELECT 0 AS IsDuplicate
	END
	ELSE SELECT 1 AS IsDuplicate
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Utl_Insert_ErrorLog]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 
Create procedure[dbo].[Utl_Insert_ErrorLog]

	@ErrorCd		int, 
	@ErrorMsg		varchar(2000), 
	@DataBaseName	varchar(50), 
	@ProcName		varchar(50), 
	@TableName		varchar(50), 
	@ActionType		varchar(3),
	@SessionId		bigint, 
	@AddlInfo		varchar(max)

as

	insert into utl_Error_Log
			(ErrorNum,
			ErrorMsg,
			DataBaseName,
			ProcName,
			TableName,
			ActionType,
			SessionId,
			AddlInfo,
			CreatedDate)

	values
			(@ErrorCd,
			@ErrorMsg,
			@DataBaseName,
			@ProcName,
			@TableName,
			@ActionType,
			@SessionId,
			@AddlInfo,
			getdate())





GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Del_DeleteCalculateWorkingDayPeriod]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'					
						UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Period SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE AutoId=@Id	
						UPDATE dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE PeriodID=@Id
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingDay_Del_DeleteListWorkingDaySupplement]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingDay_Del_DeleteListWorkingDaySupplement]
	@ListStringId			NVARCHAR(500),
	@StaffId				BIGINT,
	@DbName					NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'							
						
						DECLARE @Check BIT=1

						DECLARE @data TABLE(
							RequestId BIGINT,
							RequestStatusId BIGINT
						)

						INSERT INTO @data
								( RequestId )
						SELECT   S.Name  -- id - bigint
						FROM dbo.splitstring(@ListStringId,'','') S

						UPDATE D
							SET D.RequestStatusId=DWSA.RequestStatusId
						FROM @data D
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1.* FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=D.RequestId ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA


						DECLARE @RequestId BIGINT
						DECLARE @RequestStatusId BIGINT

						DECLARE @IsRole BIGINT
						DECLARE @IsUser BIGINT

						DECLARE WorkingdaySupplement CURSOR FOR
						SELECT RequestId,RequestStatusId FROM @data

						OPEN WorkingdaySupplement

						FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplement
							INTO @RequestId,@RequestStatusId

						WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
							BEGIN	
								
								SET @IsUser=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 
								AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=331 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

								SET @IsRole=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=270 
								AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=331 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

								IF(@IsUser=0 AND @IsRole=0)
								BEGIN
									SET @Check=0
									BREAK
								END																							
																					
								FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplement
								INTO @RequestId,@RequestStatusId
							END
						CLOSE WorkingdaySupplement
						DEALLOCATE WorkingdaySupplement

						print @Check
						IF(@Check=0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT 
									DWS.* ,
									D.RequestStatusId
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
							INNER JOIN @data D ON D.RequestId=DWS.Id
							LEFT JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC on DWSC.RequesterId=@StaffId 
							AND (DWSC.RequesterTypeId=269 or DWSC.RequesterTypeId=270)
							AND DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId=D.RequestStatusId 
							AND DWSC.NextRequestStatusId IS NULL 
							AND DWSC.RequestActionId=331 AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0	
							WHERE ISNULL(DWSC.Id,0)=0						
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							--DELETE 
							--FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
							--INNER JOIN @data D ON D.RequestId=DWS.Id

							UPDATE DWS
								SET DWS.IsDeleted=1
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
							INNER JOIN @data D ON D.RequestId=DWS.Id
						END
					'
	SET @params = '@ListStringId NVARCHAR(500),@StaffId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@ListStringId,@StaffId

END
GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetCalculateWorkingDayPeriodById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetCalculateWorkingDayPeriodById]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
						SELECT  DWP.AutoId ,
						DWP.Name ,
						DWP.FromDay AS FromDate ,
						DWP.Today AS ToDate ,
						DWP.MaximumEdition ,
						DWP.IsDefault ,
						DWP.Note ,
						DWP.Status ,
						DWW.*
						FROM    dbo.Data_Workingday_Period DWP
								INNER JOIN dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay DWW ON DWP.AutoId = DWW.PeriodID
						WHERE DWP.AutoId = @Id AND DWP.IsDeleted = 0														
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@UserId						BIGINT,
	@RoleId						BIGINT,
	@Date						DATETIME,
	@FilterType					INT, -- 0: Date, 1: Month, 2: Year
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @TimeFilter NVARCHAR(MAX)
	IF (@FilterType = 0)
	BEGIN
		SET @TimeFilter = ' AND CAST(Date as DATE) = CAST(@Date AS DATE) '
	END
	ELSE
	IF (@FilterType = 1)
	BEGIN
		SET @TimeFilter = ' AND MONTH(Date) = MONTH(@Date) AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
	END
	ELSE
	IF (@FilterType = 2)
	BEGIN
		SET @TimeFilter = ' AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
	END

	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSC.Id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS [IsCompleted],
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSA ON DWSA.RequestId = DWS.Id 
							AND DWSA.ApprovedDate = (SELECT TOP 1 MAX(DWSAm.ApprovedDate) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSAm WHERE DWSAm.RequestId = DWSA.RequestId)
						INNER JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId = DWSA.RequestStatusId AND DWSC.RequestActionId = 337 AND DWSC.RequestActionId = 337 AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0 
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						WHERE (ISNULL(@StaffId, 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = @StaffId) ' + @TimeFilter + '
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = @RoleId AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId = @UserId AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
					'
					PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StaffId	BIGINT,	@Date DateTime, @RoleId BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId, @Date, @RoleId, @UserId
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetPeriod]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetPeriod]
    @BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY ,
    @TotalRecord INT = 0 OUTPUT
AS --begin try
    DECLARE @FilterField NVARCHAR(MAX) = '' ,
        @OrderBy VARCHAR(100) = '' ,
        @PageNumber INT = 1 ,
        @PageSize INT = 9000000 ,
        @UserId INT = 1 ,
        @RoleId INT = 1 ,
        @DBName NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System' ,
        @LanguageId INT = 1
    IF EXISTS ( SELECT TOP 1
                        *
                FROM    @BaseParam )
        BEGIN
            SELECT TOP 1
                    @FilterField = FilterField ,
                    @OrderBy = OrderBy ,
                    @PageNumber = PageNumber ,
                    @PageSize = PageSize ,
                    @UserId = UserId ,
                    @RoleId = RoleId ,
                    @DBName = DbName ,
                    @LanguageId = LanguageId
            FROM    @BaseParam
        END
    DECLARE @WhereSQL NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @Delim NVARCHAR(100) ,
        @StartIndex BIGINT ,
        @EndIndex BIGINT ,
        @SQL NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLCount NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLFrom NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLSelect NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @dynamicsql NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @dynamicparamdec NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SearchResult BIGINT ,
        @OrderBySQL VARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @WhereSQLRight NVARCHAR(MAX)

    SET @OrderBy = ISNULL(@OrderBy, ' DWS.Id desc')
    SET @FilterField = ISNULL(@FilterField, '')
    SET @WhereSQL = ' ' 
    SET @WhereSQLRight = ''
    SET @PageNumber = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber, 0) = 0 THEN 1
                           ELSE CONVERT(INT, @PageNumber)
                      END
    SET @PageSize = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize, 0) = 0 THEN 50
                         ELSE CONVERT(INT, @PageSize)
                    END

		--1. Calculate to paging
    SET @StartIndex = @PageSize * @PageNumber
    SET @EndIndex = @StartIndex + @PageSize

    SET @StartIndex = ( ( @PageNumber - 1 ) * @PageSize ) + 1
    SET @EndIndex = @PageNumber * @PageSize

    IF @FilterField <> ''
        BEGIN
            SET @Delim = ' '
            SET @WhereSQL = @WhereSQL + @Delim + @FilterField
        END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

    IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
        BEGIN
            SET @Delim = ' '
            SET @WhereSQL = @WhereSQL + @Delim + @WhereSQLRight
        END

		--3. Build select query

    SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DBName + ']'
        + N'
					SELECT 
						DWP.AutoId AS Id,
					    DWP.AutoId, DWP.Name,
						DWP.FromDay AS FromDate,
						DWP.Today AS ToDate,
						DWP.MaximumEdition,
						DWP.Note,	
						DWP.Status											
			'				
    SET @SQLFrom = ' FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Period DWP'

    SET @SQL = @SQLSelect + @SQLFrom + ' WHERE DWP.IsDeleted = 0 ' + @WhereSQL
        + ' ORDER BY DWP.AutoId DESC
		  OFFSET  ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, ( @PageNumber - 1 ) * @PageSize)
        + ' ROWS  FETCH NEXT ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @PageSize) + ' ROWS ONLY '
		  
    EXEC(@SQL )
    PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
    SET @SQLCount = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DBName + ']'
        + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWP.AutoId) '
    SET @dynamicsql = @SQLCount + @SQLFrom + '  WHERE DWP.IsDeleted = 0 '
        + @WhereSQL
    SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
    EXECUTE sp_executesql @dynamicsql, @dynamicparamdec, @TotalRecord OUTPUT

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch

GO

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetSupplementConfigurationById]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						SELECT  *
						FROM    dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration
						WHERE   Id = @Id
								AND IsDeleted = 0													
					'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetSupplementConfigurationByRoleId]
    @BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY ,
    @TotalRecord INT = 0 OUTPUT
AS --begin try
    DECLARE @FilterField NVARCHAR(MAX) = '' ,
        @OrderBy VARCHAR(100) = '' ,
        @PageNumber INT = 1 ,
        @PageSize INT = 9000000 ,
        @UserId INT = 1 ,
        @RoleId INT = 1 ,
        @DBName NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System' ,
        @LanguageId INT = 1
    IF EXISTS ( SELECT TOP 1
                        *
                FROM    @BaseParam )
        BEGIN
            SELECT TOP 1
                    @FilterField = FilterField ,
                    @OrderBy = OrderBy ,
                    @PageNumber = PageNumber ,
                    @PageSize = PageSize ,
                    @UserId = UserId ,
                    @RoleId = RoleId ,
                    @DBName = DbName ,
                    @LanguageId = LanguageId
            FROM    @BaseParam
        END
    DECLARE @WhereSQL NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @Delim NVARCHAR(100) ,
        @StartIndex BIGINT ,
        @EndIndex BIGINT ,
        @SQL NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLCount NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLFrom NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLSelect NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @dynamicsql NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @dynamicparamdec NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SearchResult BIGINT ,
        @OrderBySQL VARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @WhereSQLRight NVARCHAR(MAX)

    SET @OrderBy = ISNULL(@OrderBy, ' DWSC.Id desc')
    SET @FilterField = ISNULL(@FilterField, '')
    SET @WhereSQL = ' ' 
    SET @WhereSQLRight = ''
    SET @PageNumber = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber, 0) = 0 THEN 1
                           ELSE CONVERT(INT, @PageNumber)
                      END
    SET @PageSize = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize, 0) = 0 THEN 50
                         ELSE CONVERT(INT, @PageSize)
                    END

		--1. Calculate to paging
    SET @StartIndex = @PageSize * @PageNumber
    SET @EndIndex = @StartIndex + @PageSize

    SET @StartIndex = ( ( @PageNumber - 1 ) * @PageSize ) + 1
    SET @EndIndex = @PageNumber * @PageSize

    IF @FilterField <> ''
        BEGIN
            SET @Delim = ' '
            SET @WhereSQL = @WhereSQL + @Delim + @FilterField
        END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

    IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
        BEGIN
            SET @Delim = ' '
            SET @WhereSQL = @WhereSQL + @Delim + @WhereSQLRight
        END

		--3. Build select query

    SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DBName + ']'
        + N'
					SELECT 
						DWSC.Id ,
						DWSC.RequesterId,
						DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId AS PrevStatus ,
						DWSC.NextRequestStatusId AS NextStatus ,
						DWSC.RequestActionId AS Action ,
						DWSC.IsLastStep										
			'				
    SET @SQLFrom = ' FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC'
    SET @SQL = @SQLSelect + @SQLFrom + ' WHERE DWSC.IsDeleted = 0 AND DWSC.RequesterTypeId = 270 AND DWSC.RequesterId =' + @WhereSQL
        + ' ORDER BY DWSC.Id DESC
		  OFFSET  ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, ( @PageNumber - 1 ) * @PageSize)
        + ' ROWS  FETCH NEXT ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @PageSize) + ' ROWS ONLY '
		  
    EXEC(@SQL )
    PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
    SET @SQLCount = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DBName + ']'
        + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWSC.Id) '
    SET @dynamicsql = @SQLCount + @SQLFrom + '  WHERE DWSC.IsDeleted = 0 AND DWSC.RequesterTypeId = 270 AND DWSC.RequesterId ='
        + @WhereSQL
	   PRINT @dynamicsql
    SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
    EXECUTE sp_executesql @dynamicsql, @dynamicparamdec, @TotalRecord OUTPUT

GO

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetTableNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId BIGINT,	
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' DWS.Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
							SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSC.Id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS [IsCompleted],
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							SI1.Name AS ApprovedByName
													
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='	FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						--INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSA ON DWSA.RequestId = DWS.Id 
						--AND DWSA.ApprovedDate = (SELECT TOP 1 MAX(DWSAm.ApprovedDate) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSAm WHERE DWSAm.RequestId = DWSA.RequestId)
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1.* FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=DWS.Id AND IsDeleted=0 ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA
						INNER JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId = DWSA.RequestStatusId AND DWSC.RequestActionId = 337
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) D
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI1 ON D.ApprovedBy = SI1.Id
						'
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 AND (ISNULL('+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ', 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = '+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ')
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = '+ convert(varchar,@RoleId) + 'AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId ='+ convert(varchar,@UserId) +' AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						   ' +@WhereSQL + 
	   ' ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
		  OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		  PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWS.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ '  WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 AND (ISNULL('+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ', 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = '+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ')
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = '+ convert(varchar,@RoleId) + 'AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId ='+ convert(varchar,@UserId) +' AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						   ' +@WhereSQL
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@StaffId BIGINT,@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@StaffId,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch
	 
GO

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetTableWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
							SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							SI1.Name AS ApprovedByName							
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='	FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id	
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI1 ON DWSA.ApprovedBy = SI1.Id
						'
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 and ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		 ' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		  PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWS.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 and' +@WhereSQL
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkDayByPeroidId]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkDayByPeroidId]
	@PeriodID BIGINT,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
AS
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
				SELECT  DWW.Id ,
				DWW.PeriodID ,
				DWW.Monday ,
				DWW.Tuesday ,
				DWW.Wednesday ,
				DWW.Thursday ,
				DWW.Friday ,
				DWW.Saturday ,
				DWW.Sunday ,
				DWW.OrderWeek
				FROM    dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay DWW
				WHERE   DWW.PeriodID = @PeriodID
						AND DWW.IsDeleted = 0 
		'
	SET @params = '@PeriodID BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@PeriodID

END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayAllStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayAllStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query
		-- FilterField ex: DSP.ParentId = @StaffId AND MONTH(DWS.Date) = @Month AND YEAR(DWS.Date) = @Year 
		-- p/s: For login Staff only add at the end of FilterField "AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId"
		SET	@SQLSelect = 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
				DWS.StaffId AS Id,
				DSI.Name,
				DWS.StandardWorkingday,
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.TotalWorkingday, 0)) AS TotalWorkingday,
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.Workingday,0)) AS Workingday,
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.WorkingdayOvertime, 0)) AS WorkingdayOvertime,
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.WorkingdayAnnualLeave,0)) AS WorkingdayAnnualLeave,
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.WorkingdaySupplement, 0)) AS WorkingdaySupplement,	
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.WorkingdayUnpaidLeave, 0)) AS WorkingdayUnpaidLeave,
				SUM(ISNULL(DWS.OtherWorkingday, 0)) AS OtherWorkingday,
				ISNULL(SUM(DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ''00:00:00.000'', CAST(DWS.EarlyDuration AS TIME))), 0) + ISNULL(SUM(DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ''00:00:00.000'', CAST(DWS.LateDuration AS TIME))), 0) AS TotalLateEarly
			FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary DWS
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP ON DWS.StaffId = DSP.StaffId
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id = DWS.StaffId
			WHERE ' +@WhereSQL + '
			GROUP BY DWS.StaffId, DSI.Name, DWS.StandardWorkingday
			ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ ' 
			OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY
			'	
		PRINT (@SQLSelect)	  
		EXEC(@SQLSelect)

		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'
			USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			SELECT 
			@TotalRecord =COUNT(DISTINCT DWS.StaffId)
			FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary DWS
			INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Parent DSP ON DWS.StaffId = DSP.StaffId
			WHERE ' +@WhereSQL
			PRINT(@SQLCount)
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @SQLCount,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayAllStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayAllStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeave]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeave]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,	
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' DWS.Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
									SELECT 
										DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.AutoId AS Id,
										DWA.Name,
										DWA.AnnualLeave,
										DWA.TypeId,
										DWA.RegimeId,
										DWA.PeriodApplyId,
										DWA.Status,
										DWA.DateApply,
										DWA.ExpiryDate,
										DWA.Note,
										COUNT(DWASM.Id) AS TotalShare																													
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave DWA
										LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper DWASM ON DWA.AutoId = DWASM.AnnualLeaveId
										'
		DECLARE @SQLGroup NVARCHAR(max)='GROUP BY DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.Name,
										DWA.AnnualLeave,
										DWA.TypeId,
										DWA.RegimeId,
										DWA.PeriodApplyId,
										DWA.Status,
										DWA.DateApply,
										DWA.ExpiryDate,
										DWA.Note'

	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom + ' WHERE 1=1 '  +@WhereSQL + @SQLGroup +
	   ' ORDER BY DWA.AutoId DESC
		  OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
	  
	EXEC(@SQL)


		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWA.AutoId) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ '  WHERE 1=1 ' +@WhereSQL 
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayByStaffAndMonth]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayByStaffAndMonth]
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@Month  					INT,
	@Year  						INT,
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							*							
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary
						WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND MONTH(Date) = @Month AND YEAR(Date) = @Year
					'
	SET @params = '@StaffId	BIGINT,	@Month INT,	@Year INT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId, @Month, @Year

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingDayCalculationPeriodById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingDayCalculationPeriodById]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
						SELECT  DWP.AutoId ,
						DWP.Name ,
						DWP.FromDay AS FromDate ,
						DWP.Today AS ToDate ,
						DWP.MaximumEdition ,
						DWP.IsDefault ,
						DWP.Note ,
						DWP.Status ,
						DWW.*
						FROM    dbo.Data_Workingday_Period DWP
								INNER JOIN dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay DWW ON DWP.AutoId = DWW.PeriodID
						WHERE DWP.AutoId = @Id AND DWP.IsDeleted = 0														
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END
GO

/*

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayHoliday]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,	
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' DWS.Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
									SELECT 
										DWH.Id,
										DWH.Name,
										DWH.ClassifyId,
										DWH.IsAnnualLeave,
										DWH.SalaryRegimeId,
										DWH.OvertimeRate,
										DWH.Note,
										DWHM.MaxDate,
										DWHM.MinDate,
										CASE 
											WHEN DWH.IsAnnualLeave=0 AND DWHM.MaxDate>DWHM.MinDate THEN (CONVERT(VARCHAR, DWHM.MinDate,103) + '' - '' + CONVERT(VARCHAR,DWHM.MaxDate,103))
											WHEN DWH.IsAnnualLeave=0 AND DWHM.MaxDate=DWHM.MinDate THEN CONVERT(VARCHAR, DWHM.MaxDate,103)
											WHEN DWH.IsAnnualLeave=1 AND DWHM.MaxDate=DWHM.MinDate THEN CAST(DAY(DWHM.MaxDate) AS VARCHAR(2)) + ''/'' + CAST(MONTH(DWHM.MaxDate) AS VARCHAR(2)) 
											WHEN DWH.IsAnnualLeave=1 AND DWHM.MaxDate>DWHM.MinDate THEN (CAST(DAY(DWHM.MinDate) AS VARCHAR(2)) + ''/'' + CAST(MONTH(DWHM.MinDate) AS VARCHAR(2))) + '' - '' + (CAST(DAY(DWHM.MaxDate) AS VARCHAR(2)) + ''/'' + CAST(MONTH(DWHM.MaxDate) AS VARCHAR(2)))
										END AS ApproxDate																			
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Holiday DWH
								OUTER APPLY( SELECT MAX(Date) AS MaxDate,MIN(Date) AS MinDate FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_HolidayMapper WHERE HolidayId=DWH.Id AND IsDeleted=0 ) DWHM'

	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWH.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL + 
	   ' ORDER BY DWH.Id DESC
		  OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		  PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWH.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ '  WHERE DWH.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch
	 
GO

SET ANSI_NULLS ON

SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingDayHolidayById]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
						SELECT 
							DWH.* ,
							DWHM.MaxDate,
							DWHM.MinDate
						FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Holiday DWH
						OUTER APPLY( SELECT MAX(Date) AS MaxDate,MIN(Date) AS MinDate FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_HolidayMapper WHERE HolidayId=DWH.Id AND IsDeleted=0 ) DWHM
						WHERE DWH.Id=@Id AND DWH.IsDeleted=0															
					'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END
GO

					'
	SET @params = '@HolidayId BIGINT'

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayMachineByStaffAndMonth]
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@Month  					INT,
	@Year  						INT,
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							Id,
							StaffId,
							CheckTime,
							CheckType,
							CreatedBy,
							CreatedDate							
						FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_CheckInOut
						WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND MONTH(CheckTime) = @Month AND YEAR(CheckTime) = @Year
					'
	SET @params = '@StaffId	BIGINT,	@Month INT,	@Year INT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId, @Month, @Year

END

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayShift]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,	
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' DWS.Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				SELECT s.[ShiftId]
					  ,s.[ShiftId] AS Id
					  ,s.[Name]
					  ,s.[PeriodId]
					  ,s.[DatabaseName]
					  ,s.[IsOverNight]
					  ,s.[LateAllowed]
					  ,s.[EarlyAllowed]
					  ,s.Status
					  ,s.IsDefault
					  ,DWP.Name	AS PeriodName														
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom=' FROM [dbo].[Data_Workingday_Shift]	s
					 LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Period DWP ON DWP.AutoId=s.PeriodId '

	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE s.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL + 
	   ' ORDER BY s.ShiftId DESC
		  OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		  PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(s.ShiftId) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ '  WHERE s.IsDeleted = 0 ' +@WhereSQL
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch
	 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayShiftById]
	@Id BIGINT,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
				SELECT DWS.[ShiftId]
					  ,DWS.[ShiftId] AS Id
					  ,DWS.[Name]
					  ,DWS.[PeriodId]
					  ,DWS.[DatabaseName]
					  ,DWS.[IsOverNight]
					  ,DWS.[LateAllowed]
					  ,DWS.[EarlyAllowed]
					  ,DWS.[WorkId]
					  ,DWS.Status
					  ,DWS.IsDefault
					  ,DWS.ToShift
					  ,DWS.FromShift
			 FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift	DWS
			 WHERE DWS.ShiftId=@Id and DWS.IsDeleted=0
		'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayShiftDetailByShiftId]

	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
				SELECT 		
					DWSD.[Id],
					DWSD.[ShiffId],
					DWSD.[StartTime],
					DWSD.[EndTime],
					DWSD.[TotalTime],
					DWSD.[StartDate],
					DWSD.[EndDate],
					DWSD.[Status],
					DWSD.[OvertimeMinRequire],
					DWSD.[SalaryRatio],
					DWSD.[IsLunchBreak],
					DWSD.[IsOverTime],
					DWSD.[T2],
					DWSD.[T3],
					DWSD.[T4],
					DWSD.[T5],
					DWSD.[T6],
					DWSD.[T7],
					DWSD.[CN]
				FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift_Detail DWSD
				WHERE DWSD.ShiffId=@ShiftId and DWSD.IsDeleted=0 
		'
	SET @params = '@ShiftId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@ShiftId

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementApprovalById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
