GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementApprovalById]
	@RequestId				BIGINT,
	@DbName					NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT DWA.*
								,DSI.Name AS ApprovalByName
						FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI on DSI.Id=DWA.ApprovedBy
						WHERE  DWA.RequestId=@RequestId AND DWA.RequestStatusId NOT IN (323,324)
					'
	SET @params = '@RequestId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@RequestId

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementById]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(MAX)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							DSWP.OrganizationId
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSWP ON DSWP.StaffId = DWS.StaffId AND DSWP.StartDate IS NOT NULL AND DSWP.EndDate IS NOT NULL
						WHERE DWS.Id = @Id
					'
	SET @params = '@Id	BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@Month  					INT,
	@Year  						INT,
	@FilterString				NVARCHAR(500),
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,						
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWS.IsCompleted,
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							DSWP.OrganizationId
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA					
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSWP ON DSWP.StaffId = DWS.StaffId AND DSWP.StartDate IS NOT NULL AND DSWP.EndDate IS NULL
						WHERE DWS.StaffId = @StaffId AND MONTH(Date) = @Month AND YEAR(Date) = @Year '+ @FilterString +' AND DWS.IsDeleted=0
						ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
					'
					PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StaffId	BIGINT,	@Month INT,	@Year INT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId, @Month, @Year
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Get_SearchWorkingdaySupplement]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Get_SearchWorkingdaySupplement]
	@LanguageId					BIGINT,
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@UserId						BIGINT,
	@RoleId						BIGINT,
	@Date						DATETIME,
	@FilterType					INT, -- 0: Date, 1: Month, 2: Year
	@FilterTypeSupplement		INT,--0:Tìm tất cả, 1:Tìm đề nghị cần duyệt
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @TimeFilter NVARCHAR(MAX)

	IF(@FilterTypeSupplement=1)
	BEGIN
		IF (@FilterType = 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @TimeFilter = ' AND CAST(Date as DATE) = CAST(@Date AS DATE) '
		END
		ELSE
		IF (@FilterType = 1)
		BEGIN
			SET @TimeFilter = ' AND MONTH(Date) = MONTH(@Date) AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
		END
		ELSE
		IF (@FilterType = 2)
		BEGIN
			SET @TimeFilter = ' AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
		END

		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSC.Id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS [IsCompleted],
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSA ON DWSA.RequestId = DWS.Id 
							AND DWSA.ApprovedDate = (SELECT TOP 1 MAX(DWSAm.ApprovedDate) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSAm WHERE DWSAm.RequestId = DWSA.RequestId)
						INNER JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId = DWSA.RequestStatusId AND DWSC.RequestActionId = 337
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SM ON SM.Id=DWS.SupplementTypeId OR SM.Id=DWS.ReasonTypeId
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = SM.Id
						WHERE (ISNULL(@StaffId, 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = @StaffId) ' + @TimeFilter + '
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = @RoleId AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId = @UserId AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						AND L.DataType = ''MasterData'' AND L.PropertyName = ''Name'' AND L.LanguageId = @LanguageId AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')
						ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
					'

		SET @params = '@LanguageId BIGINT,@StaffId	BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT, @RoleId BIGINT,@Date DATETIME'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@LanguageId, @StaffId, @UserId, @RoleId,@Date
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT DISTINCT
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SM ON SM.Id=DWS.SupplementTypeId OR SM.Id=DWS.ReasonTypeId
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = SM.Id
						WHERE L.DataType = ''MasterData'' AND L.PropertyName = ''Name'' AND L.LanguageId = @LanguageId AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')
					'
		SET @params = '@LanguageId BIGINT,@StaffId	BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT, @RoleId BIGINT,@Date DATETIME'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@LanguageId, @StaffId, @UserId, @RoleId,@Date
	END
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Supplement_Approve]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Supplement_Approve]
	@Date			DATETIME,
	@StaffId		INT,
	@DbName			NVARCHAR(MAX)
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE 
		@ExeQuery1 NVARCHAR(MAX), 
		@ExeQuery2 NVARCHAR(MAX), 
		@ExeQuery3 NVARCHAR(MAX), 
		@ExeQuery4 NVARCHAR(MAX), 
		@ExeQuery5 NVARCHAR(MAX), 
		@ExeQuery6 NVARCHAR(MAX), 
		@params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery1 = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
					DECLARE @ShiftId BIGINT = (SELECT TOP 1 ShiftId 
						FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess 
						WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND IsDeleted = 0
						ORDER BY StartDate DESC)

					
					DECLARE @PreCalculableTime TABLE(
						StartTime DATETIME,
						EndTime DATETIME,
						SupplementType INT
					)
					DECLARE @FinalCalculableTime TABLE(
						StartTime DATETIME,
						EndTime DATETIME,
						WorkingDay FLOAT,
						Overtime FLOAT,
						Late DATETIME,
						Early DATETIME
					)
					DECLARE @UnCalculableTime TABLE(
						StartTime DATETIME,
						EndTime DATETIME,
						IsCalc BIT,
						WorkingDay FLOAT,
						Late DATETIME,
						Early DATETIME
					)
					-- Công trên máy
					INSERT INTO @PreCalculableTime VALUES(NULL, NULL, 0)
					UPDATE @PreCalculableTime
					SET StartTime = (SELECT MIN(DWC.CheckTime) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_CheckInOut DWC WHERE DWC.StaffId = @StaffID AND CAST(DWC.CheckTime AS DATE) = @Date)					
					IF (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_CheckInOut DWC WHERE DWC.StaffId = @StaffID AND CAST(DWC.CheckTime AS DATE) = @Date) > 1
					BEGIN
						UPDATE @PreCalculableTime
						SET EndTime = (SELECT MAX(DWC.CheckTime) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_CheckInOut DWC WHERE DWC.StaffId = @StaffID AND CAST(DWC.CheckTime AS DATE) = @Date)	
					END

						

					INSERT INTO @PreCalculableTime
					SELECT 
						DWS.StartTime,
						DWS.EndTime,
						DWS.SupplementTypeId
					FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
					WHERE DWS.SupplementTypeId IN (371, 373) AND DWS.IsCompleted = 1  AND DWS.Date = @Date AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId 
					
					--DELETE @PreCalculableTime WHERE StartTime IS NULL AND EndTime IS NULL	
						
							
			'

		SET @ExeQuery2 = '
				
					--Gộp mốc thời gian của công trên máy, bổ sung công, nghỉ phép

					IF (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM @PreCalculableTime) = 1
					BEGIN
						
						INSERT INTO @FinalCalculableTime
							(StartTime, EndTime)
						SELECT StartTime, EndTime FROM @PreCalculableTime
						
					END
					ELSE					

					INSERT INTO @FinalCalculableTime
					(StartTime, EndTime)
					SELECT 
					   A.StartTime,
					   CAST((CAST(CAST((SELECT TOP 1 S.EndTime 
										FROM @PreCalculableTime S 
										WHERE CAST(S.EndTime AS TIME) = MIN(CAST(B.EndTime AS TIME))
										) AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) +  '' '' + CAST(MIN(CAST(B.EndTime AS TIME)) AS NVARCHAR(12))) AS DATETIME) AS EndTime		
					FROM @PreCalculableTime A
					INNER JOIN @PreCalculableTime B ON (CAST(ISNULL(A.StartTime, B.EndTime) AS TIME) < CAST(ISNULL(B.EndTime, A.StartTime) AS TIME))
					  AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @PreCalculableTime C 
									 WHERE CAST(B.EndTime AS TIME) >= CAST(ISNULL(C.StartTime, B.EndTime) AS TIME)  AND CAST(B.EndTime AS TIME) < CAST(ISNULL(C.EndTime, B.EndTime) AS TIME)) 
					WHERE NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @PreCalculableTime D 
									 WHERE CAST(A.StartTime AS TIME) > CAST(ISNULL(D.StartTime, A.StartTime) AS TIME)  
											AND CAST(A.StartTime AS TIME) <= CAST(ISNULL(D.EndTime, A.StartTime) AS TIME)) 
					GROUP BY A.StartTime 
					ORDER BY A.StartTime 
														
					

					--Chia tách bổ sung không lương theo block giờ
					INSERT INTO @UnCalculableTime
					(StartTime, EndTime, IsCalc)
					SELECT 
						DWSD.StartTime,
						DWSD.EndTime,
						CASE WHEN EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @FinalCalculableTime F 
												WHERE ( DWSD.StartTime >= CAST(F.StartTime AS TIME) AND DWSD.StartTime < CAST(F.EndTime AS TIME)) OR 
													(DWSD.EndTime > CAST(F.StartTime AS TIME) AND DWSD.EndTime <= CAST(F.EndTime AS TIME))) THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS IsCalc
					FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
					LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift_Detail DWSD ON DWSD.ShiffId = @ShiftId AND ISNULL(DWSD.SalaryRatio, 0) = 0
						AND DATEDIFF(MINUTE, DWSD.StartTime, (CAST(DWS.StartTime AS TIME))) > 0	AND DWSD.EndTime > CAST(DWS.StartTime AS TIME)
					WHERE DWS.SupplementTypeId = 372 AND DWS.IsCompleted = 1  AND DWS.Date = @Date AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId 
						
					'
		SET @ExeQuery3 = '
					--Tính công và thời gian đi muộn về sớm
					UPDATE F 
						SET F.WorkingDay = GT.Workingday,
							F.Late = GT.Late,
							F.Early = GT.Early
					FROM @FinalCalculableTime F
					OUTER APPLY(SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, F.StartTime, F.EndTime, @StaffID)) GT	
					--Tính công và thời gian đi muộn về sớm của bổ sung không lương
					UPDATE F 
						SET F.WorkingDay = GT.Workingday,
							F.Late = GT.Late,
							F.Early = GT.Early
					FROM @UnCalculableTime F
					OUTER APPLY(SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, F.StartTime, F.EndTime, @StaffID)) GT	

					--Tính lại đi muộn, về sớm nếu thời gian trùng với khoảng thời gian bổ sung không lương
					UPDATE F
						SET F.Late = CASE WHEN EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @UnCalculableTime U
												WHERE CAST(F.StartTime AS TIME) > CAST(U.StartTime AS TIME) AND CAST(F.StartTime AS TIME) < CAST(U.EndTime AS TIME) AND U.IsCalc = 1) 
												THEN CAST(
														CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
														+ '' 00:00:00''	 AS DATETIME)
											ELSE F.Late
										END,
							F.Early = CASE WHEN EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @UnCalculableTime U
												WHERE CAST(F.EndTime AS TIME) > CAST(U.StartTime AS TIME) AND CAST(F.EndTime AS TIME) < CAST(U.EndTime AS TIME) AND U.IsCalc = 1) 
												THEN CAST(
														CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
														+ '' 00:00:00''	 AS DATETIME)
											ELSE F.Early
										END
					FROM @FinalCalculableTime F
					
					--Dữ liệu đầu ra
					DECLARE @NormalWorkingday FLOAT = ISNULL((SELECT SUM(WorkingDay) FROM @FinalCalculableTime), 0)
					DECLARE @OverTime FLOAT = ISNULL((SELECT SUM(GT.Overtime)
												FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
												OUTER APPLY (SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, DWS.StartTime, DWS.EndTime, @StaffID)) GT
												WHERE DWS.SupplementTypeId = 374 AND DWS.IsCompleted = 1  AND DWS.Date = @Date AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId), 0)
												+
											   ISNULL((SELECT SUM(Overtime) FROM @FinalCalculableTime), 0)

					DECLARE @TotalWorkingDay FLOAT = ISNULL(@NormalWorkingday, 0) + ISNULL(@OverTime, 0) - ISNULL((SELECT SUM(WorkingDay) FROM @UnCalculableTime WHERE IsCalc = 1), 0) '
		SET @ExeQuery4 = '
					--Lấy công làm thêm	
					INSERT INTO @FinalCalculableTime
							( StartTime ,
							  EndTime ,
							  WorkingDay 
							)
					SELECT 
						DWS.StartTime,
						DWS.EndTime,
						GT.Overtime
					FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
					OUTER APPLY (SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, DWS.StartTime, DWS.EndTime, @StaffID)) GT
					WHERE DWS.SupplementTypeId = 374 AND DWS.IsCompleted = 1  AND DWS.Date = @Date AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId

					DECLARE @TotalLateF INT = (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ''00:00:00.000'', CAST(Late AS TIME))),0) FROM @FinalCalculableTime)
					DECLARE @TotalEarlyF INT = (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ''00:00:00.000'', CAST(Early AS TIME))),0) FROM @FinalCalculableTime)
					
					DECLARE @Furlough FLOAT 
					-- Gộp thời gian nghỉ phép và tính tổng công phép
					;WITH FurLough AS(
					SELECT TOP 99999999
					   A.StartTime,
					   --t1.EndDate 
					CAST((Cast(cast((SELECT TOP 1 S.EndTime FROM @PreCalculableTime S WHERE CAST(s.EndTime AS TIME) = MIN(CAST(B.EndTime as time)) ) as date) as nvarchar) +  '' '' +cast(MIN(CAST(B.EndTime as time)) as nvarchar(12))) as datetime) AS EndTime
					
					FROM @PreCalculableTime A
					INNER JOIN @PreCalculableTime B ON (CAST(ISNULL(A.StartTime, B.EndTime) AS TIME) <= CAST(ISNULL(B.EndTime, A.StartTime) AS TIME))
					  AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @PreCalculableTime C 
									 WHERE CAST(B.EndTime AS TIME) >= CAST(ISNULL(C.StartTime, B.EndTime) AS TIME)  AND CAST(B.EndTime AS TIME) < CAST(ISNULL(C.EndTime, B.EndTime) AS TIME) AND C.SupplementType = 371) 
					WHERE NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM @PreCalculableTime D 
									 WHERE CAST(A.StartTime AS TIME) > CAST(ISNULL(D.StartTime, A.StartTime) AS TIME)  
											AND CAST(A.StartTime AS TIME) <= CAST(ISNULL(D.EndTime, A.StartTime) AS TIME) AND D.SupplementType = 371)
						
					AND A.SupplementType = 371
					GROUP BY A.StartTime 
					ORDER BY A.StartTime)
					SELECT @Furlough = SUM(GT.Workingday) FROM FurLough F
					OUTER APPLY (SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, F.StartTime, F.EndTime, @StaffId)) GT

					----Tính công trên máy
					DECLARE @WorkingDay FLOAT		
					SELECT @WorkingDay = SUM(GT.Workingday) FROM @PreCalculableTime F
					OUTER APPLY (SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, F.StartTime, F.EndTime, @StaffId)) GT
					WHERE F.SupplementType = 0

					----Tính tổng công bổ sung
					DECLARE @TotalSupplement FLOAT
					SELECT @TotalSupplement = SUM(GT.Workingday) FROM @PreCalculableTime F
					OUTER APPLY (SELECT * FROM dbo.F_Workingday_Calculation(@Date, F.StartTime, F.EndTime, @StaffId)) GT
					WHERE F.SupplementType = 373 '
		SET @ExeQuery5 = '
					--Lấy tổng thời gian bổ sung không lương
					DECLARE @TotalLeave FLOAT = (SELECT SUM(WorkingDay) FROM @UnCalculableTime)

					--Cập nhật tổng hợp công
					-- tính công chuẩn
					DECLARE @StandardWorkingday FLOAT = 0

					 UPDATE F
						SET F.StartTime=(IIF(F.StartTime<P.StartTime OR P.StartTime IS NULL,CONVERT(NVARCHAR(8),F.StartTime,108),F.StartTime)),
							F.EndTime=(IIF(F.EndTime>P.EndTime OR P.EndTime IS NULL,CONVERT(NVARCHAR(8),F.EndTime,108),F.EndTime))
					  FROM @FinalCalculableTime F
					  INNER JOIN @PreCalculableTime P on P.SupplementType=0
					
					 
					
					IF EXISTS( SELECT TOP 1 * FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary WHERE StaffID = @StaffID AND Date = @Date)
					BEGIN
						UPDATE SF
							SET SF.TotalWorkingDay = ISNULL(@TotalWorkingDay, 0),
								SF.WorkingDay = ISNULL(@WorkingDay, 0),
								SF.StartTime = (SELECT MIN(StartTime) FROM @FinalCalculableTime P),
								SF.EndTime = (SELECT MIN(P.EndTime) FROM @FinalCalculableTime P),
								SF.WorkingdayOvertime = @OverTime,
								SF.WorkingdayAnnualLeave = @Furlough,
								SF.WorkingDaySupplement = @TotalSupplement,
								SF.WorkingdayUnpaidLeave = @TotalLeave,
								SF.LateDuration = CAST(
													CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
													+ '' ''
													+ CAST(CAST(DATEADD(MINUTE, @TotalLateF, 0) AS TIME(0)) AS NVARCHAR)
													 AS DATETIME),
								SF.EarlyDuration = CAST(
													CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
													+ '' ''
													+ CAST(CAST(DATEADD(MINUTE, @TotalEarlyF, 0) AS TIME(0)) AS NVARCHAR)
													 AS DATETIME),
								SF.StandardWorkingday = @StandardWorkingday
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary SF
						WHERE StaffID = @StaffID AND Date = @Date 
					END
					ELSE
					BEGIN
						
						INSERT dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary (
							StaffID, 
							Date, 
							StartTime, 
							EndTime, 
							WorkingDay, 
							WorkingdayOvertime, 
							WorkingdaySupplement, 
							WorkingdayAnnualLeave,
							WorkingdayUnpaidLeave, 
							TotalWorkingday, 
							LateDuration,
							EarlyDuration,
							StandardWorkingday)
						VALUES (
							@StaffID, 
							@Date, 
							(SELECT MIN(P.StartTime) FROM @FinalCalculableTime P),
							(SELECT MIN(P.EndTime) FROM @FinalCalculableTime P),  
							ISNULL(@WorkingDay, 0),
							@OverTime,
							@TotalSupplement,
							@Furlough,
							@TotalLeave,
							ISNULL(@TotalWorkingDay, 0),
							CAST(
								CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
								+ '' ''
								+ CAST(CAST(DATEADD(MINUTE, @TotalLateF, 0) AS TIME(0)) AS NVARCHAR)
								 AS DATETIME),
							CAST(
								CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
								+ '' ''
								+ CAST(CAST(DATEADD(MINUTE, @TotalEarlyF, 0) AS TIME(0)) AS NVARCHAR)
								 AS DATETIME),
							0)

					END '
		SET @ExeQuery6 = '
					-- Xử lý bổ sung đi muộn về sớm
					IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 Id 
								FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
								WHERE DWS.SupplementTypeId IN (370, 459) AND DWS.IsCompleted = 1  AND DWS.Date = @Date AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId) --xin đi muộn về sớm
					BEGIN
						DECLARE @TotalLate INT, @TotalEarly INT
						DECLARE @HourLate DATETIME,@HourEarly DATETIME
							DECLARE @StartTime DATETIME, @EndTime DATETIME
							SELECT
								@TotalLate = ISNULL(SUM(DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ''00:00:00'',
														CAST(IIF(DWS.SupplementTypeId = 370, MissingTimeDuration, ''00:00:00'')  AS TIME(0)))),0),
								@TotalEarly = ISNULL(SUM(DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ''00:00:00'', 
														CAST(IIF(DWS.SupplementTypeId = 459, MissingTimeDuration, ''00:00:00'')  AS TIME(0)))),0)
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
							WHERE DWS.SupplementTypeId IN (370, 459) AND DWS.IsCompleted = 1  AND DWS.Date = @Date AND DWS.StaffId = @StaffId 					
						
							SET @TotalLate =  ISNULL(@TotalLate, 0) - ISNULL(@TotalLateF, 0)
							SET @TotalEarly = ISNULL(@TotalEarly, 0) - ISNULL(@TotalEarlyF, 0)

							UPDATE dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Summary 
								SET LateDuration = CAST(
														CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
														+ '' ''
														+ CAST(CAST(DATEADD(MINUTE, IIF(@TotalLate >= 0, 0, 0 - @TotalLate), 0) AS TIME(0)) AS NVARCHAR)
														 AS DATETIME),
									EarlyDuration = CAST(
														CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR) 
														+ '' ''
														+ CAST(CAST(DATEADD(MINUTE, IIF(@TotalEarly >= 0, 0, 0 - @TotalEarly), 0) AS TIME(0)) AS NVARCHAR)
														 AS DATETIME)
							WHERE Date = @Date AND StaffID = @StaffID	
					END
					'
	SET @ExeQuery1 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery1, '@StaffId', CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR))
	SET @ExeQuery2 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery2, '@StaffId', CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR))
	SET @ExeQuery3 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery3, '@StaffId', CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR))
	SET @ExeQuery4 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery4, '@StaffId', CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR))
	SET @ExeQuery5 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery5, '@StaffId', CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR))
	SET @ExeQuery6 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery6, '@StaffId', CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR))

	SET @ExeQuery1 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery1, '@Date', '''' + CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR(10)) + '''')
	SET @ExeQuery2 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery2, '@Date', '''' + CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR(10)) + '''')
	SET @ExeQuery3 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery3, '@Date', '''' + CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR(10)) + '''')
	SET @ExeQuery4 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery4, '@Date', '''' + CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR(10)) + '''')
	SET @ExeQuery5 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery5, '@Date', '''' + CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR(10)) + '''')
	SET @ExeQuery6 = REPLACE(@ExeQuery6, '@Date', '''' + CAST(CAST(@Date AS DATE) AS NVARCHAR(10)) + '''')

	EXEC(@ExeQuery1 + @ExeQuery2 + @ExeQuery3 + @ExeQuery4 + @ExeQuery5 + @ExeQuery6) 
END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveCalculateWorkingDayPeriod]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveCalculateWorkingDayPeriod]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @Name NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @FromDate INT ,
    @ToDate INT ,
    @Status BIGINT ,
    @Note NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
    @UserID BIGINT ,
    @MaximumEdition INT ,
    @IsDefault BIT ,
    @DbName NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @WorkDayPeriodType WorkDayType READONLY
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
				IF ( @IsDefault = 1 )
    BEGIN
        UPDATE  dbo.Data_Workingday_Period
        SET     IsDefault = 0
    END
IF ( @Id = 0 )
    BEGIN
        INSERT  INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Period
                ( Name ,
                  FromDay ,
                  Today ,
                  Status ,
                  Note ,
                  IsDeleted ,
                  IsDefault ,
                  MaximumEdition ,
                  CreatedBy ,
                  CreatedDate
			    )
        VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - NVARCHAR(500)
                  @FromDate , -- FromDate - INT
                  @ToDate , -- ToDate - INT
                  @Status , -- Status - INT
                  @Note , -- Note - NVARCHAR(MAX),							  
                  0 ,  -- IsDeleted - bit							  
                  @IsDefault ,  -- IsDefault - bit
                  @MaximumEdition , -- MaximumEdition INT
                  @UserID , -- UserID - INT
                  GETDATE() -- CreatedDate - DATETIME
						
                )
        SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
        IF ( ( SELECT   COUNT(Id)
               FROM     @WorkDayPeriodType
               WHERE    Id = 0
             ) > 0 )
            BEGIN
                INSERT  INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_WorkDay
                        ( 
						  [PeriodID] ,
                          [Monday] ,
                          [Tuesday] ,
                          [Wednesday] ,
                          [Thursday] ,
                          [Friday] ,
                          [Saturday] ,
                          [Sunday] ,
                          [OrderWeek] ,
                          [IsDeleted]
								
                        )
                        SELECT  @Id --WorkingDayPeriodID
                                ,
                                WDPT.Monday ,
                                WDPT.Tuesday ,
                                WDPT.Wednesday ,
                                WDPT.Thursday ,
                                WDPT.Friday ,
                                WDPT.Saturday ,
                                WDPT.Sunday ,
                                WDPT.OrderWeek ,
                                0
                        FROM    @WorkDayPeriodType WDPT
                        WHERE   WDPT.Id = 0
            END
    END
ELSE
    BEGIN
	--update calculate working day period
		UPDATE  dbo.Data_Workingday_Period
		SET     Name = @Name ,
				FromDay = @FromDate ,
				Today = @ToDate ,
				Status = @Status ,
				Note = @Note ,
				IsDefault = @IsDefault ,
				MaximumEdition = @MaximumEdition
		WHERE   AutoId = @Id	
	--update workday	
		UPDATE  DWW
		SET     DWW.Monday = WDPT.Monday
			    ,DWW.Tuesday = WDPT.Tuesday
			    ,DWW.Wednesday = WDPT.Wednesday
				,DWW.Thursday = WDPT.Thursday
				,DWW.Friday = WDPT.Friday
				,DWW.Saturday = WDPT.Saturday
				,DWW.Sunday = WDPT.Sunday
		FROM    dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay DWW
				INNER JOIN @WorkDayPeriodType WDPT ON DWW.Id = WDPT.Id
	END														
			'
        SET @params = ' @Id BIGINT ,
						@Name NVARCHAR(500) ,
						@FromDate INT ,
						@ToDate INT ,
						@Status BIGINT ,
						@Note NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
						@UserID BIGINT ,
						@MaximumEdition INT ,
						@IsDefault BIT,
						@DbName NVARCHAR(500),
						@WorkDayPeriodType WorkDayType READONLY
						'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id, @Name, @FromDate, @ToDate,
            @Status, @Note, @UserID, @MaximumEdition, @IsDefault, @DbName,
            @WorkDayPeriodType
	
    END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveListWorkingdaySupplenment]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveListWorkingdaySupplenment]
	@WorkingdaySupplementType	WorkingdaySupplementType READONLY,
	@StaffId							BIGINT,
	@IsApproval							BIT=0,
	@DbName								NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'							
						
						DECLARE @Check BIT=1
						DECLARE @Add BIT=1

						DECLARE @Id BIGINT
						DECLARE @Date DATETIME
						DECLARE @SupplementTypeId BIGINT
						DECLARE @StartTime DATETIME2
						DECLARE @EndTime DATETIME2
						DECLARE @MissingTimeDuration DATETIME2
						DECLARE @ReasonTypeId BIGINT
						DECLARE @OvertimeRate FLOAT
						DECLARE @Note NVARCHAR(500)
						DECLARE @RequestStatusId BIGINT
						DECLARE @StaffId1 BIGINT
						
						DECLARE @IsRole BIGINT
						DECLARE @IsUser BIGINT

						DECLARE WorkingdaySupplement CURSOR FOR
						SELECT Id,Date,SupplementTypeId,StartTime,EndTime,MissingTimeDuration,ReasonTypeId,OvertimeRate,Note,RequestStatusId,StaffId FROM @WorkingdaySupplementType

						OPEN WorkingdaySupplement

						FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplement
							INTO @Id,@Date,@SupplementTypeId,@StartTime,@EndTime,@MissingTimeDuration,@ReasonTypeId,@OvertimeRate,@Note,@RequestStatusId,@StaffId1

						WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
							BEGIN	
								

								IF(@Id<>0)
								BEGIN
									
									SET @IsUser=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 
									AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=331 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

									SET @IsRole=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=270 
									AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=331 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)																	
								
									IF(@IsUser=0 AND @IsRole=0)
									BEGIN
										SET @Check=0
										BREAK
									END	 
								
								END
								
								IF(@Id<>0)
								BEGIN
									SET @Add=0
								END	
								ELSE
								BEGIN
									INSERT INTO dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement
										 ( StaffId ,
										   SupplementTypeId ,
										   Date ,
										   StartTime ,
										   EndTime ,
										   MissingTimeDuration ,
										   OvertimeRate ,
										   ReasonTypeId ,
										   Note ,
										   IsCompleted ,
										   CreatedBy ,
										   CreatedDate ,
										   IsDeleted
										 )
									 VALUES  ( @StaffId , -- StaffId - bigint
											   @SupplementTypeId , -- SupplementTypeId - bigint
											   @Date , -- Date - date
											   @StartTime , -- StartTime - datetime
											   @EndTime , -- EndTime - datetime
											   @MissingTimeDuration , -- MissingTimeDuration - datetime
											   @OvertimeRate , -- OvertimeRate - decimal
											   @ReasonTypeId , -- ReasonTypeId - bigint
											   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
											   0 , -- IsCompleted - bit
											   @StaffId , -- CreatedBy - bigint
											   GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
											   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
											 )

									 SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

									 IF(@IsApproval=0)
									 BEGIN
										INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
											 ( RequestId ,
											   RequestStatusId ,
											   ApprovedBy ,
											   ApprovedDate ,
											   Note,
											   IsDeleted
											 )
										VALUES  ( @Id , -- RequestId - bigint
												   323 , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
												   @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
												   GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
												   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
												   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
												 )
									 END
									 ELSE
									 BEGIN

										DECLARE @RoleId BIGINT
										SET @RoleId=(SELECT TOP 1 RoleId FROM dbo.Data_StaffRole WHERE StaffId=@StaffId)

										SET @IsUser=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 
											AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND RequestActionId=332 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

										SET @IsRole=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@RoleId AND RequesterTypeId=270 
											AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND RequestActionId=332 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

										IF(@IsUser=0 AND @IsRole=0)
										BEGIN
											INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
											 ( RequestId ,
											   RequestStatusId ,
											   ApprovedBy ,
											   ApprovedDate ,
											   Note,
											   IsDeleted
											 )
											VALUES  ( @Id , -- RequestId - bigint
												   323 , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
												   @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
												   GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
												   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
												   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
												 )

											
										END
										ELSE
										BEGIN

											DECLARE @NextRequestStatusId BIGINT

											IF(@IsUser=1)
											BEGIN
												SET @NextRequestStatusId=(SELECT NextRequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL  AND RequestActionId=332 AND IsDeleted=0)
											END
											IF(@IsRole=1)
											BEGIN
												
												SET @NextRequestStatusId=(SELECT NextRequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@RoleId AND RequesterTypeId=270 AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND RequestActionId=332 AND IsDeleted=0)
											END

											INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
											 ( RequestId ,
											   RequestStatusId ,
											   ApprovedBy ,
											   ApprovedDate ,
											   Note,
											   IsDeleted
											 )
											VALUES  (@Id , -- RequestId - bigint
												   @NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
												   @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
												   GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
												   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
												   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
												 )
										END
									END								 
								END																													
																					
								FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplement
								INTO @Id,@Date,@SupplementTypeId,@StartTime,@EndTime,@MissingTimeDuration,@ReasonTypeId,@OvertimeRate,@Note,@RequestStatusId,@StaffId1
							END
						CLOSE WorkingdaySupplement
						DEALLOCATE WorkingdaySupplement

						IF(@Check=0)
						BEGIN							
							SELECT * FROM @WorkingdaySupplementType
						END
						ELSE IF(@Check=1 AND @Add=0)
						BEGIN
							UPDATE WS
								SET WS.SupplementTypeId=WST.SupplementTypeId,
									WS.Date=WST.Date,
									WS.StartTime=WST.StartTime ,
									WS.EndTime=WST.EndTime ,
									WS.MissingTimeDuration=WST.MissingTimeDuration,
									WS.OvertimeRate=WST.OvertimeRate,
									WS.ReasonTypeId=WST.ReasonTypeId,
									WS.Note=WST.Note,
									WS.IsCompleted=0,
									WS.UpdatedBy=@StaffId ,
									WS.UpdatedDate=GETDATE() ,
									WS.IsDeleted=0
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement WS
							INNER JOIN @WorkingdaySupplementType WST on WS.Id=WST.Id

							
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
									(	RequestId ,
										RequestStatusId ,
										ApprovedBy ,
										ApprovedDate ,
										Note,
										IsDeleted
									)
							SELECT   WST.Id , -- RequestId - bigint
									  DWSC.NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
									  @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
									  GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
									  WST.Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
							FROM @WorkingdaySupplementType WST
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC on DWSC.RequesterId= @StaffId
							 AND (DWSC.RequesterTypeId=269 or DWSC.RequesterTypeId=270)  
							 AND DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId=WST.RequestStatusId
							 AND DWSC.NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL
							 AND DWSC.RequestActionId=331
							 AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0

						END
					'
	SET @params = '@WorkingdaySupplementType WorkingdaySupplementType READONLY,@IsApproval BIT,@StaffId	BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@WorkingdaySupplementType,@IsApproval,@StaffId

END
GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveWorkingdayCalculationPeriod]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveWorkingdayCalculationPeriod]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @Name NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @FromDate INT ,
    @ToDate INT ,
    @Status BIGINT ,
    @Note NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
    @UserID BIGINT ,
    @MaximumEdition INT ,
    @IsDefault BIT ,
    @DbName NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @WorkDayPeriodType WorkDayType READONLY
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
				IF ( @IsDefault = 1 )
    BEGIN
        UPDATE  dbo.Data_Workingday_Period
        SET     IsDefault = 0
    END
IF ( @Id = 0 )
    BEGIN
        INSERT  INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Period
                ( Name ,
                  FromDay ,
                  Today ,
                  Status ,
                  Note ,
                  IsDeleted ,
                  IsDefault ,
                  MaximumEdition ,
                  CreatedBy ,
                  CreatedDate
			    )
        VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - NVARCHAR(500)
                  @FromDate , -- FromDate - INT
                  @ToDate , -- ToDate - INT
                  @Status , -- Status - INT
                  @Note , -- Note - NVARCHAR(MAX),							  
                  0 ,  -- IsDeleted - bit							  
                  @IsDefault ,  -- IsDefault - bit
                  @MaximumEdition , -- MaximumEdition INT
                  @UserID , -- UserID - INT
                  GETDATE() -- CreatedDate - DATETIME
						
                )
        SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
        IF ( ( SELECT   COUNT(Id)
               FROM     @WorkDayPeriodType
               WHERE    Id = 0
             ) > 0 )
            BEGIN
                INSERT  INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_WorkDay
                        ( 
						  [PeriodID] ,
                          [Monday] ,
                          [Tuesday] ,
                          [Wednesday] ,
                          [Thursday] ,
                          [Friday] ,
                          [Saturday] ,
                          [Sunday] ,
                          [OrderWeek] ,
                          [IsDeleted]
								
                        )
                        SELECT  @Id --WorkingDayPeriodID
                                ,
                                WDPT.Monday ,
                                WDPT.Tuesday ,
                                WDPT.Wednesday ,
                                WDPT.Thursday ,
                                WDPT.Friday ,
                                WDPT.Saturday ,
                                WDPT.Sunday ,
                                WDPT.OrderWeek ,
                                0
                        FROM    @WorkDayPeriodType WDPT
                        WHERE   WDPT.Id = 0
            END
    END
ELSE
    BEGIN
	--update calculate working day period
		UPDATE  dbo.Data_Workingday_Period
		SET     Name = @Name ,
				FromDay = @FromDate ,
				Today = @ToDate ,
				Status = @Status ,
				Note = @Note ,
				IsDefault = @IsDefault ,
				MaximumEdition = @MaximumEdition
		WHERE   AutoId = @Id	
			--update workday	
		UPDATE  DWW
		SET     DWW.Monday = WDPT.Monday
		FROM    dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay DWW
				INNER JOIN @WorkDayPeriodType WDPT ON DWW.PeriodID = WDPT.PeriodID
			END														
			'
        SET @params = ' @Id BIGINT ,
						@Name NVARCHAR(500) ,
						@FromDate INT ,
						@ToDate INT ,
						@Status BIGINT ,
						@Note NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
						@UserID BIGINT ,
						@MaximumEdition INT ,
						@IsDefault BIT,
						@DbName NVARCHAR(500),
						@WorkDayPeriodType WorkDayType READONLY
						'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id, @Name, @FromDate, @ToDate,
            @Status, @Note, @UserID, @MaximumEdition, @IsDefault, @DbName,
            @WorkDayPeriodType
	
    END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveWorkingdayHoliday]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveWorkingdayHoliday]
	 @Id BIGINT,
     @Name NVARCHAR(500),
     @ClassifyId BIGINT,
     @IsAnnualLeave	BIT,
     @SalaryRegimeId BIGINT,
     @OvertimeRate	FLOAT,
     @Note  NVARCHAR(500),	
     @CreatedBy BIGINT,
     @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
     @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType WorkingdayHolidayMapperType READONLY
AS
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				IF(@Id=0)
				BEGIN
					INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Holiday
			        ( Name ,
			          ClassifyId ,
			          IsAnnualLeave ,
			          SalaryRegimeId ,
			          OvertimeRate ,
			          Note ,
			          CreatedBy ,
			          CreatedDate ,
			          IsDeleted
			        )
					VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(max)
						  @ClassifyId , -- ClassifyId - bigint
						  @IsAnnualLeave , -- IsAnnualLeave - bit
						  @SalaryRegimeId , -- SalaryRegimeId - bigint
						  @OvertimeRate , -- OvertimeRate - float
						  @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
						  @CreatedBy, -- CreatedBy - bigint
						  GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
						  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						)
					SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()
					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM  @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType)>0)
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper
								( HolidayId ,
								  DesistRegimeId ,
								  Date ,
								  IsDeleted
								)
						SELECT   @Id , -- HolidayId - bigint
								  WHDMT.DesistRegimeId , -- DesistRegimeId - bigint
								  WHDMT.Date , -- Date - datetime
								  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						FROM @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType  WHDMT  
					END
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Holiday 
							SET Name=@Name,
								ClassifyId=@ClassifyId,
								IsAnnualLeave=@IsAnnualLeave,
								SalaryRegimeId=@SalaryRegimeId,
								OvertimeRate=@OvertimeRate,
								Note=@Note			
					WHERE Id=@Id

					UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE HolidayId=@Id

					UPDATE DWHM
						SET DWHM.IsDeleted=0,
							DWHM.DesistRegimeId=WHMT.DesistRegimeId
					FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper DWHM
					INNER JOIN @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType WHMT ON WHMT.Id = DWHM.Id
					
					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM  @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType WHERE Id=0)>0)
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper
								( HolidayId ,
								  DesistRegimeId ,
								  Date ,
								  IsDeleted
								)
						SELECT   @Id , -- HolidayId - bigint
								  WHDMT.DesistRegimeId , -- DesistRegimeId - bigint
								  WHDMT.Date , -- Date - datetime
								  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						FROM @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType WHDMT
						LEFT JOIN Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper DWH on DWH.HolidayId=@Id AND DWH.Date=WHDMT.Date
						WHERE WHDMT.Id=0 AND ISNULL(DWH.Id,0)=0

						UPDATE DWHM
								SET DWHM.IsDeleted=0,
							DWHM.DesistRegimeId=WHMT.DesistRegimeId
							FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper DWHM
							LEFT JOIN @WorkingdayHolidayMapperType WHMT ON WHMT.Id=0
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_HolidayMapper DWHM1 ON DWHM1.Date=DWHM.Date AND DWHM1.HolidayId=@Id AND DWHM1.IsDeleted=1
						WHERE WHMT.Id=0 AND DWHM1.Id<>0 
					END
				END															
			'
		SET @params =' @Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@ClassifyId BIGINT,@IsAnnualLeave	BIT, @SalaryRegimeId BIGINT,@OvertimeRate FLOAT,@Note NVARCHAR(500),@CreatedBy BIGINT,@WorkingdayHolidayMapperType WorkingdayHolidayMapperType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@Name,@ClassifyId,@IsAnnualLeave, @SalaryRegimeId,@OvertimeRate,@Note,@CreatedBy,@WorkingdayHolidayMapperType
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveWorkingdayShift]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[Workingday_Update_SaveWorkingdayShift]
	 @Id BIGINT,
     @Name NVARCHAR(500),
     @PeriodId BIGINT,
     @DatabaseName	NVARCHAR(500),
     @IsOverNight BIT,
     @LateAllowed DECIMAL(18,2),
	 @EarlyAllowed DECIMAL(18,2),
     @WorkId  BIGINT,	
     @Status BIGINT,
	 @IsDefault BIT,
	 @ToShift TIME(7),
	 @FromShift TIME(7),
	 @CreatedBy BIGINT,
     @DbName NVARCHAR(500),
     @WorkingdayShiftDetailType WorkingdayShiftDetailType READONLY
AS
 

BEGIN
	 
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				
				IF(@Id=0)
				BEGIN
					INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift
							 ( Name ,
							   PeriodId ,
							   DatabaseName ,
							   IsOverNight ,
							   LateAllowed ,
							   EarlyAllowed ,
							   ToShift,
							   FromShift,
							   WorkId ,
							   Status ,
							   IsDefault,
							   IsDeleted
							 )
					 VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(50)
							   @PeriodId , -- PeriodId - bigint
							   @DbName , -- DatabaseName - varchar(50)
							   @IsOverNight , -- IsOverNight - bit
							   @LateAllowed , -- LateAllowed - decimal
							   @EarlyAllowed  , -- EarlyAllowed - decimal
							   @ToShift,
							   @FromShift,
							   @WorkId, -- WorkId - bigint
							   @Status , -- Status - bigint
							   @IsDefault , -- IsDefault - bit
							   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
							 )

					SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()
					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @WorkingdayShiftDetailType WHERE Id=0)>0)
					BEGIN
						 INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift_Detail
								 ( ShiffId ,
								   StartTime ,
								   EndTime ,
								   TotalTime ,
								   StartDate ,
								   Status ,
								   OvertimeMinRequire ,
								   SalaryRatio ,
								   IsLunchBreak ,
								   IsOverTime ,
								   T2 ,
								   T3 ,
								   T4 ,
								   T5 ,
								   T6 ,
								   T7 ,
								   CN,
								   IsDeleted
								 )
						 SELECT   @Id , -- ShiffId - bigint
								   WSDT.StartTime, -- StartTime - time
								   WSDT.EndTime , -- EndTime - time
								   WSDT.TotalTime , -- TotalTime - decimal
								   GETDATE() , -- StartDate - date
								   1, -- Status - int
								   WSDT.OvertimeMinRequire , -- OvertimeMinRequire - decimal
								   WSDT.SalaryRatio , -- SalaryRatio - decimal
								   WSDT.IsLunchBreak , -- IsLunchBreak - bit
								   WSDT.IsOverTime , -- IsOverTime - bit
								   WSDT.T2 , -- T2 - bit
								   WSDT.T3 , -- T3 - bit
								   WSDT.T4 , -- T4 - bit
								   WSDT.T5 , -- T5 - bit
								   WSDT.T6 , -- T6 - bit
								   WSDT.T7 , -- T7 - bit
								   WSDT.CN, -- CN - bit
								   0
						FROM @WorkingdayShiftDetailType WSDT
					END
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					 UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift
							SET Name=@Name ,
								PeriodId=@PeriodId,
								DatabaseName= @DbName,
								IsOverNight=@IsOverNight,	
								LateAllowed=@LateAllowed,
								EarlyAllowed=@EarlyAllowed,
								ToShift=@ToShift,
								FromShift=@FromShift,
								WorkId=@WorkId,
								Status=@Status,
								IsDefault=@IsDefault
					WHERE ShiftId=@Id
					 
					UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift_Detail SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE ShiffId=@Id

					UPDATE DWSD
							SET 
								DWSD.StartTime=DWSDT.StartTime,
								DWSD.EndTime=DWSDT.EndTime,
								DWSD.TotalTime=DWSDT.TotalTime,
								DWSD.Status=1,
								DWSD.OvertimeMinRequire=DWSDT.OvertimeMinRequire,
								DWSD.SalaryRatio=DWSDT.SalaryRatio,
								DWSD.IsLunchBreak=DWSDT.IsLunchBreak,
								DWSD.IsOverTime=DWSDT.IsOverTime,
								DWSD.T2=DWSDT.T2,
								DWSD.T3=DWSDT.T3,
								DWSD.T4=DWSDT.T4,
								DWSD.T5=DWSDT.T5,
								DWSD.T6=DWSDT.T6,
								DWSD.T7=DWSDT.T7,
								DWSD.CN=DWSDT.CN,
								DWSD.IsDeleted=0
					FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift_Detail DWSD
					INNER JOIN @WorkingdayShiftDetailType DWSDT ON DWSDT.Id=DWSD.Id

					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @WorkingdayShiftDetailType WHERE Id=0)>0)
					BEGIN
						 INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Shift_Detail
								 ( ShiffId ,
								   StartTime ,
								   EndTime ,
								   TotalTime ,
								   StartDate ,
								   Status ,
								   OvertimeMinRequire ,
								   SalaryRatio ,
								   IsLunchBreak ,
								   IsOverTime ,
								   T2 ,
								   T3 ,
								   T4 ,
								   T5 ,
								   T6 ,
								   T7 ,
								   CN ,
								   IsDeleted
								 )
						 SELECT   @Id , -- ShiffId - bigint
								   WSDT.StartTime, -- StartTime - time
								   WSDT.EndTime , -- EndTime - time
								   WSDT.TotalTime , -- TotalTime - decimal
								   GETDATE() , -- StartDate - date
								   1, -- Status - int
								   WSDT.OvertimeMinRequire , -- OvertimeMinRequire - decimal
								   WSDT.SalaryRatio , -- SalaryRatio - decimal
								   WSDT.IsLunchBreak , -- IsLunchBreak - bit
								   WSDT.IsOverTime , -- IsOverTime - bit
								   WSDT.T2 , -- T2 - bit
								   WSDT.T3 , -- T3 - bit
								   WSDT.T4 , -- T4 - bit
								   WSDT.T5 , -- T5 - bit
								   WSDT.T6 , -- T6 - bit
								   WSDT.T7 , -- T7 - bit
								   WSDT.CN ,-- CN - bit
								   0
						FROM @WorkingdayShiftDetailType WSDT
						WHERE WSDT.Id=0
					END

				END
																		
			'
		SET @params ='@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@PeriodId BIGINT,@DatabaseName	NVARCHAR(500),@IsOverNight BIT,@LateAllowed DECIMAL(18,2), @EarlyAllowed DECIMAL(18,2),@WorkId  BIGINT,
		  @Status BIGINT, @IsDefault BIT,@ToShift TIME(7),@FromShift TIME(7), @CreatedBy BIGINT,@DbName NVARCHAR(500), @WorkingdayShiftDetailType WorkingdayShiftDetailType READONLY'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@Name,@PeriodId,@DatabaseName,@IsOverNight,@LateAllowed,@EarlyAllowed,@WorkId,@Status,@IsDefault,@ToShift,@FromShift,@CreatedBy,@DbName,@WorkingdayShiftDetailType
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Del_DeleteWorkingdayAnnualLeave]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Del_DeleteWorkingdayAnnualLeave]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'											
						IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper WHERE AnnualLeaveId=@Id AND IsDeleted=0)>0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave WHERE  AutoId=@Id
						END
						ELSE
						BEGIN
							DELETE  FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave WHERE AutoId=@Id
						END
					'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeave]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeave]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,	
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' DWS.Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
									SELECT 
										DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.AutoId AS Id,
										DWA.Name,
										DWA.AnnualLeave,
										DWA.TypeId,
										DWA.RegimeId,
										DWA.PeriodApplyId,
										DWA.Status,
										DWA.DateApply,
										DWA.ExpiryDate,
										DWA.Note,
										COUNT(DWASM.Id) AS TotalShare																													
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave DWA
										LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper DWASM ON DWA.AutoId = DWASM.AnnualLeaveId AND DWASM.IsDeleted=0
										'
		DECLARE @SQLGroup NVARCHAR(max)='GROUP BY DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.Name,
										DWA.AnnualLeave,
										DWA.TypeId,
										DWA.RegimeId,
										DWA.PeriodApplyId,
										DWA.Status,
										DWA.DateApply,
										DWA.ExpiryDate,
										DWA.Note'

	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom + ' WHERE 1=1 '  +@WhereSQL + @SQLGroup +
	   ' ORDER BY DWA.AutoId DESC
		  OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
	PRINT(@SQL)  
	EXEC(@SQL)


		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWA.AutoId) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ '  WHERE 1=1 ' +@WhereSQL 
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	end try

	begin catch

		declare	@ErrorNum				int,
				@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
				@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
				@SessionId				int,
				@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

		set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
		set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
		set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
		set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeaveById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE  PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeaveById]
	@Id BIGINT,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
									SELECT 
										DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.AutoId AS Id,
										DWA.Name,
										DWA.AnnualLeave,
										DWA.TypeId,
										DWA.RegimeId,
										DWA.PeriodApplyId,
										DWA.Status,
										DWA.DateApply,
										DWA.ExpiryDate,
										DWA.Note,
										COUNT(DWASM.Id) AS TotalShare
									FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave DWA
									LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper DWASM ON DWA.AutoId = DWASM.AnnualLeaveId
									WHERE DWA.AutoId=@Id 
									GROUP BY DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.AutoId,
										DWA.Name,
										DWA.AnnualLeave,
										DWA.TypeId,
										DWA.RegimeId,
										DWA.PeriodApplyId,
										DWA.Status,
										DWA.DateApply,
										DWA.ExpiryDate,
										DWA.Note
		'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id

END
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperAnnualLeaveId]
	@AnnualLeaveId BIGINT,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(100)
as
 
BEGIN	

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'			
									SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper WHERE AnnualLeaveId=@AnnualLeaveId AND IsDeleted=0
		'
	SET @params = '@AnnualLeaveId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@AnnualLeaveId

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayFurlough]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Get_GetWorkingdayFurlough]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType	READONLY,
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@TotalRecord				INT = 0 OUTPUT
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField, -- By Staff : 'DSP.StaffId = 3'
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id ASC')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
			PRINT @FilterField
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--3. Build select query

		SET	@SQLSelect						= 
		N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
		DECLARE 	@SysAnnualLeave DECIMAL(18,2),
					@SysAnnualLeaveSeniority DECIMAL(18,2),
					@DateYear DATE = DATEFROMPARTS(YEAR(GETDATE()), 1, 1)

		SELECT 
			@SysAnnualLeave = AnnualLeave,
			@SysAnnualLeaveSeniority = AnnualLeaveSeniority 
		FROM System_AnnualLeave

		SELECT 
			DI.Id,
			DI.Name,
			CC.StartDate,
			AnnualLeave=IIF(
								cc.StartDate<=@DateYear,
								@SysAnnualLeave,
								IIF(YEAR(
											CC.StartDate)=YEAR(@DateYear),	
											@SysAnnualLeave-MONTH(CC.StartDate) + IIF(DAY(CC.StartDate) < 15, 1, 0),
											0)
							)
			,FurloughSeniority = CAST(ROUND(DATEDIFF(DAY,CAST(CC.StartDate AS DATE), GETDATE()) / (@SysAnnualLeaveSeniority * 365), 0, 0) AS DECIMAL(18,2))
			,AnnualTotal = IIF(
										CC.StartDate<=@DateYear,
										@SysAnnualLeave,
										IIF(
											YEAR(cc.StartDate)=YEAR(@DateYear), 
											@SysAnnualLeave - MONTH(CC.StartDate) + IIF(day(CC.StartDate) < 15, 1, 0), 
											0)
									) 
									+ ISNULL(CAST(ROUND(DATEDIFF(DAY,CAST(CC.StartDate AS DATE), GETDATE()) / (@SysAnnualLeaveSeniority * 365), 0, 0) AS DECIMAL(18,2)), 0)
									+ ISNULL(AnnualLeavelastyear, 0)
									+ ISNULL(AnnualLeaveOther, 0)
			,AnnualLeaveLastYear
			,AnnualLeaveOther
			,AnnualLeaveUse = ISNULL((SELECT SUM(ISNULL(WorkingdayAnnualLeave, 0)) 
									FROM Data_WorkingDay_Summary 
									WHERE StaffId = DI.Id AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@DateYear)), 0)
			,AnnualLeaveRemain = IIF(
										CC.StartDate<=@DateYear,
										@SysAnnualLeave,
										IIF(
											YEAR(cc.StartDate)=YEAR(@DateYear), 
											@SysAnnualLeave - MONTH(CC.StartDate) + IIF(day(CC.StartDate) < 15, 1, 0), 
											0)
									) 
									+ isnull(CAST(ROUND(DATEDIFF(DAY,CAST(CC.StartDate AS DATE), GETDATE()) / (@SysAnnualLeaveSeniority * 365), 0, 0) AS DECIMAL(18,2)),0)
									+ ISNULL(AnnualLeavelastyear, 0)
									+ ISNULL(AnnualLeaveOther, 0)
									- ISNULL((SELECT SUM(ISNULL(WorkingdayAnnualLeave, 0)) 
									FROM Data_WorkingDay_Summary 
									WHERE StaffId = DI.Id AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@DateYear)), 0)
		'	

		SET @SQLFrom='
			FROM Data_Staff_Information DI 
			INNER JOIN Data_Staff_Parent DSP ON DSP.StaffId = DI.Id AND DSP.ParentId = ' + CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) + '
			OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * 
							FROM Data_Staff_WorkingProcess A
							WHERE A.WorkingprocessTypeId= 78 AND A.StaffId=DI.Id 
							ORDER BY StartDate DESC) CC
			OUTER APPLY (SELECT 
							AnnualLeavelastyear = SUM(IIF(DW.TypeId = 446, AnnualLeave, 0)),
							AnnualLeaveOther=SUM(IIF(DW.TypeId != 446, AnnualLeave, 0)) 
							FROM Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave DW 
							WHERE DW.StaffId=DI.Id) AA 
		'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom + ' WHERE DI.IsDeleted = 0 ' + @WhereSQL + 
		' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		EXEC(@SQL)
		print(@SQL)
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + 'SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DI.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql = @SQLCount + @SQLFrom + ' WHERE DI.IsDeleted = 0 ' + @WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql, @dynamicparamdec, @TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayFurlough: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Workingday_Get_GetWorkingdayFurlough', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Update_SaveAnnualLeave]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Update_SaveAnnualLeave]
	  @Id BIGINT,
	  @AnnualLeave DECIMAL(18,2),
	  @AnnualLeaveSeniority DECIMAL(18,2),
	  @NumberOfLeaveGranted DECIMAL(18,2),
	  @HandlingAnnualLeaveBacklog BIGINT,
	  @DateRemoveSurplusAnnualLeave DATETIME,
	  @Type INT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500)

as
 
BEGIN
	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	 
		BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
				IF(@Id=0)
				BEGIN
					INSERT INTO dbo.System_AnnualLeave
						 ( AnnualLeave ,
						   AnnualLeaveSeniority
						 )
					 VALUES  ( @AnnualLeave , -- AnnualLeave - decimal
							   @AnnualLeaveSeniority  -- AnnualLeaveSeniority - decimal
							 )
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					IF(@Type=0)
					BEGIN
						UPDATE dbo.System_AnnualLeave SET AnnualLeave=@AnnualLeave,
														  AnnualLeaveSeniority=@AnnualLeaveSeniority
													WHERE Id=@Id
					END
					ELSE
					BEGIN					
							UPDATE dbo.System_AnnualLeave SET NumberOfLeaveGranted=@NumberOfLeaveGranted,
															HandlingAnnualLeaveBacklog=@HandlingAnnualLeaveBacklog,
															DateRemoveSurplusAnnualLeave=@DateRemoveSurplusAnnualLeave
													WHERE Id=@Id						
					END
				END
																																															
			'
		SET @params = '@Id BIGINT,@AnnualLeave DECIMAL(18,2),@AnnualLeaveSeniority DECIMAL(18,2),@NumberOfLeaveGranted DECIMAL(18,2),@HandlingAnnualLeaveBacklog BIGINT,@DateRemoveSurplusAnnualLeave DATETIME,@Type INT'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@Id,@AnnualLeave,@AnnualLeaveSeniority,@NumberOfLeaveGranted,@HandlingAnnualLeaveBacklog,@DateRemoveSurplusAnnualLeave,@Type

    END 

	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Update_SaveWorkingdayAnnualLeave]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdayAnnualLeave_Update_SaveWorkingdayAnnualLeave]
	@Id BIGINT,
	@Name NVARCHAR(500),
	@AnnualLeave BIGINT,
	@TypeId BIGINT,
	@RegimeId BIGINT,
	@PeriodApplyId BIGINT,
	@Status BIGINT,
	@CreatedBy BIGINT,
	@Note NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName NVARCHAR(500),
	@WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType READONLY
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						IF(@Id=0)
						BEGIN
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave
									 ( Name ,
									   StaffId ,
									   AnnualLeave ,
									   TypeId ,
									   RegimeId ,
									   PeriodApplyId ,
									   Status ,
									   DateApply ,
									   ExpiryDate ,
									   CreatedDate ,
									   CreatedBy ,
									   Note
									 )
							 VALUES  ( @Name , -- Name - nvarchar(max)
									   0 , -- StaffId - bigint
									   @AnnualLeave , -- AnnualLeave - decimal
									   @TypeId , -- TypeId - bigint
									   @RegimeId , -- RegimeId - bigint
									   @PeriodApplyId , -- PeriodApplyId - bigint
									   @Status , -- Status - bigint
									   GETDATE() , -- DateApply - datetime
									   NULL , -- ExpiryDate - datetime
									   GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
									   @CreatedBy , -- CreatedBy - bigint
									   @Note  -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									 )

							SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

							IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WHERE Id=0)>0)
							BEGIN
								 INSERT INTO Hrm_System.dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper
										 ( StaffId, AnnualLeaveId, IsDeleted )
								 SELECT    WALSM.StaffId, -- StaffId - bigint
										   @Id, -- AnnualLeaveId - bigint
										   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								 FROM @WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WALSM
								 WHERE WALSM.Id=0
							END
						END		
						ELSE
						BEGIN

							UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave
									  SET Name=@Name,
									   AnnualLeave=@AnnualLeave,
									   RegimeId=@RegimeId,
									   PeriodApplyId=@PeriodApplyId,
									   Status=@Status,
									   Note=@Note
							WHERE AutoId=@Id
							
							UPDATE 	dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE AnnualLeaveId=@Id
								
							UPDATE 	DWASM
								SET DWASM.IsDeleted=0
							FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper DWASM 	
							INNER JOIN @WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WALSMT ON WALSMT.StaffId=DWASM.StaffId AND DWASM.AnnualLeaveId=@Id

							IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM @WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WHERE Id=0)>0)
							BEGIN
								 INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper
										 ( StaffId, AnnualLeaveId, IsDeleted )
								 SELECT    WALSMT.StaffId, -- StaffId - bigint
										   @Id, -- AnnualLeaveId - bigint
										   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								 FROM @WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WALSMT
								 LEFT JOIN Data_Workingday_AnnualLeave_Staff_Mapper WALSM ON WALSM.StaffId=WALSMT.StaffId AND WALSM.AnnualLeaveId=@Id
								 WHERE ISNULL(WALSM.Id,0)=0
							END
						 
						END																	
					'
	SET @params = '@Id BIGINT,@Name NVARCHAR(500),@AnnualLeave BIGINT,@TypeId BIGINT,@RegimeId BIGINT,@PeriodApplyId BIGINT,@Status BIGINT,@CreatedBy BIGINT,@Note NVARCHAR(MAX)
	,@DbName NVARCHAR(500),@WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType READONLY'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id,@Name,@AnnualLeave,@TypeId,@RegimeId,@PeriodApplyId,@Status,@CreatedBy,@Note,@DbName,@WorkingdayAnnualLeaveStaffMapperType

END
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingDayCalculationPeriod_Del_DeleteCalculateWorkingDayPeriod]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'					
						UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Period SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE AutoId=@Id	
						UPDATE dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE PeriodID=@Id
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingDayCalculationPeriod_Get_GetCalculateWorkingDayPeriodById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingDayCalculationPeriod_Get_GetCalculateWorkingDayPeriodById]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
						SELECT  DWP.AutoId ,
						DWP.Name ,
						DWP.FromDay AS FromDate ,
						DWP.Today AS ToDate ,
						DWP.MaximumEdition ,
						DWP.IsDefault ,
						DWP.Note ,
						DWP.Status ,
						DWW.*
						FROM  dbo.Data_Workingday_Period DWP
							INNER JOIN dbo.Data_WorkingDay_WorkDay DWW ON DWP.AutoId = DWW.PeriodID
						WHERE DWP.AutoId = @Id AND DWP.IsDeleted = 0														
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END
GO
