/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@UserId						BIGINT,
	@RoleId						BIGINT,
	@Date						DATETIME,
	@FilterType					INT, -- 0: Date, 1: Month, 2: Year
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @TimeFilter NVARCHAR(MAX)
	IF (@FilterType = 0)
	BEGIN
		SET @TimeFilter = ' AND CAST(Date as DATE) = CAST(@Date AS DATE) '
	END
	ELSE
	IF (@FilterType = 1)
	BEGIN
		SET @TimeFilter = ' AND MONTH(Date) = MONTH(@Date) AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
	END
	ELSE
	IF (@FilterType = 2)
	BEGIN
		SET @TimeFilter = ' AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
	END

	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSC.Id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS [IsCompleted],
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSA ON DWSA.RequestId = DWS.Id 
							AND DWSA.ApprovedDate = (SELECT TOP 1 MAX(DWSAm.ApprovedDate) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSAm WHERE DWSAm.RequestId = DWSA.RequestId)
						INNER JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId = DWSA.RequestStatusId AND (DWSC.RequestActionId = 337) AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0 
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						WHERE (ISNULL(@StaffId, 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = @StaffId) ' + @TimeFilter + ' AND DWS.IsDeleted=0
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = @RoleId AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId = @UserId AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
					'
					PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StaffId	BIGINT,	@Date DateTime, @RoleId BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId, @Date, @RoleId, @UserId
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetTableNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetTableNeedApproveWorkingdaySupplement]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId BIGINT,	
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' DWS.Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
							SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSC.Id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS [IsCompleted],
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							SI1.Name AS ApprovedByName
													
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='	FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSA ON DWSA.RequestId = DWS.Id 
						AND DWSA.ApprovedDate = (SELECT TOP 1 MAX(DWSAm.ApprovedDate) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSAm WHERE DWSAm.RequestId = DWSA.RequestId)
						--OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1.* FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=DWS.Id AND IsDeleted=0 ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA
						INNER JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId = DWSA.RequestStatusId AND (DWSC.RequestActionId = 337) AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0 
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) D
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI1 ON D.ApprovedBy = SI1.Id
						'
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 AND (ISNULL('+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ', 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = '+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ')
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = '+ convert(varchar,@RoleId) + 'AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId ='+ convert(varchar,@UserId) +' AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						   ' +@WhereSQL + 
	   ' ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
		  OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		  PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWS.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ '  WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 AND (ISNULL('+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ', 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = '+ convert(varchar,@StaffId) + ')
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = '+ convert(varchar,@RoleId) + 'AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId ='+ convert(varchar,@UserId) +' AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						   ' +@WhereSQL
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@StaffId BIGINT,@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@StaffId,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetTableWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetTableWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@TotalRecord int = 0 output
AS
--begin try
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		declare	@WhereSQL				nvarchar(max),
				@Delim					nvarchar(100),
				@StartIndex				bigint,
				
				@EndIndex				bigint,
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLCount					nvarchar(max),
				@SQLFrom				nvarchar(max),
				@SQLSelect					nvarchar(max),
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@SearchResult			bigint,
				@OrderBySQL				varchar(max),
				@WhereSQLRight				nvarchar(max)

		set		@OrderBy				= isnull(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		set		@FilterField			= isnull(@FilterField,'')
		set		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		set		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		set		@PageNumber				= case when isnull(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 then 1 else convert(int,@PageNumber) end
		set		@PageSize				= case when isnull(@PageSize,0)	= 0 then 50 else convert(int,@PageSize) end

		--1. Calculate to paging
		set		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		set		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		set		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		set		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		if @FilterField <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			end
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

		if @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			begin
				set	@Delim				= ' '
				set	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			end

		--3. Build select query

			set	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
							SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							SI1.Name AS ApprovedByName							
			'				
	  set @SQLFrom='	FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id	
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI1 ON DWSA.ApprovedBy = SI1.Id
						'
	  set @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 and ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy+ 
		 ' OFFSET  '+ convert(varchar,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ convert(varchar,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		  PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
		set @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWS.Id) '
		set @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE DWS.IsDeleted = 0 and' +@WhereSQL
		set @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		execute sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  output

	--end try

	--begin catch

	--	declare	@ErrorNum				int,
	--			@ErrorMsg				varchar(200),
	--			@ErrorProc				varchar(50),
	--			@SessionId				int,
	--			@AddlInfo				varchar(max)

	--	set @ErrorNum					= error_number()
	--	set @ErrorMsg					= 'System_Get_GetAllData_Organization: ' + error_message()
	--	set @ErrorProc					= error_procedure()
	--	set @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

	--	exec utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'Data_Staff_Information', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	--end catch
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO


CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementById]
	@Id					BIGINT,
	@DbName				VARCHAR(MAX)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							DSWP.OrganizationId
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSWP ON DSWP.StaffId = DWS.StaffId AND DSWP.StartDate IS NOT NULL AND DSWP.EndDate IS NULL
						WHERE DWS.Id = @Id
					'
	SET @params = '@Id	BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@Id
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementByStaffAndMonth]
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@Month  					INT,
	@Year  						INT,
	@FilterString				NVARCHAR(500),
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT 
							DWS.*,						
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWS.IsCompleted,
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName,
							DSWP.OrganizationId
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA					
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess DSWP ON DSWP.StaffId = DWS.StaffId AND DSWP.StartDate IS NOT NULL AND DSWP.EndDate IS NULL
						WHERE DWS.StaffId = @StaffId AND MONTH(Date) = @Month AND YEAR(Date) = @Year '+ @FilterString +' AND DWS.IsDeleted=0
						ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
					'
					PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StaffId	BIGINT,	@Month INT,	@Year INT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@StaffId, @Month, @Year
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_SearchWorkingdaySupplement]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Get_SearchWorkingdaySupplement]
	@LanguageId					BIGINT,
	@StaffId					BIGINT,
	@UserId						BIGINT,
	@RoleId						BIGINT,
	@Date						DATETIME,
	@FilterType					INT, -- 0: Date, 1: Month, 2: Year
	@FilterTypeSupplement		INT,--0:Tìm tất cả, 1:Tìm đề nghị cần duyệt
	@SearchKey					NVARCHAR(MAX),
	@DbName						VARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @TimeFilter NVARCHAR(MAX)

	IF(@FilterTypeSupplement=1)
	BEGIN
		IF (@FilterType = 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @TimeFilter = ' AND CAST(Date as DATE) = CAST(@Date AS DATE) '
		END
		ELSE
		IF (@FilterType = 1)
		BEGIN
			SET @TimeFilter = ' AND MONTH(Date) = MONTH(@Date) AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
		END
		ELSE
		IF (@FilterType = 2)
		BEGIN
			SET @TimeFilter = ' AND YEAR(Date) = YEAR(@Date) '
		END

		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT DISTINCT
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSC.Id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
								ELSE 0
							END AS [IsCompleted],
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSA ON DWSA.RequestId = DWS.Id 
							AND DWSA.ApprovedDate = (SELECT TOP 1 MAX(DWSAm.ApprovedDate) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWSAm WHERE DWSAm.RequestId = DWSA.RequestId)
						INNER JOIN Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC ON DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId = DWSA.RequestStatusId AND DWSC.RequestActionId = 337  AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0 
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SM ON SM.Id=DWS.SupplementTypeId OR SM.Id=DWS.ReasonTypeId
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = SM.Id
						WHERE (ISNULL(@StaffId, 0) = 0 OR DWS.StaffId = @StaffId) ' + @TimeFilter + '
						AND ((DWSC.RequesterId = @RoleId AND RequesterTypeId = 270) OR (DWSC.RequesterId = @UserId AND RequesterTypeId = 269))
						AND (L.DataType = ''MasterData'' AND L.PropertyName = ''Name'' AND L.LanguageId = @LanguageId AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'') OR  OR LOWER(SI.Name) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%''))
						ORDER BY DWS.CreatedDate DESC
					'
					PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '@LanguageId BIGINT,@StaffId	BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT, @RoleId BIGINT,@Date DATETIME'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@LanguageId, @StaffId, @UserId, @RoleId,@Date
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'	
						SELECT DISTINCT
							DWS.*,
							CASE WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (334, 335, 336)  THEN 47 
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (325, 327, 329)  THEN 49
								 WHEN DWSA.RequestStatusId IN (324, 326, 328)  THEN 50 
								 ELSE 46
							END AS [RequestStatus],
							DWSA.RequestStatusId,
							SI.Name AS StaffName
						FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
						OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval  WHERE RequestId = DWS.Id ORDER BY Id DESC) DWSA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SI ON DWS.StaffId = SI.Id
						INNER JOIN dbo.System_MasterData SM ON SM.Id=DWS.SupplementTypeId OR SM.Id=DWS.ReasonTypeId
						INNER JOIN dbo.Data_LocalizedData L ON L.DataId = SM.Id
						WHERE L.DataType = ''MasterData'' AND L.PropertyName = ''Name'' AND L.LanguageId = @LanguageId AND LOWER(L.PropertyValue) LIKE LOWER(N''%'+@SearchKey+'%'')
					'
		SET @params = '@LanguageId BIGINT,@StaffId	BIGINT, @UserId BIGINT, @RoleId BIGINT,@Date DATETIME'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@LanguageId, @StaffId, @UserId, @RoleId,@Date
	END
	
END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Update_SaveListWorkingdaySupplenment]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Update_SaveListWorkingdaySupplenment]
	@WorkingdaySupplementType	WorkingdaySupplementType READONLY,
	@StaffId							BIGINT,
	@IsApproval							BIT=0,
	@DbName								NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'							
						
						DECLARE @Check BIT=1
						DECLARE @Add BIT=1

						DECLARE @Id BIGINT
						DECLARE @Date DATETIME
						DECLARE @SupplementTypeId BIGINT
						DECLARE @StartTime DATETIME2
						DECLARE @EndTime DATETIME2
						DECLARE @MissingTimeDuration DATETIME2
						DECLARE @ReasonTypeId BIGINT
						DECLARE @OvertimeRate FLOAT
						DECLARE @Note NVARCHAR(500)
						DECLARE @RequestStatusId BIGINT
						DECLARE @StaffId1 BIGINT
						
						DECLARE @IsRole BIGINT
						DECLARE @IsUser BIGINT

						DECLARE WorkingdaySupplement CURSOR FOR
						SELECT Id,Date,SupplementTypeId,StartTime,EndTime,MissingTimeDuration,ReasonTypeId,OvertimeRate,Note,RequestStatusId,StaffId FROM @WorkingdaySupplementType

						OPEN WorkingdaySupplement

						FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplement
							INTO @Id,@Date,@SupplementTypeId,@StartTime,@EndTime,@MissingTimeDuration,@ReasonTypeId,@OvertimeRate,@Note,@RequestStatusId,@StaffId1

						WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
							BEGIN	
								

								IF(@Id<>0)
								BEGIN
									
									SET @IsUser=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 
									AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=331 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

									SET @IsRole=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=270 
									AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=331 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)																	
								
									IF(@IsUser=0 AND @IsRole=0)
									BEGIN
										SET @Check=0
										BREAK
									END	 
								
								END
								
								IF(@Id<>0)
								BEGIN
									SET @Add=0
								END	
								ELSE
								BEGIN
									INSERT INTO dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement
										 ( StaffId ,
										   SupplementTypeId ,
										   Date ,
										   StartTime ,
										   EndTime ,
										   MissingTimeDuration ,
										   OvertimeRate ,
										   ReasonTypeId ,
										   Note ,
										   IsCompleted ,
										   CreatedBy ,
										   CreatedDate ,
										   IsDeleted
										 )
									 VALUES  ( @StaffId , -- StaffId - bigint
											   @SupplementTypeId , -- SupplementTypeId - bigint
											   @Date , -- Date - date
											   @StartTime , -- StartTime - datetime
											   @EndTime , -- EndTime - datetime
											   @MissingTimeDuration , -- MissingTimeDuration - datetime
											   @OvertimeRate , -- OvertimeRate - decimal
											   @ReasonTypeId , -- ReasonTypeId - bigint
											   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
											   0 , -- IsCompleted - bit
											   @StaffId , -- CreatedBy - bigint
											   GETDATE() , -- CreatedDate - datetime
											   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
											 )

									 SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

									 IF(@IsApproval=0)
									 BEGIN
										INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
											 ( RequestId ,
											   RequestStatusId ,
											   ApprovedBy ,
											   ApprovedDate ,
											   Note,
											   IsDeleted
											 )
										VALUES  ( @Id , -- RequestId - bigint
												   323 , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
												   @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
												   GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
												   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
												   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
												 )
									 END
									 ELSE
									 BEGIN

										DECLARE @RoleId BIGINT
										SET @RoleId=(SELECT TOP 1 RoleId FROM dbo.Data_StaffRole WHERE StaffId=@StaffId)

										SET @IsUser=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 
											AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND RequestActionId=332 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

										SET @IsRole=(SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@RoleId AND RequesterTypeId=270 
											AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND RequestActionId=332 AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND IsDeleted=0)

										IF(@IsUser=0 AND @IsRole=0)
										BEGIN
											INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
											 ( RequestId ,
											   RequestStatusId ,
											   ApprovedBy ,
											   ApprovedDate ,
											   Note,
											   IsDeleted
											 )
											VALUES  ( @Id , -- RequestId - bigint
												   323 , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
												   @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
												   GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
												   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
												   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
												 )

											
										END
										ELSE
										BEGIN

											DECLARE @NextRequestStatusId BIGINT

											IF(@IsUser=1)
											BEGIN
												SET @NextRequestStatusId=(SELECT NextRequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId AND RequesterTypeId=269 AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL  AND RequestActionId=332 AND IsDeleted=0)
											END
											IF(@IsRole=1)
											BEGIN
												
												SET @NextRequestStatusId=(SELECT NextRequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@RoleId AND RequesterTypeId=270 AND CurrentRequestStatusId IS NULL AND NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL AND RequestActionId=332 AND IsDeleted=0)
											END

											INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
											 ( RequestId ,
											   RequestStatusId ,
											   ApprovedBy ,
											   ApprovedDate ,
											   Note,
											   IsDeleted
											 )
											VALUES  (@Id , -- RequestId - bigint
												   @NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
												   @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
												   GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
												   @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
												   0  -- IsDeleted - bit
												 )
										END
									END								 
								END																													
																					
								FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplement
								INTO @Id,@Date,@SupplementTypeId,@StartTime,@EndTime,@MissingTimeDuration,@ReasonTypeId,@OvertimeRate,@Note,@RequestStatusId,@StaffId1
							END
						CLOSE WorkingdaySupplement
						DEALLOCATE WorkingdaySupplement

						IF(@Check=0)
						BEGIN							
							SELECT * FROM @WorkingdaySupplementType
						END
						ELSE IF(@Check=1 AND @Add=0)
						BEGIN
							UPDATE WS
								SET WS.SupplementTypeId=WST.SupplementTypeId,
									WS.Date=WST.Date,
									WS.StartTime=WST.StartTime ,
									WS.EndTime=WST.EndTime ,
									WS.MissingTimeDuration=WST.MissingTimeDuration,
									WS.OvertimeRate=WST.OvertimeRate,
									WS.ReasonTypeId=WST.ReasonTypeId,
									WS.Note=WST.Note,
									WS.IsCompleted=0,
									WS.UpdatedBy=@StaffId ,
									WS.UpdatedDate=GETDATE() ,
									WS.IsDeleted=0
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement WS
							INNER JOIN @WorkingdaySupplementType WST on WS.Id=WST.Id

							
							INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
									(	RequestId ,
										RequestStatusId ,
										ApprovedBy ,
										ApprovedDate ,
										Note,
										IsDeleted
									)
							SELECT   WST.Id , -- RequestId - bigint
									  DWSC.NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
									  @StaffId, -- ApprovedBy - bigint
									  GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
									  WST.Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
									  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
							FROM @WorkingdaySupplementType WST
							LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC on DWSC.RequesterId= @StaffId
							 AND (DWSC.RequesterTypeId=269 or DWSC.RequesterTypeId=270)  
							 AND DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId=WST.RequestStatusId
							 AND DWSC.NextRequestStatusId IS NOT NULL
							 AND DWSC.RequestActionId=331
							 AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0

						END
					'
	SET @params = '@WorkingdaySupplementType WorkingdaySupplementType READONLY,@IsApproval BIT,@StaffId	BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@WorkingdaySupplementType,@IsApproval,@StaffId

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Update_SaveWorkingdaySupplenment]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE procedure[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplement_Update_SaveWorkingdaySupplenment]
	 @StaffId BIGINT,
	 @SupplementTypeId BIGINT,
	 @Date DATETIME,
	 @StartTime DATETIME,
     @EndTime DATETIME,
	 @MissingTimeDuration DATETIME,
	 @OvertimeRate  FLOAT,
	 @ResonTypeId BIGINT,
	 @Note NVARCHAR(MAX),	
	 @CreatedBy BIGINT,
     @UpdatedBy BIGINT,
	 @DbName NVARCHAR(100),
	 @Id BIGINT output
as


		declare	
				@SQL					nvarchar(max),
				
				
				@dynamicsql				nvarchar(max),
				@dynamicparamdec		nvarchar(max),
				@Params					nvarchar(max)
		
		if @Id = 0
			
			begin
			-- insert\
				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId and RequesterTypeId=269 and RequestActionId=331)>0)
					BEGIN
						INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_WorkingDay_Supplement]
					   ([StaffId]
					   ,[SupplementTypeId]
					   ,[Date]
					   ,[StartTime]
					   ,[EndTime]
					   ,[MissingTimeDuration]
					   ,[OvertimeRate]
					   ,[ReasonTypeId]
					   ,[Note]
					   ,[CreatedBy]
					   ,[CreatedDate]
					   ,[IsDeleted]
					   ,[IsCompleted])
					   VALUES (@StaffId,@SupplementTypeId,@Date,@StartTime,@EndTime,@MissingTimeDuration,@OvertimeRate,@ResonTypeId,@Note,@CreatedBy,getdate(),0,0)
				   
					   SET @Id=SCOPE_IDENTITY()

					   INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
							( RequestId ,
							  RequestStatusId ,
							  ApprovedBy ,
							  ApprovedDate ,
							  Note ,
							  IsDeleted
							)
					  SELECT  @Id , -- RequestId - bigint
							  DSC.NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
							  @StaffId , -- ApprovedBy - bigint
							  GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
							  @Note , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
							  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
					 FROM  Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DSC 
					 WHERE DSC.RequesterId=@StaffId AND DSC.RequesterTypeId=269 AND DSC.RequestActionId=331

					END
					
				   				
			'		
			end
		else
			begin
				--Update

				SET @SQL = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

					IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@StaffId and RequesterTypeId=269 and RequestActionId=331)>0)
					BEGIN
						update  [dbo].[Data_WorkingDay_Supplement]
						set [StaffId]=@StaffId
					   ,[SupplementTypeId]=@SupplementTypeId
					   ,[Date]=@Date
					   ,[StartTime]=@StartTime
					   ,[EndTime]=@EndTime
					   ,[MissingTimeDuration]=@MissingTimeDuration
					   ,[OvertimeRate]=@OvertimeRate
					   ,[ReasonTypeId]=@ResonTypeId
					   ,[Note]=@Note
					   ,[UpdatedBy]=@UpdatedBy
					   ,[UpdatedDate]=getdate()					
						where Id = @Id


						INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
							( RequestId ,
							  RequestStatusId ,
							  ApprovedBy ,
							  ApprovedDate ,
							  Note ,
							  IsDeleted
							)
					  SELECT  @Id , -- RequestId - bigint
							  DSC.NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
							  @StaffId , -- ApprovedBy - bigint
							  GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
							  null , -- Note - nvarchar(max)
							  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
					 FROM  Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DSC 
					 WHERE DSC.RequesterId=@StaffId AND DSC.RequesterTypeId=269 AND DSC.RequestActionId=331

					END
					
				 ' 
			end
			-- set full param
	SET @Params = 
			'
			 @StaffId BIGINT,
			 @SupplementTypeId BIGINT,
			 @Date DATETIME,
			 @StartTime DATETIME,
			 @EndTime DATETIME,
			 @MissingTimeDuration DATETIME,
			 @OvertimeRate  FLOAT,
			 @ResonTypeId BIGINT,
			 @Note NVARCHAR(MAX),
			 @CreatedBy	BIGINT,
			 @UpdatedBy bigint,
			 @DbName NVARCHAR(100),
			 @Id BIGINT output
			'
	-- EXEC insert update data with param
	print @SQL
	EXEC sp_executesql @SQL, @Params, 
    @StaffId
    ,@SupplementTypeId
	,@Date
    ,@StartTime
	,@EndTime
	,@MissingTimeDuration
    ,@OvertimeRate
    ,@ResonTypeId
    ,@Note
    ,@CreatedBy
    ,@UpdatedBy
	,@DbName
	,@Id output





GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementApproval_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementApprovalById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementApproval_Get_GetWorkingdaySupplementApprovalById]
	@RequestId				BIGINT,
	@DbName					NVARCHAR(500)
as
 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'						
						SELECT DWA.*
								,DSI.Name AS ApprovalByName
						FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval DWA
						LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI on DSI.Id=DWA.ApprovedBy
						WHERE  DWA.RequestId=@RequestId AND DWA.RequestStatusId NOT IN (323,324)
					'
	SET @params = '@RequestId BIGINT'
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,@RequestId

END
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementApproval_Update_SaveSubmitApproval]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementApproval_Update_SaveSubmitApproval]
	  @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType READONLY, 
	  @ApprovedBy BIGINT,
	  @RoleApprovedBy BIGINT,
	  @IsApproval BIT,
	  @DbName NVARCHAR(500)

as
 
BEGIN
	
	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQuery1 NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX),@ExeQueryList NVARCHAR(MAX)	 
		BEGIN
		SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

				DECLARE @Check BIGINT=1
				DECLARE @CountStaff BIGINT=1
				DECLARE @CountRole BIGINT=1
				
				IF(@IsApproval=0)
				BEGIN	
					select 1			
					IF((SELECT COUNT(WSAT.Id)
						FROM @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WSAT 
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 RequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=WSAT.RequestId AND IsDeleted=0 ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA 
						WHERE DWSA.RequestStatusId<>323 ) >0)
						BEGIN
							SELECT DWS.* 
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
							INNER JOIN @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WSAT on WSAT.RequestId=DWS.Id
							OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 RequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=WSAT.RequestId ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA 
							WHERE DWSA.RequestStatusId<>323
							SET @Check=0
						END				
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					IF((SELECT COUNT(WSAT.Id)
						FROM @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WSAT 
						OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 RequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=WSAT.RequestId AND IsDeleted=0 ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC ) DWSA 
						WHERE DWSA.RequestStatusId NOT IN(334,335,336))>0 
						)
					BEGIN
						
						SELECT DWS.* 
							FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
							INNER JOIN @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WSAT on WSAT.RequestId=DWS.Id
							OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 RequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=WSAT.RequestId ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA 
							WHERE DWSA.RequestStatusId NOT IN(334,335,336)
							SET @Check=0
					END
				END
				
				
				IF(@Check=1)
				BEGIN
					
					DECLARE @RequestId BIGINT
					DECLARE @RequestStatusId BIGINT
					DECLARE @RequestActionId BIGINT
					DECLARE @Note NVARCHAR(500)
					DECLARE @IsLastStep BIGINT
					

					DECLARE @Date DATETIME
					DECLARE @StaffId BIGINT

					DECLARE WorkingdaySupplementApproval CURSOR FOR
					SELECT RequestId,RequestStatusId,RequestActionId,Note FROM @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType

				
					OPEN WorkingdaySupplementApproval

					FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplementApproval
						INTO @RequestId,@RequestStatusId,@RequestActionId,@Note
									
					 WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
						BEGIN				
							
							SET @Date=(SELECT Date FROM Data_WorkingDay_Supplement WHERE Id=@RequestId)
							SET @StaffId=(SELECT StaffId FROM Data_WorkingDay_Supplement WHERE Id=@RequestId)
							SET @RequestStatusId=(SELECT TOP 1 RequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=@RequestId ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC)
										
							IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@ApprovedBy AND RequesterTypeId=269 AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=@RequestActionId AND IsDeleted=0 )>0 )
							BEGIN	
								INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
								( RequestId ,
								  RequestStatusId ,
								  ApprovedBy ,
								  ApprovedDate ,
								  Note ,
								  IsDeleted
								)
								SELECT  @RequestId , -- RequestId - bigint
										DWSC.NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
										@ApprovedBy , -- ApprovedBy - bigint
										GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
										@Note, -- Note - nvarchar(max)
										0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC 
								WHERE DWSC.RequesterId=@ApprovedBy AND DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND DWSC.RequesterTypeId=269 AND DWSC.RequestActionId=@RequestActionId AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0

								SET @IsLastStep =(SELECT IsLastStep FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@ApprovedBy AND RequesterTypeId=269 AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=@RequestActionId AND IsDeleted=0)
								IF(ISNULL(@IsLastStep,0)=10518 and @RequestActionId=332)
								BEGIN
									UPDATE dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement SET IsCompleted=1,UpdatedBy=@ApprovedBy,UpdatedDate=GETDATE() WHERE Id=@RequestId
									EXEC [Hrm2.0].dbo.Workingday_Supplement_Approve 
									@Date = @Date, -- datetime
									@StaffId = @StaffId, -- int
									@DbName = @DbName -- nvarchar(max)
								END

							
							END					
							ELSE IF((SELECT COUNT(Id) FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@RoleApprovedBy AND RequesterTypeId=270 AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=@RequestActionId AND IsDeleted=0)>0 )
							BEGIN								
								INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval
								( RequestId ,
								  RequestStatusId ,
								  ApprovedBy ,
								  ApprovedDate ,
								  Note ,
								  IsDeleted
								)
								SELECT  @RequestId , -- RequestId - bigint
										DWSC.NextRequestStatusId , -- RequestStatusId - bigint
										@ApprovedBy , -- ApprovedBy - bigint
										GETDATE() , -- ApprovedDate - datetime
										@Note, -- Note - nvarchar(max)
										0  -- IsDeleted - bit
								FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration DWSC 
								WHERE DWSC.RequesterId=@RoleApprovedBy AND DWSC.CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND DWSC.RequesterTypeId=270 AND DWSC.RequestActionId=@RequestActionId AND DWSC.IsDeleted=0

								SET @IsLastStep =(SELECT IsLastStep FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE RequesterId=@RoleApprovedBy AND RequesterTypeId=270 AND CurrentRequestStatusId=@RequestStatusId AND RequestActionId=@RequestActionId AND IsDeleted=0)
								IF(ISNULL(@IsLastStep,0)=10518 and @RequestActionId=332)
								BEGIN
									UPDATE dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement SET IsCompleted=1,UpdatedBy=@ApprovedBy,UpdatedDate=GETDATE() WHERE Id=@RequestId
									EXEC [Hrm2.0].dbo.Workingday_Supplement_Approve 
									@Date = @Date, -- datetime
									@StaffId = @StaffId, -- int
									@DbName = @DbName -- nvarchar(max)
								END							
							END
							ELSE
							BEGIN
								SELECT DWS.*,
								RequestStatusId=10
								FROM dbo.Data_WorkingDay_Supplement DWS
								INNER JOIN @WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WSAT on WSAT.RequestId=DWS.Id
								OUTER APPLY(SELECT TOP 1 RequestStatusId FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Approval WHERE RequestId=WSAT.RequestId ORDER BY ApprovedDate DESC) DWSA 
								--ROLLBACK TRANSACTION
							END
							FETCH NEXT FROM WorkingdaySupplementApproval
							INTO @RequestId,@RequestStatusId,@RequestActionId,@Note
						
						END

					CLOSE WorkingdaySupplementApproval
					DEALLOCATE WorkingdaySupplementApproval
				END																																												
			'
		SET @params = '@WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType READONLY,@ApprovedBy BIGINT,@RoleApprovedBy BIGINT,@IsApproval BIT,@DbName NVARCHAR(500)'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery,@params,@WorkingdaySupplementApprovalType,@ApprovedBy,@RoleApprovedBy,@IsApproval,@DbName	

    END 

	
END
GO

    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'					
						UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration SET IsDeleted=1 WHERE Id=@Id	
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Get_GetSupplementConfigurationById]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @DbName VARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
						SELECT Id, RequesterId, CurrentRequestStatusId AS PrevStatus, NextRequestStatusId AS NextStatus, RequestActionId AS Action, IsLastStep  FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration WHERE Id = @Id AND IsDeleted = 0										
					'
        SET @params = '@Id BIGINT'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id

    END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Get_GetSupplementConfigurationException]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
 

/*
***************************************************************************
	-- Author:			nhungpt
	-- Description:		Update User
	-- Date				21/11/2019					Update record
***************************************************************************
*/

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Get_GetSupplementConfigurationException]
    @BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY ,
    @TotalRecord INT = 0 OUTPUT
AS --begin try
    DECLARE @FilterField NVARCHAR(MAX) = '' ,
        @OrderBy VARCHAR(100) = '' ,
        @PageNumber INT = 1 ,
        @PageSize INT = 9000000 ,
        @UserId INT = 1 ,
        @RoleId INT = 1 ,
        @DBName NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System' ,
        @LanguageId INT = 1
    IF EXISTS ( SELECT TOP 1
                        *
                FROM    @BaseParam )
        BEGIN
            SELECT TOP 1
                    @FilterField = FilterField ,
                    @OrderBy = OrderBy ,
                    @PageNumber = PageNumber ,
                    @PageSize = PageSize ,
                    @UserId = UserId ,
                    @RoleId = RoleId ,
                    @DBName = DbName ,
                    @LanguageId = LanguageId
            FROM    @BaseParam
        END
    DECLARE @WhereSQL NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @Delim NVARCHAR(100) ,
        @StartIndex BIGINT ,
        @EndIndex BIGINT ,
        @SQL NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLCount NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLFrom NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
		@SQLJoin NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SQLSelect NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @dynamicsql NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @dynamicparamdec NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @SearchResult BIGINT ,
        @OrderBySQL VARCHAR(MAX) ,
        @WhereSQLRight NVARCHAR(MAX)

    SET @OrderBy = ISNULL(@OrderBy, ' DSCE.Id desc')
    SET @FilterField = ISNULL(@FilterField, '')
    SET @WhereSQL = ' ' 
    SET @WhereSQLRight = ''
    SET @PageNumber = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber, 0) = 0 THEN 1
                           ELSE CONVERT(INT, @PageNumber)
                      END
    SET @PageSize = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize, 0) = 0 THEN 50
                         ELSE CONVERT(INT, @PageSize)
                    END

		--1. Calculate to paging
    SET @StartIndex = @PageSize * @PageNumber
    SET @EndIndex = @StartIndex + @PageSize

    SET @StartIndex = ( ( @PageNumber - 1 ) * @PageSize ) + 1
    SET @EndIndex = @PageNumber * @PageSize

    IF @FilterField <> ''
        BEGIN
            SET @Delim = ' '
            SET @WhereSQL = @WhereSQL + @Delim + @FilterField
        END
		--2. get right for role or user

		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user

    IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
        BEGIN
            SET @Delim = ' '
            SET @WhereSQL = @WhereSQL + @Delim + @WhereSQLRight
        END

		--3. Build select query

    SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DBName + ']' + N'
					 SELECT DSI.Name AS StaffName, DWSCE.StaffId,DWSCE.OrganizationId, DWSCE.PreApprovalStatus, DWSCE.Note, Temp.ApproveByName AS ApprovedByName
			'				
    SET @SQLFrom = '    FROM dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration_Exception DWSCE'
						
	SET @SQLJoin = ' JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information DSI ON DSI.Id = DWSCE.StaffId
						OUTER APPLY (
						SELECT ApproveByName =STUFF ((SELECT '','' + IA.Name   
						FROM Data_Staff_Information IA 
						WHERE IA.Id IN (
						SELECT Name FROM dbo.splitstring(DWSCE.ApprovedBy,'','')
						) FOR XML PATH ('''')
						),1,1,'''')
						) Temp'
    SET @SQL = @SQLSelect + @SQLFrom + @SQLJoin
        + ' WHERE DWSCE.IsDeleted = 0'
        + @WhereSQL + ' ORDER BY DWSCE.StaffId DESC
		  OFFSET  ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, ( @PageNumber - 1 ) * @PageSize)
        + ' ROWS  FETCH NEXT ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @PageSize) + ' ROWS ONLY '
		  
    EXEC(@SQL )
    PRINT @SQL
		--4. Count
    SET @SQLCount = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DBName + ']'
        + ' SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(DWSCE.Id) '
    SET @dynamicsql = @SQLCount + @SQLFrom + '  WHERE DWSCE.IsDeleted = 0'
        + @WhereSQL
    PRINT @dynamicsql
    SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
    EXECUTE sp_executesql @dynamicsql, @dynamicparamdec, @TotalRecord OUTPUT

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Update_SaveSupplementConfiguration]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Update_SaveSupplementConfiguration]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @RequesterId BIGINT ,
    @RequesterTypeId BIGINT ,
    @CurrentRequestStatusId BIGINT ,
    @NextRequestStatusId BIGINT ,
    @RequestActionId BIGINT ,
    @IsLastStep BIGINT,
	@DbName NVARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
		IF ( @Id = 0 )
			BEGIN
				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration
						( RequesterId ,
						  RequesterTypeId ,
						  CurrentRequestStatusId ,
						  NextRequestStatusId ,
						  RequestActionId ,
						  IsLastStep ,
						  IsDeleted
						)
				VALUES  ( @RequesterId , -- RequesterId - bigint
						  @RequesterTypeId , -- RequesterTypeId - bigint
						  IIF(@CurrentRequestStatusId=0, NULL, @CurrentRequestStatusId), -- CurrentRequestStatusId - bigint
						  IIF(@NextRequestStatusId=0, NULL, @NextRequestStatusId), -- NextRequestStatusId - bigint
						  IIF(@RequestActionId=0, NULL, @RequestActionId), -- RequestActionId - bigint
						  @IsLastStep , -- IsLastStep - bit
						  0  -- IsDeleted - bit
						)
			END
		ELSE
			BEGIN
				UPDATE dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration 
				SET    	CurrentRequestStatusId = IIF(@CurrentRequestStatusId=0, NULL, @CurrentRequestStatusId),
						NextRequestStatusId = IIF(@NextRequestStatusId=0, NULL, @NextRequestStatusId),
						RequestActionId = IIF(@RequestActionId=0, NULL, @RequestActionId) ,
						IsLastStep = @IsLastStep
				WHERE   Id = @Id	
			END														
					'
        SET @params = ' @Id BIGINT ,
						@RequesterId BIGINT ,
						@RequesterTypeId BIGINT ,
						@CurrentRequestStatusId BIGINT ,
						@NextRequestStatusId BIGINT ,
						@RequestActionId BIGINT ,
						@IsLastStep BIGINT
						'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id, @RequesterId, @RequesterTypeId, @CurrentRequestStatusId,
            @NextRequestStatusId, @RequestActionId, @IsLastStep
	
    END

GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Update_SaveSupplementConfigurationException]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingdaySupplementConfiguration_Update_SaveSupplementConfigurationException]
    @Id BIGINT ,
    @ListStaffId NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @OrganizationId BIGINT ,
    @PreApprovalStatus BIGINT ,
    @ApprovedBy NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @Note NVARCHAR(500) ,
    @DbName NVARCHAR(500)
AS
    BEGIN
        DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX) ,
            @params NVARCHAR(MAX)	   				
															 
        SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_' + @DbName + ']'
            + N'
		IF ( @Id = 0 )
			BEGIN
				INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Workingday_Supplement_Configuration_Exception
				( StaffId ,
				  OrganizationId ,
				  PreApprovalStatus ,
				  ApprovedBy ,
				  Note ,
				  CreatedDate ,
				  CreatedBy ,
				  IsDeleted
				)
				SELECT Name AS StaffId,1,@PreApprovalStatus,@ApprovedBy,@Note,GETDATE(),1,0 FROM dbo.splitstring(@ListStaffId, '','')
			END												
					'
        SET @params = ' @Id BIGINT ,
						@ListStaffId NVARCHAR(500) ,
						@OrganizationId BIGINT ,
						@PreApprovalStatus BIGINT ,
						@ApprovedBy NVARCHAR(500) ,
						@Note NVARCHAR(500) ,
						@DbName NVARCHAR(500)
						'
        EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params, @Id,@ListStaffId ,
            @OrganizationId, @PreApprovalStatus, @ApprovedBy,
            @Note,@DbName
	
    END

GO

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO

GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_CheckContractCodeExisted]
	 @Id BIGINT = 0
    ,@ContractCode NVARCHAR(MAX)
    ,@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY
	,@Result INT OUTPUT
as
 
--begin try

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@OrderBy				VARCHAR(100) = '',
		@PageNumber				INT = 1,
		@PageSize				INT = 9000000,
		@UserId					BIGINT = 1,
		@RoleId					BIGINT = 1,
		@DBName					NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
		@LanguageId				BIT = 1
	
	IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
	BEGIN
		SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
					 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
					 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
					 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
					 @UserId	  = UserId,	
					 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
					 @DbName	  = DbName,	
					 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
		FROM @BaseParam
	END

	SET  @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 

			IF EXISTS (SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Contract WHERE ContractCode = @ContractCode AND Id != @Id)
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 1
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 0
			END				
			'

	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '	@Id BIGINT = 0
					,@ContractCode NVARCHAR(MAX)
					,@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY
					,@Result BIT OUTPUT '
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,			          
			@Id 
           ,@ContractCode 
           ,@BaseParam 
           ,@Result OUTPUT 
	
   
GO

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_CheckWorkingProcessDate]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_CheckWorkingProcessDate]
	@StartDate DATE 
	,@EndDate DATE
	,@StaffId BIGINT
	,@OrganizationId BIGINT
	,@Id BIGINT = 0
	,@DbName NVARCHAR(MAX)
	,@Result BIT OUTPUT 
AS
 
--begin try

	DECLARE @ExeQuery NVARCHAR(MAX), @params NVARCHAR(MAX)
	SET @StartDate = ISNULL(@StartDate,GETDATE())
	SET @EndDate = ISNULL(@EndDate,GETDATE())

	SET  @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 

			IF EXISTS (
				SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess 
				WHERE StaffId = @StaffId AND (OrganizationId = @OrganizationId  OR @OrganizationId = 0 ) 
					AND (
						( @StartDate BETWEEN ISNULL(StartDate,GETDATE()) AND ISNULL(EndDate,GETDATE()) )
						OR ( @EndDate BETWEEN ISNULL(StartDate,GETDATE()) AND ISNULL(EndDate,GETDATE()) )
						OR ( StartDate BETWEEN ISNULL(@StartDate,GETDATE()) AND ISNULL(@EndDate,GETDATE()) )
						OR ( EndDate BETWEEN ISNULL(@StartDate,GETDATE()) AND ISNULL(@EndDate,GETDATE()) )
					) AND Id != @Id	
			)
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 1
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 0
			END				
			'

	PRINT @ExeQuery
	SET @params = '@StartDate DATE 
	,@EndDate DATE
	,@StaffId BIGINT
	,@OrganizationId BIGINT
	,@Id BIGINT = 0
	,@DbName NVARCHAR(MAX)
	,@Result BIT OUTPUT '
	EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params,			          
			@StartDate 
           ,@EndDate 
           ,@StaffId 
           ,@OrganizationId
           ,@Id
           ,@DbName
           ,@Result OUTPUT 
	
   
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingManagerByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingManagerByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			Declare @ActiveStatus BIGINT = ( SELECT Id FROM dbo.System_MasterData WHERE GroupId = 45 AND Name = N''Đã duyệt'')

			SELECT top 1  w.[Id]
				,w.[StaffId]
				,w.[WorkingprocessTypeId]
				,w.[DecisionNo]
				,w.[WorkingStatus]
				,w.[Status]
				,w.[DecisionDate]
				,w.[StartDate]
				,w.[EndDate]
				,w.[ContractId]
				,w.[OrganizationId]
				,w.[OfficeId]
				,w.[PositionId]
				,w.[ClassificationId]
				,w.[StaffLevelId]
				,w.[ManagerId]
				,w.[PolicyId]
				,w.[CurrencyId]
				,w.[BasicPay]
				,w.[EfficiencyBonus]
				,w.[Note]
				,w.[ShiftId]
				,w.Description
				,Year = YEAR(w.StartDate)
				--,ms.Name AS ManagerName
				,hrM.Name AS HRManagerName
				,hrA.Name AS HRAdditionName
				,Ma.Name AS AdditionManagerName
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='
			
			FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Information s
			INNER JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess] w on s.CurrentWorkingProcessId = w.Id
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information hrM ON w.HRManagerId = hrM.Id
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information hrA ON s.HRAdditionId = hrA.Id
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information Ma ON s.AdditionManagerId = Ma.Id'
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE  w.IsDeleted = 0 AND hrM.IsDeleted = 0 AND hrA.IsDeleted = 0 AND Ma.IsDeleted = 0
			
			AND w.Status = @ActiveStatus 
			AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY w.StartDate DESC, w.EndDate DESC' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingProcessByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingProcessByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingProcessByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/

CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingProcessByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' Id desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'


			SELECT top 1  w.[Id]
				,w.[StaffId]
				,w.[WorkingprocessTypeId]
				,w.[DecisionNo]
				,w.[WorkingStatus]
				,w.[WorkingStatus]
				,w.[Status]
				,w.[DecisionDate]
				,w.[StartDate]
				,w.[EndDate]
				,w.[ContractId]
				,w.[OrganizationId]
				,w.[OfficeId]
				,w.[PositionId]
				,w.[ClassificationId]
				,w.[StaffLevelId]
				,w.[ManagerId]
				,w.[PolicyId]
				,w.[CurrencyId]
				,w.[BasicPay]
				,w.[EfficiencyBonus]
				,w.[Note]
				,w.[ShiftId]
				,w.Description
				,Year = YEAR(w.StartDate)
				,sc.ContractTypeId
				,sc.ContractTime
				--,ContractTime = DATEDIFF(MONTH,sc.StartDate,sc.EndDate)
			'
		SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] s
			INNER JOIN [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess] w on s.CurrentWorkingProcessId = w.Id
			LEFT JOIN Data_Staff_Contract sc ON w.ContractId = sc.Id '
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
			
			AND w.Status = 50 
			AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY w.StartDate DESC, sc.ContractStartDate DESC ' 
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		--SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		--	SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		--SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 
		--	AND GETDATE() BETWEEN ISNULL(w.StartDate, @DateTimeMinValue) AND ISNULL(w.EndDate, @DateTimeMaxValue) 
		--	AND w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		--SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		--PRINT @dynamicsql
		--EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingProcessByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetCurrentWorkingProcessByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessById]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessById]
	
	@Id								BIGINT,
	@DbName							NVARCHAR(100),
	@UserID							BIGINT,
	@RoleID							BIGINT
AS
	BEGIN TRY
		DECLARE	
		@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',		
		@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
		@Delim					NVARCHAR(100) = '',
		@Params					NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		--Check right
		SET @WhereSQLRight=''

		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END

		--select
		SET @SQLSelect = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'

			SELECT  
			   w.[Id]
			  ,w.[StaffId]
			  ,w.[WorkingprocessTypeId]
			  ,w.[DecisionNo]
			  ,w.[WorkingStatus]
			  ,w.[DecisionDate]
			  ,w.[StartDate]
			  ,w.[EndDate]
			  ,w.[ContractId]
			  ,w.[OrganizationId]
			  ,w.[OfficeId]
			  ,w.[PositionId]
			  ,w.[ClassificationId]
			  ,w.[StaffLevelId]
			  ,w.[ManagerId]
			  ,w.[HRManagerId]
			  ,w.[PolicyId]
			  ,i.[CurrencyId]
			  ,w.[BasicPay]
			  ,w.[EfficiencyBonus]
			  ,w.[PaymentForm]
			  ,w.[PaymentMethod]
			  ,w.[SalaryNote]
			  ,w.[Description]
			  ,w.[Note]
			  ,w.[Status]
			  ,w.[ShiftId]
			  ,SIM.Name as ManagerName
			  ,SIH.Name as HRManagerName
			  '
		SET @SQLFrom=' FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
			LEFT JOIN  [dbo].[Data_Staff_Information] i on i.Id = w.StaffId AND ISNULL(i.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SIM ON w.ManagerId = SIM.Id AND ISNULL(SIM.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			LEFT JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_Information SIH ON w.HRManagerId = SIH.Id AND ISNULL(SIH.IsDeleted,0) = 0 ' 
		SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE ISNULL(w.IsDeleted,0) = 0
			  AND w.Id = ' + CAST(@id AS NVARCHAR)+ ' ' +@WhereSQL 
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH
		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessById: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@Id=' + CONVERT(VARCHAR, @Id)
		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessById', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo
	END CATCH


GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessByStaff]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE[dbo].[WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessByStaff]
	@BaseParam BaseParamType READONLY,
	@StaffId		BIGINT = 0,
	@TotalRecord	INT = 0 output
AS
BEGIN TRY
	DECLARE @FilterField		NVARCHAR(MAX) = '',
			@OrderBy			VARCHAR(100) = '',
			@PageNumber			INT = 1,
			@PageSize			INT = 9000000,
			@UserId				INT = 1,
			@RoleId				INT = 1,
			@DBName				NVARCHAR(50) = 'Hrm_System',
			@LanguageId			INT = 1
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @BaseParam)
		BEGIN
			SELECT TOP 1 @FilterField = FilterField,
						 @OrderBy	  = OrderBy,	
						 @PageNumber  = PageNumber,
						 @PageSize	  = PageSize,
						 @UserId	  = UserId,	
						 @RoleId	  = RoleId,
						 @DbName	  = DbName,	
						 @LanguageId  = LanguageId	
			FROM @BaseParam
		END
		DECLARE	@WhereSQL				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@Delim					NVARCHAR(100),
				@StartIndex				BIGINT,
				
				@EndIndex				BIGINT,
				@SQL					NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLCount				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLFrom				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SQLSelect				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				
				@dynamicsql				NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@dynamicparamdec		NVARCHAR(MAX),
				@SearchResult			BIGINT,
				@OrderBySQL				VARCHAR(MAX),
				@WhereSQLRight			NVARCHAR(MAX)

		SET		@OrderBy				= ISNULL(@OrderBy,' w.StartDate desc')
		SET		@FilterField			= ISNULL(@FilterField,'')
		SET		@WhereSQL				= ' ' 
		SET		@WhereSQLRight			=''
		SET		@PageNumber				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageNumber,0)	= 0 THEN 1 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageNumber) END
		SET		@PageSize				= CASE WHEN ISNULL(@PageSize,0)	= 0 THEN 50 ELSE CONVERT(int,@PageSize) END

		--1. Calculate to paging
		SET		@StartIndex				= @PageSize * @PageNumber
		SET		@EndIndex				= @StartIndex + @PageSize

		SET		@StartIndex				= ((@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) + 1
		SET		@EndIndex				= @PageNumber * @PageSize

		IF @FilterField <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @FilterField
			END
		--2. get right for role or user
		-- set @WhereSQLRight by role or user
		IF @WhereSQLRight <> ''
			BEGIN
				SET	@Delim				= ' AND '
				SET	@WhereSQL			= @WhereSQL + @Delim +  @WhereSQLRight
			END
		--3. Build select query
			SET	@SQLSelect						= 
			N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
			
			SELECT [Id]
			  ,[StaffId]
			  ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]
			  ,[DecisionNo]
			  ,[WorkingStatus]
			  ,[WorkingStatus]
			  ,[Status]
			  ,[DecisionDate]
			  ,[StartDate]
			  ,[EndDate]
			  ,[ContractId]
			  ,[OrganizationId]
			  ,[OfficeId]
			  ,[PositionId]
			  ,[ClassificationId]
			  ,[StaffLevelId]
			  ,[ManagerId]
			  ,[PolicyId]
			  ,[CurrencyId]
			  ,[BasicPay]
			  ,[EfficiencyBonus]
			  ,[Note]
			  ,Description
			  ,Year = YEAR(w.StartDate)
			  '

	  SET @SQLFrom='FROM [dbo].[Data_Staff_WorkingProcess] w'
	  SET @SQL=@SQLSelect + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 and w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL + 
	  ' ORDER BY ' + @OrderBy --+ 
	  --' OFFSET  '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,(@PageNumber - 1) * @PageSize) +' ROWS  FETCH NEXT '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR,@PageSize) +' ROWS ONLY '
		  
		 PRINT(@SQL)
		  EXEC(@SQL )
		--4. Count
		SET @SQLCount=N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + '] ' + '
		
			SELECT @TotalRecord = COUNT(w.Id) '
		SET @dynamicsql=@SQLCount + @SQLFrom+ ' WHERE w.IsDeleted = 0 and w.StaffId = '+CAST(@StaffId AS NVARCHAR) +' ' +@WhereSQL 
		SET @dynamicparamdec = '@TotalRecord INT OUTPUT'
		PRINT @dynamicsql
		EXEC sp_executesql @dynamicsql,@dynamicparamdec,@TotalRecord  OUTPUT
		
	END TRY

	BEGIN CATCH

		DECLARE	@ErrorNum				INT,
				@ErrorMsg				VARCHAR(200),
				@ErrorProc				VARCHAR(50),
				@SessionId				INT,
				@AddlInfo				VARCHAR(MAX)

		SET @ErrorNum					= ERROR_NUMBER()
		SET @ErrorMsg					= 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessByStaff: ' + ERROR_MESSAGE()
		SET @ErrorProc					= ERROR_PROCEDURE()
		SET @AddlInfo					= '@OrderBy=' + @OrderBy

		EXEC utl_Insert_ErrorLog @ErrorNum,@DbName, @ErrorMsg, @ErrorProc, 'WorkingProcess_Get_GetWorkingProcessByStaff', 'GET', @SessionId, @AddlInfo

	END CATCH
	 
GO
/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Update_SaveWorkingProcessFull]    Script Date: 2/7/2020 6:02:25 PM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
