CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[WorkingProcess_Update_SaveWorkingProcessFull]
	  @IsPossition				BIT,
	  @IsSalary					BIT,
	  @IsContract				BIT,
	  @WorkingProcess			Data_Staff_WorkingProcessType READONLY,
	  @Contract					Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
	  @StaffAllowance			Data_Staff_AllowanceType READONLY,
	  @StaffBenefit				Data_Staff_BenefitType READONLY,
	  @DbName					NVARCHAR(500),
	  @UserId					BIGINT

AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE 
		@ExeQuery			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		,@params			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		,@ExeQueryList		NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''	
		,@WorkingProcessId  BIGINT = 0
		,@ContractId		BIGINT
		,@StaffId  BIGINT = 0
		,@Status  BIGINT = 0
		 
		 SELECT @WorkingProcessId = Id FROM @WorkingProcess
		 SELECT @StaffId = StaffId FROM @WorkingProcess
		 SELECT @Status = Status FROM @WorkingProcess
		 SELECT @ContractId = Id FROM @Contract

		BEGIN
		IF(ISNULL(@WorkingProcessId,0)=0)
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
Declare @CtId   BIGINT
Declare @Id         BIGINT
Declare @PreviousWpId BIGINT =  ( SELECT TOP 1 Id FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Status = 50 and StaffId = @StaffId
						ORDER BY StartDate DESC
						)

IF(ISNULL(@IsContract,0) = 1)
BEGIN
INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Contract]
	([StaffId]
	,[ContractTypeId]
	,[ContractTime]
	,[ContractCode]
	,[Name]
	,[ContractStartDate]
	,[ContractEndDate]
	,[ContractNote]
	,[ContractStatus]
	,[CreateBy]
	,[CreateDate])
SELECT	[StaffId]
	,[ContractTypeId]
	,[ContractTime]
	,[ContractCode]
	,[Name]
	,[ContractStartDate]
	,[ContractEndDate]
	,[ContractNote]
	,[ContractStatus]
	,@UserId
	,GETDATE()
FROM @Contract
SET @CtId =  SCOPE_IDENTITY()
END
ELSE
BEGIN
	SET @CtId = ( SELECT TOP 1 ContractId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Id = @PreviousWpId
						)
END
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess(			
	WorkingprocessTypeId	
	,Status				
	,DecisionNo			
	,DecisionDate			
	,Description			
	,Note	
	,StartDate
	,EndDate
	,StaffId
	,WorkingStatus
	,Isdeleted
	,CreatedBy
	,CreatedDate
	,ContractId	)
SELECT WorkingprocessTypeId	
	,Status				
	,DecisionNo			
	,DecisionDate			
	,Description			
	,Note	
	,StartDate
	,EndDate
	,StaffId
	,WorkingStatus
	,Isdeleted
	,@UserId
	,GETDATE()
	,@CtId
FROM @WorkingProcess
SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
PRINT @Id
PRINT @StaffId
PRINT @Status
IF(@IsPossition = 1)
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	   w.ShiftId			= tmp.ShiftId				
	  ,w.PositionId		= tmp.PositionId			
	  ,w.StaffLevelId		= tmp.StaffLevelId			
	  ,w.OrganizationId	= tmp.OrganizationId	
	  ,w.ClassificationId	= tmp.ClassificationId	
	  ,w.WorkingStatus	= tmp.WorkingStatus			
	  ,w.ManagerId		= tmp.ManagerId
	  ,w.HRManagerId      = tmp.HRManagerId	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
INNER JOIN @WorkingProcess tmp ON tmp.StaffId = w.StaffId	
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId
END
ELSE
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	   ShiftId			 = wPre.ShiftId				
	  ,PositionId		 = wPre.PositionId			
	  ,StaffLevelId		 = wPre.StaffLevelId			
	  ,OrganizationId	 = wPre.OrganizationId	
	  ,ClassificationId	 = wPre.ClassificationId	
	  ,WorkingStatus	 = wPre.WorkingStatus			
	  ,ManagerId		 = wPre.ManagerId
	  ,HRManagerId       = wPre.HRManagerId	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 	
JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess wPre	ON wPre.Id = @PreviousWpId
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId	
END
IF(@IsSalary = 1)
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	 w.PolicyId			= tmp.PolicyId				
	,w.BasicPay			= tmp.BasicPay				
	,w.EfficiencyBonus	= tmp.EfficiencyBonus		
	,w.PaymentForm		= tmp.PaymentForm			
	,w.PaymentMethod	= tmp.PaymentMethod		
	,w.SalaryNote		= tmp.SalaryNote	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
INNER JOIN @WorkingProcess tmp ON tmp.StaffId = w.StaffId	
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId		
END
ELSE
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	 w.PolicyId			= wPre.PolicyId				
	,w.BasicPay			= wPre.BasicPay				
	,w.EfficiencyBonus	= wPre.EfficiencyBonus		
	,w.PaymentForm		= wPre.PaymentForm			
	,w.PaymentMethod		= wPre.PaymentMethod		
	,w.SalaryNote			= wPre.SalaryNote	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 	
JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess wPre	ON wPre.Id = @PreviousWpId
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId
END
IF(@Status = 50)
BEGIN
	UPDATE Data_Staff_Information SET CurrentWorkingProcessId = @Id WHERE Id = @StaffId
END

INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance
   ( WorkingProcessId ,
     StaffId ,
     AllowanceType ,
     Status ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 TaxExemption ,
	 CreatedBy,
	 CreatedDate,
     IsDeleted
   )
SELECT @Id ,
     @StaffId ,
     AllowanceType ,
     Status ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 TaxExemption ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffAllowance Where ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Benefits
   ( WorkingProcessId ,
     StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 CreatedBy,
	 CreatedDate,
     IsDeleted
   )
SELECT @Id ,
     @StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffBenefit WHERE ISNULL(IsDeleted, 0) = 0
SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Id = @Id
'
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
UPDATE w
   SET [StaffId]	= tmp.[StaffId]				
      ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]= tmp.[WorkingprocessTypeId]	
      ,[DecisionNo]		= tmp.[DecisionNo]				
      ,[WorkingStatus]	= tmp.[WorkingStatus]			
      ,[DecisionDate]	= tmp.[DecisionDate]			
      ,[StartDate]		= tmp.[StartDate]				
      ,[EndDate]		= tmp.[EndDate]				
      --,[ContractId]	= tmp.[ContractId]				
      ,[OrganizationId]	= tmp.[OrganizationId]			
      ,[OfficeId]		= tmp.[OfficeId]				
      ,[PositionId]		= tmp.[PositionId]				
      ,[ClassificationId]	= tmp.[ClassificationId]		
      ,[StaffLevelId]	= tmp.[StaffLevelId]			
      ,[ManagerId]		= tmp.[ManagerId]				
      ,[HRManagerId]	= tmp.[HRManagerId]			
      ,[PolicyId]		= tmp.[PolicyId]				
      ,[BasicPay]		= tmp.[BasicPay]				
      ,[EfficiencyBonus]	= tmp.[EfficiencyBonus]		
      ,[PaymentForm]	= tmp.[PaymentForm]			
      ,[PaymentMethod]	= tmp.[PaymentMethod]			
      ,[SalaryNote]		= tmp.[SalaryNote]				
      ,[Description]	= tmp.[Description]			
      ,[Note]			= tmp.[Note]					
      --,[IsDeleted]	= tmp.[IsDeleted]				
      ,[Status]			= tmp.[Status]		
      ,[ShiftId]		= tmp.[ShiftId]	
      ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
	INNER JOIN @WorkingProcess tmp ON tmp.Id = w.Id	
	WHERE w.Id = @WorkingProcessId
IF(@ContractId > 0)
BEGIN
	UPDATE ct
	   SET ct.[StaffId]			= tmp.[StaffId]			
	      ,ct.[ContractTypeId]	= tmp.[ContractTypeId]		
	      ,ct.[ContractTime]	= tmp.[ContractTime]		
	      ,ct.[ContractCode]	= tmp.[ContractCode]		
	      ,ct.[Name]			= tmp.[Name]				
	      ,ct.[ContractStartDate]= tmp.[ContractStartDate]	
	      ,ct.[ContractEndDate]	= tmp.[ContractEndDate]	
	      ,ct.[ContractNote]	= tmp.[ContractNote]		
	      ,ct.[ContractStatus]	= tmp.[ContractStatus]				
	      ,ct.[ModifiedBy]		= @UserId			
	      ,ct.[ModifiedDate]	= GETDATE()		
	FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Contract ct 
	INNER JOIN @Contract tmp ON tmp.Id = ct.Id	
	WHERE ct.Id = @ContractId
END
ELSE
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Contract]
		([StaffId]
		,[ContractTypeId]
		,[ContractTime]
		,[ContractCode]
		,[Name]
		,[ContractStartDate]
		,[ContractEndDate]
		,[ContractNote]
		,[ContractStatus]
		,[CreateBy]
		,[CreateDate])
	SELECT	[StaffId]
		,[ContractTypeId]
		,[ContractTime]
		,[ContractCode]
		,[Name]
		,[ContractStartDate]
		,[ContractEndDate]
		,[ContractNote]
		,[ContractStatus]
		,@UserId
		,GETDATE()
	FROM @Contract
	SET @ContractId =  SCOPE_IDENTITY()
	UPDATE Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET ContractId = @ContractId where Id = @WorkingProcessId
END
UPDATE SA
   SET [WorkingProcessId]=@WorkingProcessId
      ,[StaffId]		= @StaffId
      ,[AllowanceType]	= TMP.AllowanceType
      ,[Status]			= TMP.Status
      ,[Amount]			= TMP.Amount
      ,[CurrencyId]		= TMP.CurrencyId
      ,[Content]		= TMP.Content
      ,[Note]			= TMP.Note
      ,[StartDate]		= TMP.StartDate
      ,[EndDate]		= TMP.EndDate
      ,[TaxExemption]	= TMP.TaxExemption
      ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId
      ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,[IsDeleted]		= TMP.IsDeleted
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance SA
INNER JOIN @StaffAllowance TMP ON SA.Id = TMP.Id

INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance
  ( WorkingProcessId ,
    StaffId ,
    AllowanceType ,
    Status ,
    Amount ,
    CurrencyId ,
    Content ,
    Note ,
    StartDate ,
    EndDate ,
	TaxExemption ,
	CreatedBy,
	CreatedDate,
    IsDeleted
  )
SELECT @WorkingProcessId ,
     @StaffId ,
     AllowanceType ,
     Status ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 TaxExemption ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffAllowance Where ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0
AND Id = 0
UPDATE SB
   SET [WorkingProcessId] = @WorkingProcessId
      ,[StaffId]		= @StaffId
      ,[BenefitType]	= TMP.BenefitType
      ,[Amount]			= TMP.Amount
      ,[CurrencyId]		= TMP.CurrencyId
      ,[Content]		= TMP.Content
      ,[Note]			= TMP.Note
      ,[Status]			= TMP.Status
      ,[StartDate]		= TMP.StartDate
      ,[EndDate]		= TMP.EndDate
      ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId
      ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,[IsDeleted]		= TMP.IsDeleted
FROM Data_Staff_Benefits SB
INNER JOIN @StaffBenefit TMP ON SB.Id = TMP.Id
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Benefits
   ( WorkingProcessId ,
     StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 CreatedBy,
	 CreatedDate,
     IsDeleted
   )
SELECT @WorkingProcessId,
     @StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffBenefit WHERE ISNULL(IsDeleted, 0) = 0 AND Id = 0
SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Id = @WorkingProcessId
			'
		END
		
		PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '	 
			 @IsPossition				BIT,
			 @IsSalary					BIT,
			 @IsContract				BIT,
			 @WorkingProcess			Data_Staff_WorkingProcessType READONLY,
			 @Contract					Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
			 @StaffAllowance			Data_Staff_AllowanceType READONLY,
			 @StaffBenefit				Data_Staff_BenefitType READONLY,
			 @DbName					NVARCHAR(500),
			 @UserId					BIGINT,
			 @Status					BIGINT,
			 @StaffId					BIGINT,
			 @ContractId				BIGINT,
			 @WorkingProcessId			BIGINT
		'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params
			,@IsPossition				
			,@IsSalary
			,@IsContract
			,@WorkingProcess
			,@Contract	
			,@StaffAllowance
			,@StaffBenefit
			,@DbName		
			,@UserId	
			,@Status	
			,@StaffId	
			,@ContractId
			,@WorkingProcessId
			
    END 
END
GO

	  @IsPossition				BIT,
	  @IsSalary					BIT,

	  @Contract					Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
	  @StaffAllowance			Data_Staff_AllowanceType READONLY,
	  @StaffBenefit				Data_Staff_BenefitType READONLY,
	  @StaffOnboardInfo			StaffOnboardInfoType READONLY,
	  @DbName					NVARCHAR(500),
	  @UserId					BIGINT

AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE 
		@ExeQuery			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		,@params			NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''
		,@ExeQueryList		NVARCHAR(MAX) = ''	
		,@WorkingProcessId  BIGINT = 0
		,@ContractId		BIGINT
		,@StaffId  BIGINT = 0
		,@Status  BIGINT = 0
		 
		SELECT @WorkingProcessId = Id FROM @WorkingProcess
		SELECT @StaffId = StaffId FROM @WorkingProcess
		SELECT @Status = Status FROM @WorkingProcess
		SELECT @ContractId = Id FROM @Contract

		DECLARE 
			@IsOnboarding BIT = 0,
			@PipelineId BIGINT = 0,
			@PipelineStepId BIGINT = 0,
			@OnboardingDate	DATETIME = NULL
		IF EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM @StaffOnboardInfo)
		BEGIN
			SELECT
				 @IsOnboarding		= IsOnboarding 
				,@PipelineId		= PipelineId 
				,@PipelineStepId	= PipelineStepId 
				,@OnboardingDate	= OnboardingDate 
			FROM @StaffOnboardInfo
		END

		PRINT @PipelineId 
		PRINT	@PipelineStepId 

		BEGIN
		IF(ISNULL(@WorkingProcessId,0)=0)
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N' 
Declare @CtId   BIGINT
Declare @Id         BIGINT
Declare @PreviousWpId BIGINT =  ( SELECT TOP 1 Id FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Status = 50 and StaffId = @StaffId
						ORDER BY StartDate DESC
						)

IF(ISNULL(@IsContract,0) = 1)
BEGIN
INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Contract]
	([StaffId]
	,[ContractTypeId]
	,[ContractTime]
	,[ContractCode]
	,[Name]
	,[ContractStartDate]
	,[ContractEndDate]
	,[ContractNote]
	,[ContractStatus]
	,[CreateBy]
	,[CreateDate])
SELECT	[StaffId]
	,[ContractTypeId]
	,[ContractTime]
	,[ContractCode]
	,[Name]
	,[ContractStartDate]
	,[ContractEndDate]
	,[ContractNote]
	,[ContractStatus]
	,@UserId
	,GETDATE()
FROM @Contract
SET @CtId =  SCOPE_IDENTITY()
END
ELSE
BEGIN
	SET @CtId = ( SELECT TOP 1 ContractId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Id = @PreviousWpId
						)
END
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess(			
	WorkingprocessTypeId	
	,Status				
	,DecisionNo			
	,DecisionDate			
	,Description			
	,Note	
	,StartDate
	,EndDate
	,StaffId
	,WorkingStatus
	,Isdeleted
	,CreatedBy
	,CreatedDate
	,ContractId	)
SELECT WorkingprocessTypeId	
	,Status				
	,DecisionNo			
	,DecisionDate			
	,Description			
	,Note	
	,StartDate
	,EndDate
	,StaffId
	,WorkingStatus
	,Isdeleted
	,@UserId
	,GETDATE()
	,@CtId
FROM @WorkingProcess
SET @Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
PRINT @Id
PRINT @StaffId
PRINT @Status
IF(@IsPossition = 1)
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	   w.ShiftId			= tmp.ShiftId				
	  ,w.PositionId		= tmp.PositionId			
	  ,w.StaffLevelId		= tmp.StaffLevelId			
	  ,w.OrganizationId	= tmp.OrganizationId	
	  ,w.ClassificationId	= tmp.ClassificationId	
	  ,w.WorkingStatus	= tmp.WorkingStatus			
	  ,w.ManagerId		= tmp.ManagerId
	  ,w.HRManagerId      = tmp.HRManagerId	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
INNER JOIN @WorkingProcess tmp ON tmp.StaffId = w.StaffId	
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId
END
ELSE
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	   ShiftId			 = wPre.ShiftId				
	  ,PositionId		 = wPre.PositionId			
	  ,StaffLevelId		 = wPre.StaffLevelId			
	  ,OrganizationId	 = wPre.OrganizationId	
	  ,ClassificationId	 = wPre.ClassificationId	
	  ,WorkingStatus	 = wPre.WorkingStatus			
	  ,ManagerId		 = wPre.ManagerId
	  ,HRManagerId       = wPre.HRManagerId	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 	
JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess wPre	ON wPre.Id = @PreviousWpId
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId	
END
IF(@IsSalary = 1)
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	 w.PolicyId			= tmp.PolicyId				
	,w.BasicPay			= tmp.BasicPay				
	,w.EfficiencyBonus	= tmp.EfficiencyBonus		
	,w.PaymentForm		= tmp.PaymentForm			
	,w.PaymentMethod	= tmp.PaymentMethod		
	,w.SalaryNote		= tmp.SalaryNote	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
INNER JOIN @WorkingProcess tmp ON tmp.StaffId = w.StaffId	
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId		
END
ELSE
BEGIN
UPDATE w SET
	 w.PolicyId			= wPre.PolicyId				
	,w.BasicPay			= wPre.BasicPay				
	,w.EfficiencyBonus	= wPre.EfficiencyBonus		
	,w.PaymentForm		= wPre.PaymentForm			
	,w.PaymentMethod		= wPre.PaymentMethod		
	,w.SalaryNote			= wPre.SalaryNote	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 	
JOIN dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess wPre	ON wPre.Id = @PreviousWpId
WHERE w.Id = @Id AND w.StaffId =@StaffId
END
IF(@Status = 50)
BEGIN
	UPDATE Data_Staff_Information SET CurrentWorkingProcessId = @Id WHERE Id = @StaffId
END

INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance
   ( WorkingProcessId ,
     StaffId ,
     AllowanceType ,
     Status ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 TaxExemption ,
	 CreatedBy,
	 CreatedDate,
     IsDeleted
   )
SELECT @Id ,
     @StaffId ,
     AllowanceType ,
     Status ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 TaxExemption ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffAllowance Where ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Benefits
   ( WorkingProcessId ,
     StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 CreatedBy,
	 CreatedDate,
     IsDeleted
   )
SELECT @Id ,
     @StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffBenefit WHERE ISNULL(IsDeleted, 0) = 0
SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Id = @Id
'
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @ExeQuery = N'USE [Hrm_'+ @DbName + ']' + N'
UPDATE w
   SET [StaffId]	= tmp.[StaffId]				
      ,[WorkingprocessTypeId]= tmp.[WorkingprocessTypeId]	
      ,[DecisionNo]		= tmp.[DecisionNo]				
      ,[WorkingStatus]	= tmp.[WorkingStatus]			
      ,[DecisionDate]	= tmp.[DecisionDate]			
      ,[StartDate]		= tmp.[StartDate]				
      ,[EndDate]		= tmp.[EndDate]				
      --,[ContractId]	= tmp.[ContractId]				
      ,[OrganizationId]	= tmp.[OrganizationId]			
      ,[OfficeId]		= tmp.[OfficeId]				
      ,[PositionId]		= tmp.[PositionId]				
      ,[ClassificationId]	= tmp.[ClassificationId]		
      ,[StaffLevelId]	= tmp.[StaffLevelId]			
      ,[ManagerId]		= tmp.[ManagerId]				
      ,[HRManagerId]	= tmp.[HRManagerId]			
      ,[PolicyId]		= tmp.[PolicyId]				
      ,[BasicPay]		= tmp.[BasicPay]				
      ,[EfficiencyBonus]	= tmp.[EfficiencyBonus]		
      ,[PaymentForm]	= tmp.[PaymentForm]			
      ,[PaymentMethod]	= tmp.[PaymentMethod]			
      ,[SalaryNote]		= tmp.[SalaryNote]				
      ,[Description]	= tmp.[Description]			
      ,[Note]			= tmp.[Note]					
      --,[IsDeleted]	= tmp.[IsDeleted]				
      ,[Status]			= tmp.[Status]		
      ,[ShiftId]		= tmp.[ShiftId]	
      ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId	
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess w 
	INNER JOIN @WorkingProcess tmp ON tmp.Id = w.Id	
	WHERE w.Id = @WorkingProcessId
IF(@IsOnboarding = 1)
	BEGIN
		UPDATE [dbo].[Data_Staff_BoardingProcess] SET [OnboardingDate] = @OnboardingDate WHERE StaffId = @StaffId
        DECLARE  @TMPPipelineId	BIGINT ,@TMPPipelineStepId BIGINT
		SELECT TOP 1 @TMPPipelineId =  PipelineId, @TMPPipelineStepId = PipelineStepId FROM dbo.Data_Staff_PipelineStatus WHERE StaffId=@StaffId ORDER BY Id DESC
		IF(@TMPPipelineId !=  @PipelineId OR @TMPPipelineStepId != @PipelineStepId)
		BEGIN
			INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_PipelineStatus]
			   ([StaffId]
			   ,[PipelineId]
			   ,[PipelineStepId]
			   ,[Date]
			   ,[Note]
			   ,[IsDeleted])
			VALUEs( 
				@StaffId
			   ,@PipelineId
			   ,@PipelineStepId
			   ,GETDATE()
			   ,NULL
			   ,0)
		END
	END
IF(@ContractId > 0)
BEGIN
	UPDATE ct
	   SET ct.[StaffId]			= tmp.[StaffId]			
	      ,ct.[ContractTypeId]	= tmp.[ContractTypeId]		
	      ,ct.[ContractTime]	= tmp.[ContractTime]		
	      ,ct.[ContractCode]	= tmp.[ContractCode]		
	      ,ct.[Name]			= tmp.[Name]				
	      ,ct.[ContractStartDate]= tmp.[ContractStartDate]	
	      ,ct.[ContractEndDate]	= tmp.[ContractEndDate]	
	      ,ct.[ContractNote]	= tmp.[ContractNote]		
	      ,ct.[ContractStatus]	= tmp.[ContractStatus]				
	      ,ct.[ModifiedBy]		= @UserId			
	      ,ct.[ModifiedDate]	= GETDATE()		
	FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Contract ct 
	INNER JOIN @Contract tmp ON tmp.Id = ct.Id	
	WHERE ct.Id = @ContractId
END
ELSE
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO [dbo].[Data_Staff_Contract]
		([StaffId]
		,[ContractTypeId]
		,[ContractTime]
		,[ContractCode]
		,[Name]
		,[ContractStartDate]
		,[ContractEndDate]
		,[ContractNote]
		,[ContractStatus]
		,[CreateBy]
		,[CreateDate])
	SELECT	[StaffId]
		,[ContractTypeId]
		,[ContractTime]
		,[ContractCode]
		,[Name]
		,[ContractStartDate]
		,[ContractEndDate]
		,[ContractNote]
		,[ContractStatus]
		,@UserId
		,GETDATE()
	FROM @Contract
	SET @ContractId =  SCOPE_IDENTITY()
	UPDATE Data_Staff_WorkingProcess SET ContractId = @ContractId where Id = @WorkingProcessId
END
UPDATE SA
   SET [WorkingProcessId]=@WorkingProcessId
      ,[StaffId]		= @StaffId
      ,[AllowanceType]	= TMP.AllowanceType
      ,[Status]			= TMP.Status
      ,[Amount]			= TMP.Amount
      ,[CurrencyId]		= TMP.CurrencyId
      ,[Content]		= TMP.Content
      ,[Note]			= TMP.Note
      ,[StartDate]		= TMP.StartDate
      ,[EndDate]		= TMP.EndDate
      ,[TaxExemption]	= TMP.TaxExemption
      ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId
      ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,[IsDeleted]		= TMP.IsDeleted
FROM dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance SA
INNER JOIN @StaffAllowance TMP ON SA.Id = TMP.Id

INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Allowance
  ( WorkingProcessId ,
    StaffId ,
    AllowanceType ,
    Status ,
    Amount ,
    CurrencyId ,
    Content ,
    Note ,
    StartDate ,
    EndDate ,
	TaxExemption ,
	CreatedBy,
	CreatedDate,
    IsDeleted
  )
SELECT @WorkingProcessId ,
     @StaffId ,
     AllowanceType ,
     Status ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 TaxExemption ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffAllowance Where ISNULL(IsDeleted,0) = 0
AND Id = 0
UPDATE SB
   SET [WorkingProcessId] = @WorkingProcessId
      ,[StaffId]		= @StaffId
      ,[BenefitType]	= TMP.BenefitType
      ,[Amount]			= TMP.Amount
      ,[CurrencyId]		= TMP.CurrencyId
      ,[Content]		= TMP.Content
      ,[Note]			= TMP.Note
      ,[Status]			= TMP.Status
      ,[StartDate]		= TMP.StartDate
      ,[EndDate]		= TMP.EndDate
      ,[UpdatedBy]		= @UserId
      ,[UpdatedDate]	= GETDATE()
      ,[IsDeleted]		= TMP.IsDeleted
FROM Data_Staff_Benefits SB
INNER JOIN @StaffBenefit TMP ON SB.Id = TMP.Id
INSERT INTO dbo.Data_Staff_Benefits
   ( WorkingProcessId ,
     StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 CreatedBy,
	 CreatedDate,
     IsDeleted
   )
SELECT @WorkingProcessId,
     @StaffId ,
     BenefitType ,
     Amount ,
     CurrencyId ,
     Content ,
     Note ,
     Status ,
     StartDate ,
     EndDate ,
	 @UserId,
	 GETDATE(),
     IsDeleted
FROM @StaffBenefit WHERE ISNULL(IsDeleted, 0) = 0 AND Id = 0
SELECT * FROM dbo.Data_Staff_WorkingProcess WHERE Id = @WorkingProcessId
			'
		END
		
		PRINT @ExeQuery
		SET @params = '	 
			 @IsPossition				BIT,
			 @IsSalary					BIT,
			 @IsContract				BIT,
			 @WorkingProcess			Data_Staff_WorkingProcessType READONLY,
			 @Contract					Data_Staff_ContractType READONLY,
			 @StaffAllowance			Data_Staff_AllowanceType READONLY,
			 @StaffBenefit				Data_Staff_BenefitType READONLY,
			 @StaffOnboardInfo			StaffOnboardInfoType READONLY,
			 @IsOnboarding BIT = 0,
			 @PipelineId BIGINT = 0,
			 @PipelineStepId BIGINT = 0,
			 @OnboardingDate	DATETIME = NULL,
			 @DbName					NVARCHAR(500),
			 @UserId					BIGINT,
			 @Status					BIGINT,
			 @StaffId					BIGINT,
			 @ContractId				BIGINT,
			 @WorkingProcessId			BIGINT
		'
		EXEC sp_executesql @ExeQuery, @params
			,@IsPossition				
			,@IsSalary
			,@IsContract
			,@WorkingProcess
			,@Contract	
			,@StaffAllowance
			,@StaffBenefit
			,@StaffOnboardInfo
			,@IsOnboarding 
			,@PipelineId
			,@PipelineStepId 
			,@OnboardingDate	
			,@DbName		
			,@UserId	
			,@Status	
			,@StaffId	
			,@ContractId
			,@WorkingProcessId
			
    END 
END
GO
USE [master]
GO
ALTER DATABASE [Hrm2.0] SET  READ_WRITE 
GO
